INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLALM.ALM_COBERTURA_DATOS_ADICIONALES
SELECT DISTINCT
NUM_POLIZA,VIGENCIA_POLIZA,NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,

IND_OBJETO,
CVE_SISTEMA,
CVE_SISTEMA_INT,

IF (VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA IS NULL,0.0,VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA)                                AS VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA,
IF (CVE_UNIDAD_SUMA_ASEGURADA IS NULL,'',CVE_UNIDAD_SUMA_ASEGURADA)                   AS CVE_UNIDAD_SUMA_ASEGURADA,
IF (VAL_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL IS NULL,0.0,VAL_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL)                        AS VAL_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL,
IF (CVE_MONEDA_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL IS NULL,'',CVE_MONEDA_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL)           AS CVE_MONEDA_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL,
IF (VAL_DEDUCIBLE_INTERNACIONAL IS NULL,'',VAL_DEDUCIBLE_INTERNACIONAL)              AS VAL_DEDUCIBLE_INTERNACIONAL,
IF (CVE_MONEDA_DEDUCIBLE_INTERNACIONAL IS NULL,'',CVE_MONEDA_DEDUCIBLE_INTERNACIONAL) AS CVE_MONEDA_DEDUCIBLE_INTERNACIONAL,
IF (PCT_COASEGURO_NACIONAL IS NULL,'',PCT_COASEGURO_NACIONAL)                         AS PCT_COASEGURO_NACIONAL,
IF (LIM_COASEGURO_NACIONAL IS NULL,'',LIM_COASEGURO_NACIONAL)                         AS LIM_COASEGURO_NACIONAL,
IF (CVE_MONEDA_COASEGURO_NACIONAL IS NULL,'',CVE_MONEDA_COASEGURO_NACIONAL)           AS CVE_MONEDA_COASEGURO_NACIONAL,
IF (PCT_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL IS NULL,'',PCT_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL)               AS PCT_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL,
IF (LIM_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL IS NULL,'',LIM_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL)               AS LIM_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL,
IF (CVE_MONEDA_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL IS NULL,'',CVE_MONEDA_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL) AS CVE_MONEDA_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL,
IF (CVE_ESTATUS_COBERTURA IS NULL,'',CVE_ESTATUS_COBERTURA)                           AS CVE_ESTATUS_COBERTURA,
IF( FCH_INI_COBERTURA IS NULL OR FCH_INI_COBERTURA =0 OR TRIM(FCH_INI_COBERTURA)='' ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_INI_COBERTURA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_INI_COBERTURA,
IF( FCH_FIN_COBERTURA IS NULL OR FCH_FIN_COBERTURA =0 OR TRIM(FCH_FIN_COBERTURA )='' ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_FIN_COBERTURA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_FIN_COBERTURA,
IF( FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO IS NULL OR FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO=0 OR TRIM(FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO)='' ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO,
IF( FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO IS NULL OR FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO=0 OR TRIM(FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO)='' ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO,
IF (IND_NIVEL_ASIGNACION IS NULL,'',IND_NIVEL_ASIGNACION)                             AS IND_NIVEL_ASIGNACION,
IF (VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_OBESIDAD IS NULL,'',VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_OBESIDAD)                       AS VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_OBESIDAD,
IF (VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_DICTAMEN IS NULL,'',VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_DICTAMEN)                       AS VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_DICTAMEN,
CVE_PREEXISTENCIA_COBERTURA,
DES_PREEXISTENCIA_COBERTURA,
IF (CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE IS NULL,'',CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE)                         AS CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE,
IF( FCH_SALIDA_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO IS NULL OR FCH_SALIDA_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO=0 OR TRIM(FCH_SALIDA_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO)='',
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_SALIDA_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_SALIDA_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,
IF( FCH_REGRESO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO IS NULL OR FCH_REGRESO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO=0 OR TRIM(FCH_REGRESO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO)='',
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_REGRESO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_REGRESO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,
IF (CVE_PERIODO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO IS NULL,'',CVE_PERIODO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO)             AS CVE_PERIODO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,
IF (CVE_DESTINO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO IS NULL,'',CVE_DESTINO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO)             AS CVE_DESTINO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,
IF (CVE_TARIFICAR_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO IS NULL,'',CVE_TARIFICAR_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO)         AS CVE_TARIFICAR_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,
IF (VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NACIONAL IS NULL,'',VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NACIONAL)               AS VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NACIONAL,
IF (VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_INTERNACIONAL IS NULL,'',VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_INTERNACIONAL)     AS VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_INTERNACIONAL,
IF (CVE_UNIDAD_MEDIDA_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NAL_INTERNAL IS NULL,'',CVE_UNIDAD_MEDIDA_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NAL_INTERNAL) AS CVE_UNIDAD_MEDIDA_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NAL_INTERNAL,
IF (VAL_RECARGO IS NULL,'',VAL_RECARGO)                                               AS VAL_RECARGO,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD=0  OR TRIM(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD)='',
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))   AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD,
IF (COD_SUMA_ASEGURADA_DIARIA IS NULL,'',COD_SUMA_ASEGURADA_DIARIA)                   AS COD_SUMA_ASEGURADA_DIARIA,
IF (BAN_HOSPITALIZACION IS NULL,'',BAN_HOSPITALIZACION)                               AS BAN_HOSPITALIZACION,
IF (PCT_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA IS NULL,'',PCT_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA)                       AS PCT_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA,
IF (CVE_CONCEPTO_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA IS NULL,'',CVE_CONCEPTO_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA)     AS CVE_CONCEPTO_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA,
IF (PCT_PAGO_HONORARIOS IS NULL,'',PCT_PAGO_HONORARIOS)                               AS PCT_PAGO_HONORARIOS,
IF (PCT_DESCUENTO_RIESGO_SELECTO IS NULL,'',PCT_DESCUENTO_RIESGO_SELECTO)             AS PCT_DESCUENTO_RIESGO_SELECTO,
IF (PCT_DESCUENTO_COMERCIAL_COBERTURA IS NULL,'',PCT_DESCUENTO_COMERCIAL_COBERTURA)   AS PCT_DESCUENTO_COMERCIAL_COBERTURA,
IF (SUM_ASEGURADA_DEPENDIENTES_FALLECIMIENTO IS NULL,'',SUM_ASEGURADA_DEPENDIENTES_FALLECIMIENTO)  AS SUM_ASEGURADA_DEPENDIENTES_FALLECIMIENTO,
CVE_PERIODO_ESPERA_A_PARTIR_DE,
DES_PERIODO_ESPERA_A_PARTIR_DE,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP())  AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
CASE WHEN CVE_SISTEMA = 'INFO' THEN CAST(reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',CONCAT(NVL(NUM_POLIZA,''), CAST(NVL(VIGENCIA_POLIZA,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,0) AS STRING), NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''), CAST(NVL(IND_OBJETO, 0) AS STRING), CAST(NVL(CVE_COBERTURA, '') AS STRING))) AS VARCHAR(32)) ELSE CAST(reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',CONCAT(NVL(NUM_POLIZA,''), CAST(NVL(VIGENCIA_POLIZA,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,0) AS STRING), NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''), NVL(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,''), NVL(CVE_COBERTURA, ''))) AS VARCHAR(32)) END AS IDMD5,
CAST(reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',CONCAT(NVL(NUM_POLIZA,''), CAST(NVL(VIGENCIA_POLIZA,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,0) AS STRING), NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''), NVL(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,''), CAST(NVL(IND_OBJETO, 0) AS STRING), NVL(CVE_SISTEMA,''), NVL(CVE_SISTEMA_INT,''), NVL(CVE_COBERTURA,''), NVL(VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA,0), NVL(CVE_UNIDAD_SUMA_ASEGURADA,''), NVL(VAL_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL,0), NVL(CVE_MONEDA_DEDUCIBLE_NACIONAL,''), NVL(VAL_DEDUCIBLE_INTERNACIONAL,''), NVL(CVE_MONEDA_DEDUCIBLE_INTERNACIONAL,''), NVL(PCT_COASEGURO_NACIONAL,''), NVL(LIM_COASEGURO_NACIONAL,''), NVL(CVE_MONEDA_COASEGURO_NACIONAL,''), NVL(PCT_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL,''), NVL(LIM_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL,''), NVL(CVE_MONEDA_COASEGURO_INTERNACIONAL,''), NVL(CVE_ESTATUS_COBERTURA,''), NVL(FCH_INI_COBERTURA,''), NVL(FCH_FIN_COBERTURA,''), NVL(FCH_EFECTO_MOVIMIENTO,''), NVL(FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO,''), NVL(IND_NIVEL_ASIGNACION,''), NVL(VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_OBESIDAD,''), NVL(VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_DICTAMEN,''), NVL(CVE_PREEXISTENCIA_COBERTURA,''), NVL(DES_PREEXISTENCIA_COBERTURA,''), NVL(CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE,''), NVL(FCH_SALIDA_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,''), NVL(FCH_REGRESO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,''), NVL(CVE_PERIODO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,''), NVL(CVE_DESTINO_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,''), NVL(CVE_TARIFICAR_VIAJE_EXTRANJERO,''), NVL(VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NACIONAL,''), NVL(VAL_SUMA_ASEGURADA_INTERNACIONAL,''), NVL(CVE_UNIDAD_MEDIDA_SUMA_ASEGURADA_NAL_INTERNAL,''), NVL(VAL_RECARGO,''), NVL(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD,''), NVL(COD_SUMA_ASEGURADA_DIARIA,''), NVL(BAN_HOSPITALIZACION,''), NVL(PCT_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA,''), NVL(CVE_CONCEPTO_DESCUENTO_COBERTURA,''), NVL(PCT_PAGO_HONORARIOS,''), NVL(PCT_DESCUENTO_RIESGO_SELECTO,''), NVL(PCT_DESCUENTO_COMERCIAL_COBERTURA,''), NVL(SUM_ASEGURADA_DEPENDIENTES_FALLECIMIENTO,''), NVL(CVE_PERIODO_ESPERA_A_PARTIR_DE,'') ,NVL(DES_PERIODO_ESPERA_A_PARTIR_DE,'')  ))
AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_UNION_COBER_AD

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_COB_DATOS_ADICIONALES AS
SELECT DISTINCT
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_oficina ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS NUM_POLIZA,
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
CONCAT(NVL(gaz0_asegurado.ase_num_certif, ''), NVL(gaz0_asegurado.ase_cve_parien, '')) AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
gaz0_poliza.pol_nombre_cob,
CAST(pol_suma_aseg AS DECIMAL(18,2)) AS val_suma_asegurada,
CAST(pol_deducible AS DECIMAL (18,2))/100 AS val_deducible_nacional,
gaz0_poliza.pol_coaseguro,
CAST(gaz0_poliza.pol_plan as VARCHAR(1)) AS pol_plan  ,
CAST(gaz0_poliza.pol_stdr as VARCHAR(1)) AS pol_stdr
,CAST(gaz0_poliza.cve_unidad AS VARCHAR(15)) as cve_unidad
,CAST(gaz0_poliza.cve_moneda AS VARCHAR(15)) AS cve_moneda
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_CAT_TIPO_UNIDAD as gaz0_poliza
LEFT JOIN  BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_UNION_GAZ0_ASEGURADO as gaz0_asegurado
ON gaz0_poliza.pol_oficina = gaz0_asegurado.ase_pol_ofna
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_numero = gaz0_asegurado.ase_pol_num
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_ofi_renovac = gaz0_asegurado.pol_ofi_renovac
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_num_renovac = gaz0_asegurado.pol_num_renovac
AND gaz0_poliza.end_fecha_ini = gaz0_asegurado.end_fecha_ini
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_oficina = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_oficina
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_tipo = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_tipo
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_consec = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_consec
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_control = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_control
AND gaz0_poliza.end_liga_pol_ase = gaz0_asegurado.end_liga_pol_ase
AND gaz0_poliza.end_incluye_aseg = gaz0_asegurado.end_incluye_aseg
AND gaz0_poliza.end_subramo = gaz0_asegurado.end_subramo
AND gaz0_poliza.end_fecha_fin = gaz0_asegurado.end_fecha_fin

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_CAT_TIPO_UNIDAD AS
SELECT
gaz0_poliza.*
,nvl(trim(tipo_unidad_sum.dca_desc), '') as cve_unidad
,nvl(trim(tipo_unidad_dedu.dca_desc), '')  AS cve_moneda
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_TRANSPOSE_COBERTURA as gaz0_poliza
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.gaz0_cat_tipo_unidad as tipo_unidad_sum
on trim(gaz0_poliza.pol_uni_sum) = trim(tipo_unidad_sum.dca_clave)
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.gaz0_cat_tipo_unidad as tipo_unidad_dedu
on trim(gaz0_poliza.pol_uni_dedu) = trim(tipo_unidad_dedu.dca_clave)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_CAT_TIPO_UNIDAD AS
SELECT
gaz0_poliza.*
,nvl(trim(tipo_unidad_sum.dca_desc), '') as cve_unidad
,nvl(trim(tipo_unidad_dedu.dca_desc), '')  AS cve_moneda
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_TRANSPOSE_COBERTURA as gaz0_poliza
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.gaz0_cat_tipo_unidad as tipo_unidad_sum
on trim(gaz0_poliza.pol_uni_sum) = trim(tipo_unidad_sum.dca_clave)
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.gaz0_cat_tipo_unidad as tipo_unidad_dedu
on trim(gaz0_poliza.pol_uni_dedu) = trim(tipo_unidad_dedu.dca_clave)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_TRANSPOSE_COBERTURA AS
select * FROM(
select pol_oficina, pol_numero,pol_ofi_renovac,pol_num_renovac,
end_fecha_ini,end_num_oficina,end_num_tipo,end_num_consec,
end_num_control,end_liga_pol_ase,end_incluye_aseg,end_subramo ,end_fecha_fin,
cobeturaMap[0] as pol_nombre_cob,
cobeturaMap[1] as pol_coaseguro,
cobeturaMap[2] as pol_suma_aseg,
cobeturaMap[3] as pol_deducible,
cobeturaMap[4] as pol_plan,
cobeturaMap[5] as pol_stdr
,cobeturaMap[6] as pol_uni_sum,
cobeturaMap[7] as pol_uni_dedu
FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_TMP_SPLIT_MAP_COBERTURA ) as TMP

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_COB_DATOS_ADICIONALES AS
SELECT DISTINCT
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_oficina ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS NUM_POLIZA,
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz0_poliza.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
CONCAT(NVL(gaz0_asegurado.ase_num_certif, ''), NVL(gaz0_asegurado.ase_cve_parien, '')) AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
gaz0_poliza.pol_nombre_cob,
CAST(pol_suma_aseg AS DECIMAL(18,2)) AS val_suma_asegurada,
CAST(pol_deducible AS DECIMAL (18,2))/100 AS val_deducible_nacional,
gaz0_poliza.pol_coaseguro,
CAST(gaz0_poliza.pol_plan as VARCHAR(1)) AS pol_plan  ,
CAST(gaz0_poliza.pol_stdr as VARCHAR(1)) AS pol_stdr
,CAST(gaz0_poliza.cve_unidad AS VARCHAR(15)) as cve_unidad
,CAST(gaz0_poliza.cve_moneda AS VARCHAR(15)) AS cve_moneda
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_CAT_TIPO_UNIDAD as gaz0_poliza
LEFT JOIN  BDDLTRN.STG_CNM_CBZA_UNION_GAZ0_ASEGURADO as gaz0_asegurado
ON gaz0_poliza.pol_oficina = gaz0_asegurado.ase_pol_ofna
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_numero = gaz0_asegurado.ase_pol_num
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_ofi_renovac = gaz0_asegurado.pol_ofi_renovac
AND gaz0_poliza.pol_num_renovac = gaz0_asegurado.pol_num_renovac
AND gaz0_poliza.end_fecha_ini = gaz0_asegurado.end_fecha_ini
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_oficina = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_oficina
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_tipo = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_tipo
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_consec = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_consec
AND gaz0_poliza.end_num_control = gaz0_asegurado.end_num_control
AND gaz0_poliza.end_liga_pol_ase = gaz0_asegurado.end_liga_pol_ase
AND gaz0_poliza.end_incluye_aseg = gaz0_asegurado.end_incluye_aseg
AND gaz0_poliza.end_subramo = gaz0_asegurado.end_subramo
AND gaz0_poliza.end_fecha_fin = gaz0_asegurado.end_fecha_fin

---describe bddlapr.cnm_comisiones_asegurado_cobertura  ---describe bddlcru.cat_clave_cobertura_contratada_afectada         SELECT         CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL, TCCDMONE, CDOPERA,         CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST (FECONTAB AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTR(CAST (FECONTAB AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTR(CAST (FECONTAB AS STRING),7,2)) AS TIMESTAMP) AS FECONTAB_FH,         CASE CDOPERA             WHEN '001001' THEN  sum(IMPRNTEC)             WHEN '001003' THEN  sum(IMPRNTEC)  * -1             WHEN '003002' THEN  sum(IMPRNTEC)  * -1             WHEN '003003' THEN  sum(IMPRNTEC)  * -1             WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(IMPRNTEC)                ELSE 0             END AS  IMPRNTEC,         CASE CDOPERA                 WHEN '001001' THEN  sum(DESCCOME)             WHEN '001003' THEN  sum(DESCCOME)  * -1             WHEN '003002' THEN  sum(DESCCOME)  * -1             WHEN '003003' THEN  sum(DESCCOME)  * -1             WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(DESCCOME)                ELSE 0             END AS  DESCCOME,         CASE CDOPERA                 WHEN '001001' THEN  sum(IMREPAFR)             WHEN '001003' THEN  sum(IMREPAFR)  * -1             WHEN '003002' THEN  sum(IMREPAFR)  * -1             WHEN '003003' THEN  sum(IMREPAFR)  * -1             WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(IMREPAFR)                ELSE 0             END AS  IMREPAFR,         CASE CDOPERA                 WHEN '001001' THEN  sum(IMDERECH)             WHEN '001003' THEN  sum(IMDERECH)  * -1             WHEN '003002' THEN  sum(IMDERECH)  * -1             WHEN '003003' THEN  sum(IMDERECH)  * -1             WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(IMDERECH)                ELSE 0             END AS  IMDERECH,         CASE CDOPERA                 WHEN '001001' THEN  sum(IMIVAPRN)             WHEN '001003' THEN  sum(IMIVAPRN)  * -1             WHEN '003002' THEN  sum(IMIVAPRN)  * -1             WHEN '003003' THEN  sum(IMIVAPRN)  * -1             WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(IMIVAPRN)                ELSE 0             END AS  IMIVAPRN,         CASE CDOPERA                 WHEN '001001' THEN  sum(IMIVADER)             WHEN '001003' THEN  sum(IMIVADER)  * -1             WHEN '003002' THEN  sum(IMIVADER)  * -1             WHEN '003003' THEN  sum(IMIVADER)  * -1             WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(IMIVADER)                ELSE 0             END AS  IMIVADER,         CASE CDOPERA                 WHEN '001001' THEN  sum(IMGGINEX)             WHEN '001003' THEN  sum(IMGGINEX)  * -1             WHEN '003002' THEN  sum(IMGGINEX)  * -1             WHEN '003003' THEN  sum(IMGGINEX)  * -1             WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(IMGGINEX)                ELSE 0             END AS  IMGGINEX,         CASE CDOPERA                 WHEN '001001' THEN  sum(IMCESCOM)             WHEN '001003' THEN  sum(IMCESCOM)  * -1             WHEN '003002' THEN  sum(IMCESCOM)  * -1             WHEN '003003' THEN  sum(IMCESCOM)  * -1             WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(IMCESCOM)                ELSE 0             END AS  IMCESCOM,         CASE CDOPERA                 WHEN '001001' THEN  sum(IMPRNETA)             WHEN '001003' THEN  sum(IMPRNETA)  * -1             WHEN '003002' THEN  sum(IMPRNETA)  * -1             WHEN '003003' THEN  sum(IMPRNETA)  * -1             WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(IMPRNETA)                ELSE 0             END AS  IMPRNETA,         CASE CDOPERA                 WHEN '001001' THEN  sum(IMPRITOT)             WHEN '001003' THEN  sum(IMPRITOT)  * -1             WHEN '003002' THEN  sum(IMPRITOT)  * -1             WHEN '003003' THEN  sum(IMPRITOT)  * -1             WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(IMPRITOT)                ELSE 0         END AS  IMPRITOT,         SISTORIG     FROM (             SELECT                 CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL, CDOBJTP, CTSECOBJ, FECONTAB, CDNUMREC, INRECIFR, INDEMIAN,NUAPUNTE,                 CDCIAGRU, TCCDMONE, CDREFDET, FEPROMEC, CDINTERC,FECMVTO, TCDOMORI, NUSECMVO,                 CLFILTOM, CDFILPAG,TCTITXCT,CONCAT(TCTITXCT,TCCOPERA) AS CDOPERA, CDMCT, TCCOPERA,                  IMPCEC01 AS IMPRNTEC,                                  /* PRIMA TECNICA */                  IMPCEC09 AS DESCCOME,                                  /* DESC. COMERCIAL */                  IMPCEC03 + IMPCEC07 AS IMREPAFR,                       /* IMP. RECARGOS (PAGO FRACCIONADO Y DESC POR DOMICILIACION) */                  IMPCEC04 AS IMDERECH,                                  /* DERECHOS */                  IMPCEC05 AS IMIVAPRN,                                  /* IVA SOBRE PRIMA NETA */                  IMPCEC06 AS IMIVADER,                                  /* IVA SOBRE DERECHOS */                  IMPCEC10 AS IMGGINEX,                                  /* GASTOS DE GESTION INTERNA Y EXTERNA */                  IMPCEC02 AS IMCESCOM,                                  /* CESION DE COMISION */                  IMPCEC19 AS IMPRNETA,                                  /* PRIMA NETA */                  IMPCEC20 AS IMPRITOT,                                  /* PRIMA TOTAL */                  'INFO' AS SISTORIG             FROM  bddlcru.ktom41t                                --- MEC SEGURO DIRECTO             WHERE  CDCIAGRU = 'SA'                      /* CODIGO COMPANIA GRUPO */               AND TCTITXCT IN ('001','003')             /* TC TIPO TRANSACCION CONTABLE */               AND TCCOPERA IN ('001','002','003','006','004','005')  /* TC CODIGO OPERACION CONTABLE */  and cdnumpol = '00000249749219'         ) PRP     GROUP BY         CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL,CDOPERA, FECONTAB, TCCDMONE, SISTORIG

       WHEN '003006' THEN  sum(IMPRITOT)                ELSE 0         END AS  IMPRITOT,         SISTORIG     FROM (             SELECT                 CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL, CDOBJTP, CTSECOBJ, FECONTAB, CDNUMREC, INRECIFR, INDEMIAN,NUAPUNTE,                 CDCIAGRU, TCCDMONE, CDREFDET, FEPROMEC, CDINTERC,FECMVTO, TCDOMORI, NUSECMVO,                 CLFILTOM, CDFILPAG,TCTITXCT,CONCAT(TCTITXCT,TCCOPERA) AS CDOPERA, CDMCT, TCCOPERA,                  IMPCEC01 AS IMPRNTEC,                                  /* PRIMA TECNICA */                  IMPCEC09 AS DESCCOME,                                  /* DESC. COMERCIAL */                  IMPCEC03 + IMPCEC07 AS IMREPAFR,                       /* IMP. RECARGOS (PAGO FRACCIONADO Y DESC POR DOMICILIACION) */                  IMPCEC04 AS IMDERECH,                                  /* DERECHOS */                  IMPCEC05 AS IMIVAPRN,                                  /* IVA SOBRE PRIMA NETA */                  IMPCEC06 AS IMIVADER,                                  /* IVA SOBRE DERECHOS */                  IMPCEC10 AS IMGGINEX,                                  /* GASTOS DE GESTION INTERNA Y EXTERNA */                  IMPCEC02 AS IMCESCOM,                                  /* CESION DE COMISION */                  IMPCEC19 AS IMPRNETA,                                  /* PRIMA NETA */                  IMPCEC20 AS IMPRITOT,                                  /* PRIMA TOTAL */                  'INFO' AS SISTORIG             FROM  bddltrn.ktom41  T                              --- MEC SEGURO DIRECTO             WHERE  CDCIAGRU = 'SA'                      /* CODIGO COMPANIA GRUPO */               AND TCTITXCT IN ('001','003')             /* TC TIPO TRANSACCION CONTABLE */               AND TCCOPERA IN ('001','002','003','006','004','005')  /* TC CODIGO OPERACION CONTABLE */  and cdnumpol = '00000249749219'         ) PRP     GROUP BY         CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL,CDOPERA, FECONTAB, TCCDMONE, SISTORIG

SELECT DISTINCT *  FROM ( SELECT      MAX(nombre) AS nombre,     genero,     num_poliza,     cve_negocio_operable,     fch_vigencia_inicial,     fch_vigencia_final,     Correo,     cve_agente,     nombre_agente,     da FROM(         SELECT           DISTINCT          CONCAT(TRIM(UPPER(PERSONA.nombres))," ",TRIM(UPPER(PERSONA.apellido_paterno))," ",TRIM(UPPER(PERSONA.apellido_materno))) AS nombre,          PERSONA.genero,          TAB.num_poliza,          POLAGENTE.cve_negocio_operable,          TAB.fch_vigencia_inicial, GROUP BY 2,3) union( Select  count(DISTINCT id_participante_consolidado),segmento,"94" AS GF from crm_segmento_tom group by 2,3) ORDER BY 3,2

2) union (Select COUNT(DISTINCT id_participante_consolidado),cast(0 as string) as GF,cast(4 as string) as GF FROM crm_tablero_perfil where cve_rol in ('TOM','PAG')) union (Select COUNT(DISTINCT id_participante_consolidado), tipo_participante,cast(5 as string) as GF FROM crm_tablero_perfil where cve_rol in ('TOM','PAG') GROUP BY 2) union( SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT num_poliza) , cve_ramo, CAST(7 as string) as GF FROM crm_tablero_perfil Where cve_rol in ('TOM','PAG') GROUP BY 2) union( SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT num_poliza) , cve_ramo ,"8" AS GF FROM crm_tablero_perfil Where cve_rol in ('TOM','PAG') and tipo_participante='F' GROUP BY 2,3) union ( SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT num_poliza) , cve_ramo ,"9" AS GF FROM crm_tablero_perfil Where cve_rol in ('TOM','PAG') and tipo_participante='M' GROUP BY 2,3) union( Select personas,rol, CONCAT("90.-",trim(tipo_participante))  from  crm_jerarquia) union( Select count(DISTINCT id_participante_consolidado),cve_ramo,"91" as GF FROM crm_tablero_perfil where cve_rol in ('TOM','PAG') GROUP BY 2) union( Select  count(DISTINCT id_participante_consolidado),cve_ramo, "92" AS GF FROM crm_tablero_perfil where cve_rol in ('TOM','PAG') and tipo_participante='F' GROUP BY 2,3 ) union( Select count(DISTINCT id_participante_consolidado),cve_ramo,"93" AS GF FROM crm_tablero_perfil where cve_rol in ('TOM','PAG') AND tipo_participante='M' INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLALM.ALM_GASTO_TABULADO
SELECT DISTINCT
NVL(ID_SOLICITUD, ''),
NVL(CVE_SISTEMA_INT, ''),
NVL(CVE_SISTEMA, ''),
NVL(NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION, 0),
NVL(NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT, 0),
NVL(MTO_AUTORIZADO, 0.0),
NVL(MTO_RECLAMADO, 0.0),
NVL(MTO_TABULADO_UNITARIO, 0.0),
NVL(MTO_TABULADO, 0.0),
NVL(PCT_AUTORIZADO_TABULADOR, 0.0),
NVL(CVE_PROFESIONAL, ''),
TRIM(NVL(DESCR_PROFESIONAL, '')),
IND_TAB_AUTOMATICA,
TRIM(NVL(TCCDCPT, '')),
NVL(CDFILMED, ''),
TRIM(NVL(RFC_MEDICO, '')),
TRIM(NVL(APELLIDO_PATERNO_MEDICO, '')),
TRIM(NVL(APELLIDO_MATERNO_MEDICO, '')),
TRIM(NVL(NOMBRE_MEDICO, '')),
TRIM(NVL(RAZON_SOCIAL, '')),
NVL(CONVENIADO, ''),
TRIM(NVL(ESPECIALIDAD, '')),
TRIM(NVL(TCCDMONE, '')),
NVL(NUDOCUCO, ''),
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', CONCAT(NVL(ID_SOLICITUD,''),NVL(CVE_SISTEMA,''),NVL(NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,0),NVL(NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,0),NVL(CVE_PROFESIONAL,''))) AS IDMD5,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', CONCAT(NVL(ID_SOLICITUD,''),NVL(CVE_SISTEMA_INT,''),NVL(CVE_SISTEMA,''),NVL(NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,0),NVL(NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,0),NVL(MTO_AUTORIZADO,0),NVL(MTO_RECLAMADO,0),NVL(MTO_TABULADO_UNITARIO,0),NVL(MTO_TABULADO,0),NVL(PCT_AUTORIZADO_TABULADOR,0),NVL(CVE_PROFESIONAL,''),NVL(DESCR_PROFESIONAL,''),NVL(IND_TAB_AUTOMATICA,0),NVL(TCCDCPT, ''), NVL(CDFILMED, ''),NVL(RFC_MEDICO, ''),NVL(APELLIDO_PATERNO_MEDICO, ''),NVL(APELLIDO_MATERNO_MEDICO, ''),NVL(NOMBRE_MEDICO, ''),NVL(RAZON_SOCIAL, ''),NVL(CONVENIADO, ''),NVL(ESPECIALIDAD, ''),NVL(TCCDMONE, ''),NVL(NUDOCUCO, ''))) AS IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_CMM_GASTO_TABULADO_UNION

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_CMM_GASTO_TABULADO_INFO
SELECT
TRIM(K53T.CDSINIES) AS ID_SOLICITUD,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA,
K53T.CTNUICD AS NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,
K53T.CTNUCPT AS NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,
K53T.IMHMAUTO AS MTO_AUTORIZADO,
K53T.IMHMSOLI AS MTO_RECLAMADO,
K53T.IMHMTAUN AS MTO_TABULADO_UNITARIO,
K53T.IMHMTABU AS MTO_TABULADO,
K53T.POIMPAUT AS PCT_AUTORIZADO_TABULADOR,
TRIM(NVL(K53T.TCTIPROF, '')) AS CVE_PROFESIONAL,
TRIM(NVL(KTCT.DSELEMEN, '')) AS DESCR_PROFESIONAL,
IF(TRIM(K53T.INTABAUT)='N',0,1) AS IND_TAB_AUTOMATICA,
TRIM(NVL(K52T.TCCDCPT, '')) AS TCCDCPT,
TRIM(NVL(K52T.CDFILMED, '')) AS CDFILMED,
TRIM(NVL(CAT.RFC_MEDICO, '')) AS RFC_MEDICO,
TRIM(NVL(CAT.APELLIDO_PATERNO_MEDICO, '')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_MEDICO,
TRIM(NVL(CAT.APELLIDO_MATERNO_MEDICO, '')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_MEDICO,
TRIM(NVL(CAT.NOMBRE_MEDICO, '')) AS NOMBRE_MEDICO,
TRIM(NVL(CAT.RAZON_SOCIAL, '')) AS RAZON_SOCIAL,
IF(ISNULL(K52T.CDFILMED) OR TRIM(K52T.CDFILMED) = '', 'NO', 'SI'),
TRIM(NVL(CAT.ESPECIALIDAD, '')) AS ESPECIALIDAD,
TRIM(NVL(K53T.TCCDMONE, '')) AS TCCDMONE,
TRIM(NVL(K71T.NUDOCUCO, '')) AS NUDOCUCO
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM53T AS K53T
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM52T AS K52T
ON K53T.CDSINIES = K52T.CDSINIES AND K53T.CTNUPOIN = K52T.CTNUPOIN AND K53T.CTNUICD = K52T.CTNUICD AND K53T.CTNUCPT = K52T.CTNUCPT
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_MEDICOS AS CAT
ON CAT.NUM_FILIACION = CAST(K52T.CDFILMED AS INT)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM71T K71T
ON K53T.CDSINIES = K71T.CDSINIES AND K53T.CTNUPOIN = K71T.CTNUPOIN AND K53T.CTNUGAST = K71T.CTNUGAST
LEFT JOIN
( SELECT LTRIM(RTRIM(CDELEMEN)) AS CDELEMEN,DSELEMEN
FROM BDDLCRU.KTCTGET
WHERE LTRIM(RTRIM(CDTABLA)) = 'KACTDTG'
) KTCT
ON K53T.TCTIPROF = KTCT.CDELEMEN
WHERE K53T.CDSECUEN = 0
UNION ALL
SELECT
TRIM(K53T.CDSINIES) AS ID_SOLICITUD,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA,
K53T.CTNUICD AS NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,
K53T.CTNUCPT AS NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,
K53T.IMHMAUTO AS MTO_AUTORIZADO,
K53T.IMHMSOLI AS MTO_RECLAMADO,
K53T.IMHMTAUN AS MTO_TABULADO_UNITARIO,

create table if not exists bddldes.bov_cifras1
as
Select
cast(A.CDSINIES as char(28)) AS NUM_SINIESTRO_RECLAMACION,
cast(B.CDFACTMI as char(8)) as FOLIO_SEGUIMIENTO_PROVEEDOR,
Cast(0 as char(8)) AS NUM_PAGO_FACTURA,
cast(E.NUMOVECO as char(12)) AS NUM_PETICION_PAGO,
cast('INFO' as  char(4) ) as CVE_SISTEMA ,
cast('A' as char(1))  as CVE_RAMO,
coalesce(cast(CONCAT(SUBSTR(D.FECONTAB,1,4),'-',SUBSTR(D.FECONTAB,5,2),'-',SUBSTR(D.FECONTAB,7,2),' 00:00:00.0') as timestamp),cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00.0' as timestamp)) as FECHA_CONTABLE,
coalesce(cast(CONCAT(SUBSTR(C.FEOPERA,1,4),'-',SUBSTR(C.FEOPERA,5,2),'-',SUBSTR(C.FEOPERA,7,2),' 00:00:00.0') as timestamp),cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00.0' as timestamp)) as FECHA_CAPTURA_SISTEMA_ORIGEN,
case when trim(C.TCCDMONE)='MXP' then cast('MXN' as char(4)) else case when  trim(C.TCCDMONE)='USD' then cast('USD' as char(4)) else cast('MXN' as char(4)) end end AS CVE_MONEDA,
coalesce(cast(CONCAT(SUBSTR(C.FECHAEMI,1,4),'-',SUBSTR(C.FECHAEMI,5,2),'-',SUBSTR(C.FECHAEMI,7,2),' 00:00:00.0') as timestamp),cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00.0' as timestamp)) as FECHA_PAGO,
cast(D.CDREFCAB as char(20))  AS REFERENCIA_ASIENTO_CONTABLE,
cast(SUBSTR(E.CDCUENTA,2,4) as char(4)) AS TERMINACION_CUENTA_BANCARIA,
cast(Z.DESCRIPCION as char(50)) AS ENTIDAD_FINANCIERA,
cast(current_date() as timestamp) as TS_ALTA_AUDIT,
cast(current_date()  as timestamp) as TS_ACTUALIZA_AUDIT,
cast('DATALAKE' as char(12) ) as USUARIO_AUDIT
FROM  (select CDSINIES,TCTIPSIN from bddlcru.KSIM10T where TCTIPSIN = 'AU') as A
INNER join (select CDFACTMI,CDSINIES,TCTIPSIN,numoveco from bddlcru.KTOM14T  ) B   on
A.CDSINIES = B.CDSINIES
and A.TCTIPSIN = B.TCTIPSIN
and trim(b.CDFACTMI) <> ''
INNER join (select FECONTAB,CDSINIES,numoveco,NUMOVITO,CDREFCAB from bddlcru.ktom46t  ) d on
b.numoveco = D.numoveco
and D.FECONTAB >= '20190101'
inner join (select FEOPERA,TCCDMONE,FECHAEMI,CDSINIES,numoveco from bddlcru.KSIN30T  ) C on
b.CDSINIES = c.CDSINIES and b.numoveco = C.numoveco
inner join (select NUREFECA,CDCUENTA,CDSBANCO,numoveco from bddlcru.KTOM01T ) E on
b.numoveco = E.numoveco
LEFT  OUTER JOIN (SELECT cve_info,DESCRIPCION FROM bddlcru.cat_hom_146_bancos) Z ON
trim(E.CDSBANCO) =trim(Z.cve_info)

INNER join (select FEOPERA,TCCDMONE,FECHAEMI,CDSINIES,numoveco from bddlcru.KSIN30T ) C on

INNER join (select FECONTAB,CDSINIES,numoveco,NUMOVITO,CDREFCAB from bddlcru.ktom46t  ) d on
b.numoveco = D.numoveco
and D.FECONTAB >= '20190101'
INNER join (select NUREFECA,CDCUENTA,CDSBANCO,numoveco from bddlcru.KTOM01T ) E on
b.numoveco = E.numoveco
LEFT  OUTER JOIN (SELECT cve_info,DESCRIPCION FROM bddlcru.cat_hom_146_bancos) Z ON
trim(E.CDSBANCO) =trim(Z.cve_info)

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'

SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  BDDLTRN.DELTA_RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

LEFT JOIN
(	SELECT

FROM

FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_COMPROBANTE_delta
SELECT Z.*
FROM
(
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_COMPROBANTE           actual
INNER JOIN BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_COMPROBANTE_DELTA    stg ON
actual.idmd5         =   stg.idmd5
WHERE   NVL(actual.idmd5completo,'') <>  NVL(stg.idmd5completo,'')
UNION ALL

FROM    BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_COMPROBANTE_DELTA        stg
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLALM.ALM_COMPROBANTE actual ON
stg.idmd5 = actual.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5 IS NULL
) Z

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_COMPROBANTE_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_COMPROBANTE        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_COMPROBANTE_DELTA ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

ARA1.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl,
ARA1.pct_coaseguro_nacional,
ARA1.pct_coaseguro_internacional,
ARA1.ts_alta_hdfs
from
(
select
CSO.sistema,
ARA.num_reclamacion,
ARA.cve_sistema_int,
ARA.cve_sistema,
ARA.num_consecutivo_acumulado,
ARA.cve_tipo_mov_producido,
ARA.cve_estatus_acumulado,
ARA.cve_cobertura_afectada,
ARA.mto_suma_asegurada,
ARA.mto_suma_asegurada_pagada,
ARA.mto_suma_asegurada_remte,
ARA.cve_unidad_suma_asegurada,
ARA.mto_deducible_nacional,
ARA.mto_deducible_nacional_pagado,
ARA.mto_deducible_nacional_remte,
ARA.cve_unidad_deducible_nacional,
ARA.mto_deducible_internal,
ARA.mto_deducible_internal_pagado,
ARA.mto_deducible_internal_remte,
ARA.cve_unidad_deducible_internal,
ARA.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal,
ARA.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_pagado,
ARA.mto_tope_coaseguro_nal_remte,
ARA.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal,
ARA.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl,
ARA.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_pagado,
ARA.mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_remte,
ARA.cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_intl,
ARA.pct_coaseguro_nacional,
ARA.pct_coaseguro_internacional,
ARA.ts_alta_hdfs
from bddltrn.RECLAMACION_ACUMULADO ARA
LEFT JOIN
bddlcru.cat_sistema_origen CSO
on CSO.cve_sistema = ARA.cve_sistema_int
order by ARA.cve_sistema
) ARA1
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_sistema,sistema
from bddlcru.cat_sistema_origen
order by cve_sistema
)CSO1
ON 	ARA1.cve_sistema = CSO1.cve_sistema
WHERE 	ARA1.cve_sistema = 'INFO')INFO
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT
cve_homologada_dl as cve_cobertura_afectada1,
descr_larga_homologada_dl as descr_larga_cobertura_afectada ,
cve_origen_NZ
FROM bddlcru.CAT_COBERTURA_AFECTADA_DL
)CCAD
ON INFO.cve_cobertura_afectada = CCAD.cve_origen_NZ

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA
SELECT DISTINCT
NVL(ID_SOLICITUD,''),
NVL(CVE_SISTEMA_INT,''),
NVL(DES_SISTEMA_INT,''),
NVL(CVE_SISTEMA,''),
NVL(DES_SISTEMA,''),
NVL(CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,''),
NVL(DES_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,''),
NVL(NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,0),
NVL(CVE_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION,''),
NVL(DES_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION,''),
NVL(BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL,''),
NVL(DES_BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL,''),
NVL(CVE_PROCEDIMIENTO,''),
NVL(DES_PROCEDIMIENTO,''),
NVL(NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,0),
NVL(TOT_VECES_APLICA_PROCEDIMIENTO,0),
FCH_ATENCION,
NVL(TIPO_CPT, ''),
TRIM(NVL(CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO_TABULACION, '')),
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) TS_ALTA_HDFS,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', CONCAT(NVL(ID_SOLICITUD,''),'_', NVL(CAST(NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION AS STRING), '0'), '_', NVL(CAST(NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT AS STRING), '0'))) AS IDMD5,

FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA_CATALOGOS

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA_CATALOGOS
SELECT DISTINCT
PROCEDIMIENTO.ID_SOLICITUD,
PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
TRIM(SIST_INT.SISTEMA),
PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA,
TRIM(SIST.SISTEMA),
TRIM(SOLICITUD.CVE_ICD9),
TRIM(SOLICITUD.PADECIMIENTO_ICD9_ESP),
PROCEDIMIENTO.NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,
TRIM(COMPLICACION.CVE_ICD9),
TRIM(COMPLICACION.PADECIMIENTO_ICD9_ESP),
PROCEDIMIENTO.BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL,
CASE
WHEN TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL) = '1' THEN 'S'
WHEN TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL) = '0' THEN 'N'
ELSE '' END,
TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_PROCEDIMIENTO),
PROC.PROCEDIMIENTO_CPT,
PROCEDIMIENTO.NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,
PROCEDIMIENTO.TOT_VECES_APLICA_PROCEDIMIENTO,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO,
PROCEDIMIENTO.FECHA_ALTA,
PROCEDIMIENTO.FCH_ATENCION,
PROCEDIMIENTO.TIPO_CPT,
PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO_TABULACION
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA_UNION PROCEDIMIENTO
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN SIST_INT
ON PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = SIST_INT.CVE_SISTEMA
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN SIST
ON PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA = SIST.CVE_SISTEMA
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_PADECIMIENTO_ICD9 SOLICITUD
ON TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD) = TRIM(SOLICITUD.CVE_ICD9)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_PADECIMIENTO_ICD9 COMPLICACION
ON TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION) = TRIM(COMPLICACION.CVE_ICD9)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_PROCEDIMIENTO_CPT PROC
ON TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_PROCEDIMIENTO) = TRIM(PROC.CVE_CPT)

TRIM(SIST_INT.SISTEMA),
PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA,
TRIM(SIST.SISTEMA),
TRIM(SOLICITUD.CVE_ICD9),
TRIM(SOLICITUD.PADECIMIENTO_ICD9_ESP),
PROCEDIMIENTO.NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,
TRIM(COMPLICACION.CVE_ICD9),
TRIM(COMPLICACION.PADECIMIENTO_ICD9_ESP),
PROCEDIMIENTO.BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL,
CASE
WHEN TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL) = '1' THEN 'S'
WHEN TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL) = '0' THEN 'N'
ELSE '' END,
TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_PROCEDIMIENTO),
PROC.PROCEDIMIENTO_CPT,
PROCEDIMIENTO.NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,
PROCEDIMIENTO.TOT_VECES_APLICA_PROCEDIMIENTO,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO,
PROCEDIMIENTO.FECHA_ALTA,
PROCEDIMIENTO.FCH_ATENCION,
PROCEDIMIENTO.TIPO_CPT,
PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO_TABULACION
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA_UNION PROCEDIMIENTO
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN SIST_INT
ON PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA_INT = SIST_INT.CVE_SISTEMA
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN SIST
ON PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA = SIST.CVE_SISTEMA
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_PADECIMIENTO_ICD9 SOLICITUD
ON TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD) = TRIM(SOLICITUD.CVE_ICD9)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_PADECIMIENTO_ICD9 COMPLICACION
ON TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION) = TRIM(COMPLICACION.CVE_ICD9)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_PROCEDIMIENTO_CPT PROC
ON TRIM(PROCEDIMIENTO.CVE_PROCEDIMIENTO) = TRIM(PROC.CVE_CPT)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_NOTAS_MED_ADM_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_NOTAS_MED_ADM        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_NOTAS_MED_ADM_DELTA ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA_EXTRACCION_AZUL
SELECT DISTINCT
CAST(CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE AS STRING),2,'0'),NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE, LPAD(CAST(NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING),7,'0')) AS VARCHAR(11)),
CAST('AZUL' AS VARCHAR(4)),
CAST('RCLA' AS VARCHAR(4)),
COALESCE(SLR0.ICD_CVE, ''),
CMP0.CMP_NUM,
COALESCE(CMP0.CMP_ICD_CVE,''),
CAST(CASE WHEN CMP0.CMP_ICD_CVE IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS VARCHAR(1)),
NRLTTTA0.CVE_CPT AS CVE_PROCEDIMIENTO,
NRLTTTA0.TTA_NUM AS NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,
NRLTTTA0.TTA_CTD AS TOT_VECES_APLICA_PROCEDIMIENTO,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO,
NRLTTTA0.TTA_ACT AS FECHA_ALTA,
NRLTDIM0.DIM_FEC_DIC AS FCH_ATENCION,
NPMTTPRC.PRC_NOM_TIP AS TIPO_CPT,
NPMTTMDC.TMD_DES AS CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO_TABULACION
FROM BDDLCRU.NRLTTTA0 NRLTTTA0
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(DATE(TTA_ACT)) AS TTA_ACT FROM BDDLCRU.NRLTTTA0) AS DELTA
ON DATE(NRLTTTA0.TTA_ACT) = DELTA.TTA_ACT
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTSLR0 AS SLR0
ON NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE = SLR0.CEO_CVE AND TRIM(NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE) = TRIM(SLR0.MDA_CVE) AND NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL = SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTCMP0 AS CMP0
ON NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE = CMP0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE = CMP0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL = CMP0.SLR_NUM_FOL AND NRLTTTA0.CMP_NUM = CMP0.CMP_NUM
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NRLTDIM0 AS NRLTDIM0
ON NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE = NRLTDIM0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE = NRLTDIM0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL = NRLTDIM0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTCPTC AS NPMTCPTC
ON TRIM(NRLTTTA0.CVE_CPT) = TRIM(NPMTCPTC.CPT_CVE)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTTPRC AS NPMTTPRC
ON TRIM(NPMTCPTC.PRC_CVE) = TRIM(NPMTTPRC.PRC_CVE)
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CEO_CVE, MDA_CVE, SLR_NUM_FOL, CPT_CVE, TMD_CVE, TTA_NUM, CMP_NUM from BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTGTB0 WHERE TMD_CVE IS NOT NULL) AS LMP_NRLTGTB0
ON NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE = LMP_NRLTGTB0.CEO_CVE AND TRIM(NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE) = TRIM(LMP_NRLTGTB0.MDA_CVE) AND NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL = LMP_NRLTGTB0.SLR_NUM_FOL AND TRIM(NRLTTTA0.CVE_CPT) = TRIM(LMP_NRLTGTB0.CPT_CVE) AND NRLTTTA0.TTA_NUM = LMP_NRLTGTB0.TTA_NUM AND NRLTTTA0.CMP_NUM = LMP_NRLTGTB0.CMP_NUM
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTTMDC AS NPMTTMDC
ON LMP_NRLTGTB0.TMD_CVE = NPMTTMDC.TMD_CVE
WHERE CMP0.CMP_NUM IS NOT NULL

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA_EXTRACCION_AZUL
SELECT DISTINCT
CAST(CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE AS STRING),2,'0'),NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE, LPAD(CAST(NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING),7,'0')) AS VARCHAR(11)),

LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTTPRC AS NPMTTPRC
ON TRIM(NPMTCPTC.PRC_CVE) = TRIM(NPMTTPRC.PRC_CVE)
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CEO_CVE, MDA_CVE, SLR_NUM_FOL, CPT_CVE, TMD_CVE, TTA_NUM, CMP_NUM from BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTGTB0 WHERE TMD_CVE IS NOT NULL) AS LMP_NRLTGTB0
ON NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE = LMP_NRLTGTB0.CEO_CVE AND TRIM(NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE) = TRIM(LMP_NRLTGTB0.MDA_CVE) AND NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL = LMP_NRLTGTB0.SLR_NUM_FOL AND TRIM(NRLTTTA0.CVE_CPT) = TRIM(LMP_NRLTGTB0.CPT_CVE) AND NRLTTTA0.TTA_NUM = LMP_NRLTGTB0.TTA_NUM AND NRLTTTA0.CMP_NUM = LMP_NRLTGTB0.CMP_NUM
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTTMDC AS NPMTTMDC
ON LMP_NRLTGTB0.TMD_CVE = NPMTTMDC.TMD_CVE
WHERE CMP0.CMP_NUM IS NOT NULL

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA_EXTRACCION_AZUL
SELECT DISTINCT
CAST(CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE AS STRING),2,'0'),NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE, LPAD(CAST(NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING),7,'0')) AS VARCHAR(11)),
CAST('AZUL' AS VARCHAR(4)),
CAST('RCLA' AS VARCHAR(4)),
COALESCE(SLR0.ICD_CVE, ''),
CMP0.CMP_NUM,
COALESCE(CMP0.CMP_ICD_CVE,''),
CAST(CASE WHEN CMP0.CMP_ICD_CVE IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS VARCHAR(1)),
NRLTTTA0.CVE_CPT AS CVE_PROCEDIMIENTO,
NRLTTTA0.TTA_NUM AS NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,
NRLTTTA0.TTA_CTD AS TOT_VECES_APLICA_PROCEDIMIENTO,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO,
NRLTTTA0.TTA_ACT AS FECHA_ALTA,
NRLTDIM0.DIM_FEC_DIC AS FCH_ATENCION,
NPMTTPRC.PRC_NOM_TIP AS TIPO_CPT,
NPMTTMDC.TMD_DES AS CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO_TABULACION
FROM BDDLCRU.NRLTTTA0 NRLTTTA0
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(DATE(TTA_ACT)) AS TTA_ACT FROM BDDLCRU.NRLTTTA0) AS DELTA
ON DATE(NRLTTTA0.TTA_ACT) = DELTA.TTA_ACT
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTSLR0 AS SLR0
ON NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE = SLR0.CEO_CVE AND TRIM(NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE) = TRIM(SLR0.MDA_CVE) AND NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL = SLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTCMP0 AS CMP0
ON NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE = CMP0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE = CMP0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL = CMP0.SLR_NUM_FOL AND NRLTTTA0.CMP_NUM = CMP0.CMP_NUM
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NRLTDIM0 AS NRLTDIM0
ON NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE = NRLTDIM0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE = NRLTDIM0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL = NRLTDIM0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTCPTC AS NPMTCPTC
ON TRIM(NRLTTTA0.CVE_CPT) = TRIM(NPMTCPTC.CPT_CVE)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTTPRC AS NPMTTPRC
ON TRIM(NPMTCPTC.PRC_CVE) = TRIM(NPMTTPRC.PRC_CVE)
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CEO_CVE, MDA_CVE, SLR_NUM_FOL, CPT_CVE, TMD_CVE, TTA_NUM, CMP_NUM from BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTGTB0 WHERE TMD_CVE IS NOT NULL) AS LMP_NRLTGTB0
ON NRLTTTA0.CEO_CVE = LMP_NRLTGTB0.CEO_CVE AND TRIM(NRLTTTA0.MDA_CVE) = TRIM(LMP_NRLTGTB0.MDA_CVE) AND NRLTTTA0.SLR_NUM_FOL = LMP_NRLTGTB0.SLR_NUM_FOL AND TRIM(NRLTTTA0.CVE_CPT) = TRIM(LMP_NRLTGTB0.CPT_CVE) AND NRLTTTA0.TTA_NUM = LMP_NRLTGTB0.TTA_NUM AND NRLTTTA0.CMP_NUM = LMP_NRLTGTB0.CMP_NUM
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTTMDC AS NPMTTMDC
ON LMP_NRLTGTB0.TMD_CVE = NPMTTMDC.TMD_CVE
WHERE CMP0.CMP_NUM IS NOT NULL

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLINT.COMPROBANTE_RFC_PROVEEDOR
SELECT DISTINCT
CASE WHEN LOCATE('R', TRIM(STS.NUM_SOLICITUD), 1) = 0 THEN TRIM(STS.NUM_SOLICITUD) ELSE SUBSTRING(TRIM(STS.NUM_SOLICITUD),1,LOCATE('R', TRIM(STS.NUM_SOLICITUD), 1) -1) END AS FOLIO_SOLICITUD
,TRIM(STS.NUM_SOLICITUD) AS NUM_SOLICITUD, TRIM(STS.NUM_RECLAMACION) AS NUM_RECLAMACION, STS.ID_TRANSACCION
,SCSM.FOLIO_SOLICITUD_MEDICA, UPPER(SCSM.ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL) AS ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL
,TRIM(BCF.FOLIO_INTERNO_COMPROBANTE) AS FOLIO_INTERNO_COMPROBANTE, BCF.MTO_TOTAL_CFD, BCF.TS_EXPEDICION_CFD, TRIM(BCF.RFC_EMISOR) AS rfc_proveedor, BCF.RAZON_SOCIAL_EMISOR_FACTURA, TRIM(BCF.RFC_RECEPTOR) AS RFC_RECEPTOR, BCF.RAZON_SOCIAL_RECEPTOR_FACTURA
FROM BDDLCRU.SIN_TRAMITE_SINIESTRO STS
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.SIN_COMPROBANTE_SOLICITUD_MEDICA SCSM
ON STS.ID_TRANSACCION = SCSM.FOLIO_SOLICITUD_MEDICA
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT UPPER(ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL) AS ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL
,FOLIO_INTERNO_COMPROBANTE, MTO_TOTAL_CFD, TS_EXPEDICION_CFD, RFC_EMISOR, RAZON_SOCIAL_EMISOR_FACTURA, RFC_RECEPTOR, RAZON_SOCIAL_RECEPTOR_FACTURA
,RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY UPPER(ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL), FOLIO_INTERNO_COMPROBANTE ORDER BY TS_ALTA_AUDIT DESC) AS RNK_RFC
FROM BDDLCRU.BUF_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL
) BCF
ON BCF.RNK_RFC = 1
AND UPPER(SCSM.ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL) = BCF.ID_COMPROBANTE_FISCAL
WHERE TRIM(STS.CVE_TIPO_TRANSACCION) = '8'

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_NOTAS_MED_ADM_DELTA_INFO
SELECT
SOLICITUD.ID_SOLICITUD,
SOLICITUD.CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
SOLICITUD.CVE_SISTEMA,
CHT.CDTINOV1,
TRIM(REGEXP_REPLACE(COALESCE(TRIM(CTT5.DSCORTAM),''), '([^a-zA-Z0-9*!@+-/#$%()_=/<>?\|&\\s]|\\t|\\r|\\n|\\u0001|)', '')) AS DSCORTAM,
ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY CHT.CDCODFUN ORDER BY CHT.TSULTMOD ASC) AS NUMERO_CONSEG,
TRIM(REGEXP_REPLACE(COALESCE(TRIM(CTT5.TXAVISO),''), '([^a-zA-Z0-9*!@+-/#$%()_=/<>?\|&\\s]|\\t|\\r|\\n|\\u0001|)', ''))  AS DETALLE,

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_PROCEDIMIENTO_DELTA_EXTRACCION_INFO
SELECT DISTINCT
CAST(KACM52T.CDSINIES AS VARCHAR(11)),
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR(4)),
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR(4)),
CASE WHEN 51T.INPRINCI = 'N' THEN '' ELSE COALESCE(51T.TCCDICD,'') END AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(KACM52T.CTNUICD,-999) AS NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,
CASE WHEN 51T.INPRINCI = 'N' THEN '' ELSE COALESCE(51T.TCCDICD,'') END AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION,
CAST(CASE WHEN 51T.INPRINCI = 'N' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS VARCHAR(1)) AS BAN_PAD_PRINCIPAL, NVL(KACM52T.TCCDCPT, '') AS CVE_PROCEDIMIENTO,
KACM52T.CTNUCPT AS NUM_CONS_PROCEDIMIENTO_AUT,
KACM52T.NUUNIDAD AS TOT_VECES_APLICA_PROCEDIMIENTO,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5, CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO,
KACM52T.TSULTMOD,
CASE WHEN KACM52T.FEATENCI IS NULL THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(KACM52T.FEATENCI AS STRING), 1, 4), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(KACM52T.FEATENCI AS STRING), 5, 2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(KACM52T.FEATENCI AS STRING), 7, 2))), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) AS TIMESTAMP) END AS FCH_ATENCION,
PRC.PRC_NOM_TIP AS TIPO_CPT,
KACM52T.TCCDCMED AS CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO_TABULACION
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM52T KACM52T
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(DATE(TSULTMOD)) AS TSULTMOD FROM BDDLCRU.KACM52T) AS DELTA
ON DATE(KACM52T.TSULTMOD) = DELTA.TSULTMOD
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KSIA12T KSIA12T
ON KACM52T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN  BDDLCRU.KACM51T 51T
ON KACM52T.CDSINIES = 51T.CDSINIES AND KACM52T.CTNUPOIN = 51T.CTNUPOIN AND KACM52T.CTNUICD = 51T.CTNUICD
LEFT JOIN BDDLDES.NPMTCPTC PTC ON TRIM(KACM52T.TCCDCPT) = TRIM(PTC.CPT_CVE)
LEFT JOIN BDDLDES.NPMTTPRC PRC ON TRIM(PTC.PRC_CVE) = TRIM(PRC.PRC_CVE)
WHERE 51T.INPRINCI != 'N' AND 51T.INPRINCI IS NOT NULL

ON KACM52T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN  BDDLCRU.KACM51T 51T
ON KACM52T.CDSINIES = 51T.CDSINIES AND KACM52T.CTNUPOIN = 51T.CTNUPOIN AND KACM52T.CTNUICD = 51T.CTNUICD
LEFT JOIN BDDLDES.NPMTCPTC PTC ON TRIM(KACM52T.TCCDCPT) = TRIM(PTC.CPT_CVE)
LEFT JOIN BDDLDES.NPMTTPRC PRC ON TRIM(PTC.PRC_CVE) = TRIM(PRC.PRC_CVE)
WHERE 51T.INPRINCI != 'N' AND 51T.INPRINCI IS NOT NULL

'AZUL' 					 AS cve_sistema_int,

AUR1.AUR_DED_NAL_UNI     AS cve_unidad_deducible_nacional,
AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT         AS mto_deducible_internal,
AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT_ACU     AS mto_deducible_internal_pagado,
IF(AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT = -1,-1,IF(AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT_ACU > AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT,0,AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT - AUR1.AUR_DED_EXT_ACU))AS mto_deducible_internal_remte,

AUR1.AUR_UNI_LIM_COA     AS cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_nal,
AUR1.AUR_LIM_COA_VAL_EXT AS mto_tope_coaseguro_intl,
AUR1.AUR_COA_ACU_EXT     AS mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_pagado,
IF(AUR1.AUR_LIM_COA_VAL_EXT = -1,-1,IF(AUR1.AUR_COA_ACU_EXT > AUR1.AUR_LIM_COA_VAL_EXT,0,AUR1.AUR_LIM_COA_VAL_EXT - AUR1.AUR_COA_ACU_EXT)) AS mto_tope_coaseguro_intl_remte,
AUR1.AUR_UNI_LIM_COA_EXT AS cve_unidad_tope_coaseguro_inl,
AUR_COA_CNR/100          AS pct_coaseguro_nacional,
AUR_COA_CNR_EXT/100      AS pct_coaseguro_internacional,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS ts_alta_hdfs
From
(
SELECT
RCL0.rcl_num,
RCL0.rcl_org
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTRCL0 RCL0
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(fechaaud) AS fechaaud FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTRCL0) AS T2

) AS RCL01
INNER JOIN
(
SELECT
AUR.rlc_num ,
AUR.cob_cve,
AUR.aur_sum_cnr,
AUR.aur_uni_sum,
AUR.aur_sum_ejr,
AUR.aur_ded_nal,
AUR.aur_ded_nal_uni,
AUR.aur_ded_nal_acu,
AUR.aur_ded_ext,
AUR.aur_ded_ext_uni,
AUR.aur_ded_ext_acu,
AUR.aur_lim_coa_val,
AUR.aur_uni_lim_coa,
AUR.aur_coa_acu,
AUR.aur_coa_cnr,
AUR.aur_cns,
AUR.aur_ess_acu_inf,
AUR.aur_lim_coa_val_ext,
AUR.aur_uni_lim_coa_ext,
AUR.aur_coa_acu_ext,
AUR.aur_coa_cnr_ext
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTAUR0 AUR
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(fechaaud) AS fechaaud FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTAUR0) AS T2
ON TO_DATE(T2.fechaaud) = TO_DATE(AUR.fechaaud)
) AS AUR1
ON RCL01.rcl_num = AUR1.rlc_num

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_NOTAS_MED_ADM_DELTA_RCLA
SELECT DISTINCT
ENR.ID_SOLICITUD,
ENR.CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
ENR.CVE_SISTEMA,
NRLTNOT0.NOT_TIP,
IF(TRIM(NRLTNOT0.NOT_TIP) = 'AD', 'Administrativa', IF(TRIM(NRLTNOT0.NOT_TIP) = 'ME', 'Medica', IF(TRIM(NRLTNOT0.NOT_TIP) = 'OT', 'Otra', ''))),
NRLTNOT0.NOT_NUM,
TRIM(REGEXP_REPLACE(COALESCE(TRIM(NRLTNOT0.NOT_TEX),''), '([^a-zA-Z0-9*!@+-/#$%()_=/<>?\|&\\s]|\\t|\\r|\\n|\\v|\\b|\\u0001|)', '')) NOT_TEXT,
TRIM(NRLTNOT0.USU_CVE),
CONCAT(TRIM(NRLTUSU0.USU_NOM), ' ', TRIM(NRLTUSU0.USU_APE_PAT), ' ',TRIM(NRLTUSU0.USU_APE_MAT)),
CASE WHEN NRLTNOT0.NOT_FEC_HOR = 0 OR NRLTNOT0.NOT_FEC_HOR IS NULL THEN CAST(FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE CAST( CAST ( CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(NRLTNOT0.NOT_FEC_HOR AS STRING), 7, 4), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(NRLTNOT0.NOT_FEC_HOR AS STRING), 1, 2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(NRLTNOT0.NOT_FEC_HOR AS STRING), 4, 2)) AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP) END,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()),
'',
''
FROM BDDLENR.ENR_SOLICITUD AS ENR
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(ts_alta_hdfs) AS ts_alta_hdfs FROM BDDLENR.ENR_SOLICITUD) AS T2 ON TO_DATE(T2.ts_alta_hdfs) = TO_DATE(ENR.ts_alta_hdfs)
JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTNOT0 AS NRLTNOT0
ON TRIM(ENR.CVE_MODALIDAD) = TRIM(NRLTNOT0.MDA_CVE) AND ENR.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL = CAST(NRLTNOT0.CEO_CVE AS SMALLINT) AND TRIM(ENR.FOLIO_SOLICITUD) = CAST(NRLTNOT0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING)
JOIN BDDLCRU.NRLTUSU0 AS NRLTUSU0
ON TRIM(NRLTNOT0.USU_CVE) = TRIM(NRLTUSU0.USU_CVE)
WHERE CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'AZUL'

''
FROM BDDLENR.ENR_SOLICITUD AS ENR
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(ts_alta_hdfs) AS ts_alta_hdfs FROM BDDLENR.ENR_SOLICITUD) AS T2 ON TO_DATE(T2.ts_alta_hdfs) = TO_DATE(ENR.ts_alta_hdfs)
JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTNOT0 AS NRLTNOT0
ON TRIM(ENR.CVE_MODALIDAD) = TRIM(NRLTNOT0.MDA_CVE) AND ENR.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL = CAST(NRLTNOT0.CEO_CVE AS SMALLINT) AND TRIM(ENR.FOLIO_SOLICITUD) = CAST(NRLTNOT0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING)
JOIN BDDLCRU.NRLTUSU0 AS NRLTUSU0
ON TRIM(NRLTNOT0.USU_CVE) = TRIM(NRLTUSU0.USU_CVE)
WHERE CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'AZUL'

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_NOTAS_MED_ADM_DELTA_RCLA
SELECT DISTINCT
ENR.ID_SOLICITUD,
ENR.CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
ENR.CVE_SISTEMA,
NRLTNOT0.NOT_TIP,
IF(TRIM(NRLTNOT0.NOT_TIP) = 'AD', 'Administrativa', IF(TRIM(NRLTNOT0.NOT_TIP) = 'ME', 'Medica', IF(TRIM(NRLTNOT0.NOT_TIP) = 'OT', 'Otra', ''))),
NRLTNOT0.NOT_NUM,
TRIM(REGEXP_REPLACE(COALESCE(TRIM(NRLTNOT0.NOT_TEX),''), '([^a-zA-Z0-9*!@+-/#$%()_=/<>?\|&\\s]|\\t|\\r|\\n|\\v|\\b|\\u0001|)', '')) NOT_TEXT,
TRIM(NRLTNOT0.USU_CVE),
CONCAT(TRIM(NRLTUSU0.USU_NOM), ' ', TRIM(NRLTUSU0.USU_APE_PAT), ' ',TRIM(NRLTUSU0.USU_APE_MAT)),
CASE WHEN NRLTNOT0.NOT_FEC_HOR = 0 OR NRLTNOT0.NOT_FEC_HOR IS NULL THEN CAST(FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE CAST( CAST ( CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(NRLTNOT0.NOT_FEC_HOR AS STRING), 7, 4), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(NRLTNOT0.NOT_FEC_HOR AS STRING), 1, 2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(NRLTNOT0.NOT_FEC_HOR AS STRING), 4, 2)) AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP) END,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()),
'',
''
FROM BDDLENR.ENR_SOLICITUD AS ENR
INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(ts_alta_hdfs) AS ts_alta_hdfs FROM BDDLENR.ENR_SOLICITUD) AS T2 ON TO_DATE(T2.ts_alta_hdfs) = TO_DATE(ENR.ts_alta_hdfs)
JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTNOT0 AS NRLTNOT0
ON TRIM(ENR.CVE_MODALIDAD) = TRIM(NRLTNOT0.MDA_CVE) AND ENR.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL = CAST(NRLTNOT0.CEO_CVE AS SMALLINT) AND TRIM(ENR.FOLIO_SOLICITUD) = CAST(NRLTNOT0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING)
JOIN BDDLCRU.NRLTUSU0 AS NRLTUSU0
ON TRIM(NRLTNOT0.USU_CVE) = TRIM(NRLTUSU0.USU_CVE)
WHERE CVE_SISTEMA_INT = 'AZUL'

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_alm_recibo_con_cambios

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_delta
SELECT
CAST(NVL(pol.cve_folio_agente_1,'') AS VARCHAR(10))				AS  cve_folio_agente_1,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(10))                                       	AS  cve_folio_agente_2,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(10))                                       	AS  cve_folio_agente_3,
CAST(NVL(RTRIM(cat.cve_canal_cobro), '') AS VARCHAR(20))		AS 	cve_canal_cobro,
CAST(NVL(ban.cdbanco,'') 			AS VARCHAR( 4))				AS  cve_banco,
CAST(NVL(mc.cve_medio_cobro,'') 	AS VARCHAR( 3))				AS	cve_medio_cobro,
CAST(NVL(mc.descr_medio_cobro,'') 	AS VARCHAR(30))				AS 	descr_medio_cobro,
pol.cve_cobertura_contable                                      AS  cve_cobertura_contable,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_estado_recibo_anterior, '') AS VARCHAR(13))    AS  cve_estado_recibo_anterior,
cat.descr_estado_recibo_anterior,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_estado_recibo, '') AS varchar(1))				AS  cve_estado_recibo,
cat.descr_estado_recibo,
CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP)                                         AS  fch_cambio_estado,
rec.fch_emision,
rec.fch_inicio_vigencia_recibo,
CAST(
NVL(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento AS STRING), 1,4), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento    AS STRING), 5,2), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento    AS STRING), 7,2),
' 00:00:00'), '1400-01-01 00:00:00.000')
AS TIMESTAMP)                                               AS  fch_movimiento,
CAST(
NVL(CASE
WHEN rec.cve_estado_recibo = 'L'   AND fch_p.fch_pago > 0
THEN
CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago AS STRING), 1,4), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago    AS STRING), 5,2), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago    AS STRING), 7,2),
' 00:00:00')
ELSE NULL
END, '1400-01-01 00:00:00.000')
AS TIMESTAMP)                                               AS  fch_pago,
rec.fch_fin_vigencia_recibo,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_forma_pago, '') 	AS VARCHAR( 1))				AS  cve_forma_pago,
CAST(NVL(cat.descr_forma_pago, '') 	AS VARCHAR(30))				AS  descr_forma_pago,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision_recargo,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision_derecho_poliza,
CAST(0 AS DECIMAL(13,2))                                        AS  mto_descuento_volumen,
CAST(imp.iva        AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_iva,
CAST(imp.recargos   AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_recargo,
CAST(imp.derechos   AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_derecho_poliza,
CAST(imp.prima_neta AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_prima_neta,
rec.mto_total_pago,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision, '')   	AS 	VARCHAR( 1))  	AS	cve_ind_nivel_emision,
CAST(NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision, '') 	AS 	VARCHAR(15)) 	AS	descr_ind_nivel_emision,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento, '') 	AS 	VARCHAR( 1)) 	AS	cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,
CAST(NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento, '') AS 	VARCHAR(15)) 	AS descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,
CAST(''   AS VARCHAR(6))                                        AS  num_endoso,
rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza,
rec.num_poliza,
rec.num_recibo,
CAST(''   AS VARCHAR(8))                                        AS  num_poliza_cobranza,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_comision,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_1,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_2,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_3,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_prima_total,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_tipo_transaccion, '') 	 AS	VARCHAR( 2))		AS	cve_tipo_transaccion,
CAST(NVL(cat.descr_tipo_transaccion, '') AS	VARCHAR(40)) 		AS	descr_tipo_transaccion,
rec.num_version_poliza,
rec.vigencia_poliza,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR( 4))                                     AS  cve_sistema,
CAST(NULL   AS VARCHAR( 4))                                     AS  cve_sistema_int,
CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP)              AS  fechaaud,
rec.ori_registro,
rec.fechaaud_registro,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex', CAST(rec.num_recibo AS STRING)) AS idmd5,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
CONCAT(NVL(pol.cve_folio_agente_1,'')
, NVL(cat.cve_canal_cobro,''), NVL(ban.CDBANCO,''), NVL(cve_medio_cobro,''), NVL(descr_medio_cobro,''), cve_cobertura_contable
, NVL(cve_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cve_estado_recibo,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo,'')
, NVL(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_forma_pago,''), NVL(cat.descr_forma_pago,'')
, NVL(CAST(imp.iva AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.recargos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.derechos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.prima_neta AS STRING),'')
, NVL(CAST(rec.mto_total_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,'')
, NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,''), NVL(CAST(rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza AS STRING),''), rec.num_poliza, NVL(rec.num_recibo,'')
, NVL(rec.cve_tipo_transaccion,''), NVL(cat.descr_tipo_transaccion,''), rec.num_version_poliza, rec.vigencia_poliza
))                                                      AS idmd5completo
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info rec
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_poliza pol ON
rec.num_poliza          = pol.num_poliza
AND rec.num_version_poliza  = pol.num_version_poliza
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_importe imp ON
rec.num_recibo = imp.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_n50 AS n50  ON
rec.num_recibo = n50.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_medio_cobro mc ON
rec.num_recibo = mc.num_recibo
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco ban ON
rec.num_recibo          = ban.num_recibo
AND rec.tccancob            = 'BC'
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_fch_pago fch_p ON
rec.num_recibo = fch_p.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_catalogos cat ON
rec.num_recibo = cat.num_recibo

CAST('' AS VARCHAR(10))                                       	AS  cve_folio_agente_3,
CAST(NVL(RTRIM(cat.cve_canal_cobro), '') AS VARCHAR(20))		AS 	cve_canal_cobro,
CAST(NVL(ban.cdbanco,'') 			AS VARCHAR( 4))				AS  cve_banco,
CAST(NVL(mc.cve_medio_cobro,'') 	AS VARCHAR( 3))				AS	cve_medio_cobro,
CAST(NVL(mc.descr_medio_cobro,'') 	AS VARCHAR(30))				AS 	descr_medio_cobro,
pol.cve_cobertura_contable                                      AS  cve_cobertura_contable,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_estado_recibo_anterior, '') AS VARCHAR(13))    AS  cve_estado_recibo_anterior,
cat.descr_estado_recibo_anterior,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_estado_recibo, '') AS varchar(1))				AS  cve_estado_recibo,
cat.descr_estado_recibo,
CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP)                                         AS  fch_cambio_estado,
rec.fch_emision,
rec.fch_inicio_vigencia_recibo,
CAST(
NVL(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento AS STRING), 1,4), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento    AS STRING), 5,2), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento    AS STRING), 7,2),
' 00:00:00'), '1400-01-01 00:00:00.000')
AS TIMESTAMP)                                               AS  fch_movimiento,
CAST(
NVL(CASE
WHEN rec.cve_estado_recibo = 'L'   AND fch_p.fch_pago > 0
THEN
CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago AS STRING), 1,4), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago    AS STRING), 5,2), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago    AS STRING), 7,2),
' 00:00:00')
ELSE NULL
END, '1400-01-01 00:00:00.000')
AS TIMESTAMP)                                               AS  fch_pago,
rec.fch_fin_vigencia_recibo,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_forma_pago, '') 	AS VARCHAR( 1))				AS  cve_forma_pago,
CAST(NVL(cat.descr_forma_pago, '') 	AS VARCHAR(30))				AS  descr_forma_pago,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision_recargo,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision_derecho_poliza,
CAST(0 AS DECIMAL(13,2))                                        AS  mto_descuento_volumen,
CAST(imp.iva        AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_iva,
CAST(imp.recargos   AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_recargo,
CAST(imp.derechos   AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_derecho_poliza,
CAST(imp.prima_neta AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_prima_neta,
rec.mto_total_pago,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision, '')   	AS 	VARCHAR( 1))  	AS	cve_ind_nivel_emision,
CAST(NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision, '') 	AS 	VARCHAR(15)) 	AS	descr_ind_nivel_emision,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento, '') 	AS 	VARCHAR( 1)) 	AS	cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,
CAST(NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento, '') AS 	VARCHAR(15)) 	AS descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,
CAST(''   AS VARCHAR(6))                                        AS  num_endoso,
rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza,
rec.num_poliza,
rec.num_recibo,
CAST(''   AS VARCHAR(8))                                        AS  num_poliza_cobranza,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_comision,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_1,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_2,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_3,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_prima_total,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_tipo_transaccion, '') 	 AS	VARCHAR( 2))		AS	cve_tipo_transaccion,
CAST(NVL(cat.descr_tipo_transaccion, '') AS	VARCHAR(40)) 		AS	descr_tipo_transaccion,
rec.num_version_poliza,
rec.vigencia_poliza,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR( 4))                                     AS  cve_sistema,
CAST(NULL   AS VARCHAR( 4))                                     AS  cve_sistema_int,
CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP)              AS  fechaaud,
rec.ori_registro,
rec.fechaaud_registro,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex', CAST(rec.num_recibo AS STRING)) AS idmd5,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
CONCAT(NVL(pol.cve_folio_agente_1,'')
, NVL(cat.cve_canal_cobro,''), NVL(ban.CDBANCO,''), NVL(cve_medio_cobro,''), NVL(descr_medio_cobro,''), cve_cobertura_contable
, NVL(cve_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cve_estado_recibo,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo,'')
, NVL(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_forma_pago,''), NVL(cat.descr_forma_pago,'')
, NVL(CAST(imp.iva AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.recargos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.derechos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.prima_neta AS STRING),'')
, NVL(CAST(rec.mto_total_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,'')
, NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,''), NVL(CAST(rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza AS STRING),''), rec.num_poliza, NVL(rec.num_recibo,'')
, NVL(rec.cve_tipo_transaccion,''), NVL(cat.descr_tipo_transaccion,''), rec.num_version_poliza, rec.vigencia_poliza
))                                                      AS idmd5completo
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info rec
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_poliza pol ON
rec.num_poliza          = pol.num_poliza
AND rec.num_version_poliza  = pol.num_version_poliza
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_importe imp ON
rec.num_recibo = imp.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_n50 AS n50  ON
rec.num_recibo = n50.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_medio_cobro mc ON
rec.num_recibo = mc.num_recibo
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco ban ON
rec.num_recibo          = ban.num_recibo
AND rec.tccancob            = 'BC'
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_fch_pago fch_p ON
rec.num_recibo = fch_p.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_catalogos cat ON
rec.num_recibo = cat.num_recibo

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_CNM_PRIMA_EMITIDA_POLIZA_ENDOSO_DLT AS
SELECT
CASE WHEN anio_mes_contable=0 THEN 140001 ELSE anio_mes_contable END AS anio_mes_contable,
CASE WHEN fch_contable IS NULL THEN CAST("1400-01-01 00:00:00" AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE fch_contable END AS fch_contable,
num_poliza,
vigencia_poliza,
num_version_poliza,
num_poliza_cobranza,
num_endoso,
forma_pago,
cve_tipo_endoso,
mto_prima_tecnica,
mto_recargo_descuento,
mto_prima_neta,
mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
pct_pago_prima,
mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
mto_derecho_poliza,
mto_cesion_comision,
mto_iva_poliza,
mto_prima_total,
cve_cobertura_contable,
CASE WHEN fch_emision IS NULL THEN CAST("1400-01-01 00:00:00" AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE fch_emision END AS fch_emision,
NVL(segmento, '') AS segmento,
NVL(desc_segmento, '') AS desc_segmento,
NVL(negocio, '') AS negocio,
NVL(desc_negocio, '') AS desc_negocio,
NVL(bonos, '') AS bonos,
NVL(desc_bonos, '') AS desc_bonos,
NVL(plan_incentivos, '') AS plan_incentivos,
NVL(pol_contr, '') AS pol_contr,
NVL(desc_pol_contr, '') AS desc_pol_contr,
NVL(contrb, '') AS contrb,
NVL(pol_prest, '') AS pol_prest,
NVL(desc_pol_prest, '') AS desc_pol_prest,
NVL(mot_exc, '') AS mot_exc,
NVL(desc_mot_exc, '') AS desc_mot_exc,
cve_canal_venta_alterno,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(NVL(num_poliza,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''))) AS idmd5,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(
NVL(num_poliza,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''),
NVL(forma_pago,'') ,NVL(cve_tipo_endoso,''),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_tecnica AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_descuento AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_neta AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_cesion_comision AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(pct_pago_prima AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_derecho_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_iva_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_total AS INT),0) AS STRING),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contable,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(anio_mes_contable AS INT),0) AS STRING))) as idmd5completo,
from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS FECHAAUD,
cve_sistema_int
FROM(
select * from  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_DLT
) AS STG_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA
ORDER BY fch_contable,num_poliza,num_version_poliza, cve_sistema_int

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_INFO_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA as
SELECT
CAST(anio_mes_contable AS INT) AS anio_mes_contable ,
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(fecha_contable,1,4),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_contable,5,2),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_contable,7,2)," 00:00:00") AS timestamp) as fch_contable ,
CAST (num_poliza as varchar(14)) as num_poliza ,
CAST (indicador_vigencia as int) as vigencia_poliza,
CAST (num_version_poliza as int) as num_version_poliza  ,
CAST ('' as varchar(8)) as num_poliza_cobranza  ,
CAST ('' as varchar(6)) as num_endoso  ,
CAST (forma_pago as String) as forma_pago,
CAST ('' as varchar(3)) as cve_tipo_endoso,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_tecnica) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_tecnica,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_descuento) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_descuento,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_neta)AS DECIMAL(20,6))  as mto_prima_neta,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado)AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
CAST (pct_pago_prima AS DECIMAL(11,6)) as pct_pago_prima ,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
CAST (SUM(mto_derecho_poliza) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_derecho_poliza,
CAST (SUM(mto_cesion_comision) AS DECIMAL(20,6))  as mto_cesion_comision,
CAST (SUM(mto_iva_poliza) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_iva_poliza,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_total) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_total,
CAST(SUBSTR (cve_cobertura_contable,2,3) as varchar(3)) as cve_cobertura_contable,
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(fecha_emision,1,4),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_emision,5,2),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_emision,7,2)) AS timestamp) as fch_emision,
CAST(segmento AS VARCHAR(300)) AS segmento,
CAST(desc_segmento AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_segmento,
CAST(negocio AS VARCHAR(300)) AS negocio,
CAST(desc_negocio AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_negocio,
CAST(bonos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS bonos,
CAST(desc_bonos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_bonos,
CAST(plan_incentivos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS plan_incentivos,
CAST(pol_contr AS VARCHAR(300)) AS pol_contr,
CAST(desc_pol_contr AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_pol_contr,
CAST(contrb AS VARCHAR(300)) AS contrb,
CAST(pol_prest AS VARCHAR(300)) AS pol_prest,
CAST(desc_pol_prest AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_pol_prest,
CAST(mot_exc AS VARCHAR(300)) AS mot_exc,
CAST(desc_mot_exc AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_mot_exc,
'' as cve_canal_venta_alterno,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO,
CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS fechaaud,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR(10)) AS cve_sistema_int
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_IMPORTE_FILTER  as importe
group by num_poliza,
num_version_poliza,
anio_mes_contable,
cve_cobertura_contable,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
indicador_vigencia,
fecha_contable,
forma_pago,
fecha_emision,
pct_pago_prima
ORDER BY  fch_contable,cve_sistema_int,num_poliza,num_version_poliza

INSERT  OVERWRITE   TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco
SELECT rec.num_recibo,
CAST(
CASE WHEN rec.tccancob = 'BC' AND rec.cve_estado_recibo = 'L'
THEN TRIM(SUBSTR(ban.CDBANCO, 2,3))
ELSE ''
END
AS VARCHAR(4))                              AS  cve_banco
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info rec
LEFT OUTER JOIN
bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco ban
ON      rec.num_recibo   = ban.num_recibo

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_IMPORTE_FILTER as
SELECT
substr(CAST(FECONTAB AS string),1,6) as anio_mes_contable,
CAST(FECONTAB as String) as fecha_contable,
CDNUMPOL as num_poliza,
CTVRSPOL as num_version_poliza,
INANCACO as indicador_vigencia,
CDMCT as cobertura_contable,
CDOBJTP as objeto_codigo,
CTSECOBJ as objeto_secuencia,
TCFORPAG as forma_pago,
SIGNO * PRTECNICA as mto_prima_tecnica,
SIGNO * (PRNETA - PRTECNICA)   as mto_recargo_descuento,
SIGNO * PRNETA  as mto_prima_neta,
SIGNO * (IMREFRAC1 + IMREFRAC2) as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
PORCNFP as pct_pago_prima,
SIGNO * PRNETANFP as mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
CASE WHEN PORCNFP > 0 THEN SIGNO * (PRNETA  - PRNETANFP) else (SIGNO * PRNETA)  END as mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
SIGNO * IMDERPOL as mto_derecho_poliza,
-1 * SIGNO * PRCEDIDA as mto_cesion_comision,
SIGNO * (IMIVA + GAIVA )as mto_iva_poliza,
SIGNO * (PRNETA - PRCEDIDA +IMREFRAC1 + IMREFRAC2 + IMDERPOL + IMIVA + GAIVA) as mto_prima_total,
CDRAMDGS as cve_cobertura_contable,
nvl(segmento,'') as segmento,
nvl(desc_segmento,'') as desc_segmento,
nvl(negocio,'') as negocio,
nvl(desc_negocio,'') as desc_negocio,
nvl(bonos,'') as bonos,
nvl(desc_bonos,'') as desc_bonos,
nvl(plan_incentivos,'') as plan_incentivos,
nvl(pol_contr,'') as pol_contr,
nvl(desc_pol_contr,'') as desc_pol_contr,
nvl(contrb,0) as contrb,
nvl(pol_prest,'') as pol_prest,
nvl(desc_pol_prest,'') as desc_pol_prest,
nvl(mot_exc,'') as mot_exc,
nvl(desc_mot_exc,'') as desc_mot_exc,
CAST(FEMISION as String) AS fecha_emision
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_KTOM41T_FILTER  as ktom41t
order by fecha_contable, num_poliza,num_version_poliza

INSERT  OVERWRITE   TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco1

FROM bddlcru.ktom13t m13

FROM bddlcru.ktoa13t rmc

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_KTOM41T_FILTER AS
SELECT
ktom41t.CDNUMPOL,
ktom41t.CTVRSPOL,
ktom41t.CDRAMDGS,
kcim06t.INANCACO,
catalogo.DSFORPAG as TCFORPAG,
ktom41t.cdmct,
ktom41t.cdobjtp,
ktom41t.ctsecobj,
case when ktom41t.TCCOPERA= '003' then  -1 else  1 end as SIGNO,
ktom41t.impcec01 as PRTECNICA ,
ktom41t.impcec02 as PRCEDIDA,
ktom41t.impcec03 as IMREFRAC1,
ktom41t.impcec04 as IMDERPOL,
ktom41t.impcec05 as IMIVA ,
ktom41t.impcec06 as GAIVA ,
ktom41t.impcec07 as IMREFRAC2,
ktom41t.Impcec19 as PRNETA ,
ktom41t.impcec20 as PRTOTAL ,
KCIM16T.IMCAAP15 as PORCNFP,
(IMPCEC19 * (KCIM16T.IMCAAP15 / 100)) AS  PRNETANFP,
CASE WHEN (KCIM06T.FEMISION=0 OR KCIM06T.FEMISION IS NULL ) THEN 14000101 ELSE KCIM06T.FEMISION END AS FEMISION,
CASE WHEN FECONTAB<14000101 THEN 14000101 ELSE FECONTAB END AS FECONTAB,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDETISEG AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS SEGMENTO,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETSEG.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_segmento,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDNEGMUL AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS NEGOCIO,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETMUL.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_negocio,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.CDTIPBON AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS BONOS,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETBON.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_bonos,
CASE WHEN (KCIM06T.INPOLPAI = 'N') THEN 'True' ELSE 'False' END AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.INPOLCON AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS POL_CONTR,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETPCO.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_pol_contr,
CAST(gmmep.PORCONTR AS INT) AS CONTRB,
CAST(NVL(CAST(gmmep.INPOLPRE AS STRING), '')AS STRING) AS POL_PREST,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETPPR.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_pol_prest,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KCIM06T.INPOLPAI AS STRING), '')AS STRING)  AS MOT_EXC,
CAST(NVL(CAST(KTCTGETMOT.dselemen AS STRING), '')AS STRING) as desc_mot_exc
FROM (SELECT * FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_KTOM41  ) as ktom41t
INNER JOIN
(SELECT distinct CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL, INANCACO, TCFORPAG,FEMISION, INPOLPAI
FROM bddlcru.kcim06t WHERE cdciagru='SA' and cdprodte like 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT distinct CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL, INANCACO, TCFORPAG,FEMISION, INPOLPAI
FROM bddlcru.kcim06H WHERE cdciagru='SA' and cdprodte like 'G%'
) AS KCIM06T
ON KTOM41T.cdnumpol=KCIM06T.cdnumpol
AND KTOM41T.ctvrspol=KCIM06T.ctvrspol
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT trim(CDELEMEN) AS CDFORPAG, TRIM(SUBSTR(DSELEMEN,1,30)) AS DSFORPAG
FROM bddlcru.KTCTGET WHERE trim(CDTABLA)='KCIT27S' AND trim(CDIDIOMA)='ES') AS   CATALOGO
ON CATALOGO.CDFORPAG = KCIM06T.TCFORPAG
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT distinct CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL,IMCAAP15
FROM bddlcru.kcim16t  WHERE NURELREP = 1 and CDPRODTE like 'G%'
UNION ALL
SELECT distinct CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL,IMCAAP15
FROM bddlcru.kcim16h  WHERE NURELREP = 1 and CDPRODTE like 'G%'
) as KCIM16T
ON KTOM41T.cdnumpol=KCIM16T.cdnumpol
AND KTOM41T.ctvrspol=KCIM16T.ctvrspol
left join bddlalm.gmm_elemento_poliza gmmep
on ktom41t.CDNUMPOL = TRIM(gmmep.num_poliza) and ktom41t.CTVRSPOL = gmmep.num_version
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGXG') as KTCTGETSEG on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.CDETISEG) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETSEG.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KCDTECG') as KTCTGETMOT on  CAST(TRIM(KCIM06T.INPOLPAI) AS STRING)= TRIM(KTCTGETMOT.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGYG') as KTCTGETMUL on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.CDNEGMUL) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETMUL.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGZG') as KTCTGETBON on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.CDTIPBON) AS STRING)= TRIM(KTCTGETBON.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTCTSNG') as KTCTGETPCO on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.INPOLCON) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETPCO.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTCTSNG') as KTCTGETPPR on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.INPOLPRE) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETPPR.cdelemen)

SELECT distinct CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL,IMCAAP15
FROM bddlcru.kcim16h  WHERE NURELREP = 1 and CDPRODTE like 'G%'
) as KCIM16T
ON KTOM41T.cdnumpol=KCIM16T.cdnumpol
AND KTOM41T.ctvrspol=KCIM16T.ctvrspol
left join bddlalm.gmm_elemento_poliza gmmep
on ktom41t.CDNUMPOL = TRIM(gmmep.num_poliza) and ktom41t.CTVRSPOL = gmmep.num_version
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGXG') as KTCTGETSEG on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.CDETISEG) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETSEG.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KCDTECG') as KTCTGETMOT on  CAST(TRIM(KCIM06T.INPOLPAI) AS STRING)= TRIM(KTCTGETMOT.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGYG') as KTCTGETMUL on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.CDNEGMUL) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETMUL.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTPTGZG') as KTCTGETBON on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.CDTIPBON) AS STRING)= TRIM(KTCTGETBON.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTCTSNG') as KTCTGETPCO on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.INPOLCON) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETPCO.cdelemen)
left join (select cdelemen, dselemen from bddlcru.KTCTGET where trim(cdtabla) =  'KTCTSNG') as KTCTGETPPR on  CAST(TRIM(gmmep.INPOLPRE) AS STRING) = TRIM(KTCTGETPPR.cdelemen)

NVL(cve_forma_pago ,''),
NVL(mto_prima_tecnica ,''),
NVL(mto_recargo_descuento ,''),
NVL(mto_gasto ,''),
NVL(mto_iva_poliza ,''),

)) as varchar(32)) as idmd5completo

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0
