, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cirind,'')   as des_nivel_hospital

, nvl(CAT_ADMIN.descripcion,'') as des_admon_poliza

, nvl( CAT_TERRITO.PLNDSC,'')  as des_gama_poliza
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan,'') AS cve_plan_gama
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.plndsc,'')  as  des_plan_gama
, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan,'') AS cve_territorialidad
, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.clspln,'')   as  des_territorialidad
, '' AS cve_canal_venta
, ''  as  des_canal_venta
, '' AS cve_segmento
, ''   as   des_segmento
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dirplz,0) else  nvl(agente.dirplz,0) end AS cve_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS direccion_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.cdedoplz,0) else  nvl(agente.cdedoplz,0) end AS cve_edo_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsedoplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsedoplz,'') end AS estado_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.GRZCVE,0) else  nvl(agente.GRZCVE,0) end AS cve_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS des_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz,'') else  nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ.cddirplz,'') end AS cve_red_territorial
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.red_terr,'') else  nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ.red_terr,'') end AS des_red_territorial
, '' AS ban_preexistencia

, '' AS num_reg_producto

, '' AS cve_reg_producto

, ''    as    des_tipo_poliza

, '' AS cve_prod_comercial
, ''  as   des_prod_comercial
, '' AS cve_motivo_movimiento
, ''   as  des_motivo_movimiento
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '')
, current_timestamp() AS ts_alta_hdfs
FROM
(
Select * from bddltrn.agrupado_gaz0_polizahis_duplicados
) gaz
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
cat.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat.dirplz,'') dirplz
, nvl(cat.cdedoplz,'')  cdedoplz
, nvl(cat.am_proc,'') am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') dsedoplz
, cat.redterin
,cat.GRZCVE
FROM bddlcru.cat_cagente2 cat
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz
ON cat.dirplz = plz.cddirplz
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz
ON cat.cdedoplz = edoplz.cdedoplz
) agente
ON gaz.pol_cve_agente = agente.clnumfol
AND gaz.pol_fec_emision_join = agente.am_proc
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_414_estatus_poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) STATUS
ON STATUS.cve_azul = gaz.pol_status_emis

(
select cve_hom,descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_415_forma_de_pago where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) for_pago
on for_pago.cve_azul = gaz.pol_cve_pago
LEFT JOIN(
select trim(cve_hom) cve_hom, trim(descripcion) descripcion,trim(cve_azul) cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_148_Clave_Experiencia_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
)CAT_EXPERI
ON gaz.pol_cve_experiencia=CAT_EXPERI.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN

select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_594_Tipo_Administracion_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul<>''
)CAT_ADMIN
ON CAT_ADMIN.cve_azul= gaz.pol_tipo_admon
LEFT JOIN
(
select trim(cve_pool) cve_pool, trim(pool) pool from bddlcru.cat_pool
)CAT_POOL
ON gaz.pol_pool =  CAT_POOL.cve_pool
LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ
on agente.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
(
select cdtiplan, clspln,PLNDSC from bddlcru.cat_cplanes
) CAT_TERRITO
ON CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_sramo_plan
LEFT JOIN
(
select a.cdtiplan , b.cve_hom , a.cirind, a.plndsc from bddlcru.cat_cplanes a inner join
bddlcru.cat_hom_72_181_426_587_circ_med b on a.cirind=b.descripcion
)CAT_CIRCULO  ON  gaz.pol_num_tipo = cast(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan as decimal(3,0))
LEFT JOIN
(
select psramcob,subsubco cve_cobertura_contable ,subdessu descripcion_cobertura_contable from bddlcru.cat_subramo
)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE
ON CAT_CVE_CONTABLE.psramcob=gaz.pol_sramo_cont
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT
cat2.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat2.dirplz,'') as dirplz
, nvl(cat2.cdedoplz,'') as cdedoplz
, nvl(cat2.am_proc,'') as am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') as dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') as dsedoplz
, cat2.redterin as redterin
,cat2.GRZCVE
FROM
( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,
RANK () over(partition by clnumfol
order by am_proc asc)  as Posicion from bddlcru.cat_cagente2
where clnumfol is not null
) A where Posicion=1)
cat2
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz

on obtiene_agente_min.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN

on gaz.pol_sramo_cont=cat_sramo.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN
(
select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN
ON CAT_PLAN.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_num_tipo
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)
WHERE gaz.ultimo_reg = 1

INSERT INTO TABLE bddltrn.stg_poliza_azul
SELECT DISTINCT
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) as num_poliza

, -999 AS num_version_poliza
, CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
, 'AZUL' AS cve_sistema

140001

, nvl(CAT_POOL.pool,'')   as  des_pool

, nvl(CAT_PLAN.plntpo,'')   as  des_plan

, ''   as   des_usuario

, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cirind,'')   as des_nivel_hospital

, nvl( CAT_TERRITO.PLNDSC,'')  as des_gama_poliza

, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.clspln,'')   as  des_territorialidad
, '' AS cve_canal_venta

, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dirplz,0) else  nvl(agente.dirplz,0) end AS cve_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS direccion_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.cdedoplz,0) else  nvl(agente.cdedoplz,0) end AS cve_edo_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsedoplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsedoplz,'') end AS estado_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.GRZCVE,0) else  nvl(agente.GRZCVE,0) end AS cve_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS des_da

, '' AS cve_motivo_movimiento
, ''   as  des_motivo_movimiento

,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '')

,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '')

(

) gaz
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
cat.clnumfol as clnumfol

, nvl(cat.am_proc,'') am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') dsedoplz
, cat.redterin

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

LEFT JOIN

LEFT JOIN(

)CAT_EXPERI

)CAT_ADMIN

)CAT_POOL

LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz

)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE

LEFT JOIN
(

,cat2.GRZCVE

( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,
RANK () over(partition by clnumfol
order by am_proc asc)  as Posicion from bddlcru.cat_cagente2

) A where Posicion=1)
cat2
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz

LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz

LEFT JOIN
(

)CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN
on obtiene_agente_min.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
bddlcru.cat_hom_460_subramo_admvo_pol cat_sramo

LEFT JOIN
(
select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN

LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)
WHERE gaz.ultimo_reg = 1

INSERT INTO TABLE bddltrn.stg_poliza_azul
SELECT DISTINCT
CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) as num_poliza
, -999 AS vigencia_poliza
, -999 AS num_version_poliza
, CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
, 'AZUL' AS cve_sistema
, 'AZUL' AS cve_sistema_int
, nvl(CAT_CVE_CONTABLE.cve_cobertura_contable,'')    AS cve_cobertura_contable
,  nvl(CAT_CVE_CONTABLE.descripcion_cobertura_contable,'')  as des_cobertura_contable
, nvl(STATUS.cve_hom,'') AS cve_estatus_poliza
, nvl(STATUS.descripcion,'')  as  des_estatus_poliza
, nvl(for_pago.cve_hom,'') AS cve_forma_pago
, nvl(for_pago.descripcion,'')    as des_forma_pago
, nvl(gaz.pol_cve_agente,'') AS cve_folio
, nvl(gaz.pol_razon_soc,'')   as des_folio
, NVL(
CAST(CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_ini_vig AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_ini_vig AS STRING),5,2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_ini_vig AS STRING),7,2)) AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP)
) AS fch_ini_vigencia
, NVL(
CAST(CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_fin_vig AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_fin_vig AS STRING),5,2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_fin_vig AS STRING),7,2)) AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP)
) AS fch_fin_vigencia
, gaz.pol_rfc AS rfc_contratante
, gaz.pol_razon_soc AS nombre_contratante
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cve_hom,'')    AS cve_circulo_medico
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cirind,'')   as des_circulo_medico
, CAST(CAST('1400-01-01' AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP) fch_ini_poliza
, NVL(
CAST(CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_emision AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_emision AS STRING),5,2), '-', SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_emision AS STRING),7,2)) AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP)
) AS fch_emision
, NVL(
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_emision AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTR(CAST(gaz.pol_fec_emision AS STRING),5,2) ) AS INT),
140001
) AS anio_mes_emision
,  nvl(CAT_EXPERI.cve_hom,'') AS cve_experiencia
, nvl(CAT_EXPERI.descripcion,'')  as     des_experiencia
, nvl(gaz.pol_pool,'') AS cve_pool
, nvl(CAT_POOL.pool,'')   as  des_pool
, nvl(cat_sramo.cve_hom,0) AS cve_ramo
, nvl(cat_sramo.descripcion,'')   as  des_ramo
, nvl(gaz.pol_num_tipo,'') AS cve_plan
, nvl(CAT_PLAN.plntpo,'')   as  des_plan
, '' AS ban_coaseguro_cero
, '' AS cve_usuario
, ''   as   des_usuario
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cve_hom,'')    AS cve_nivel_hospital
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cirind,'')   as des_nivel_hospital
, nvl(CAT_ADMIN.cve_hom,'') AS cve_admon_poliza
, nvl(CAT_ADMIN.descripcion,'') as des_admon_poliza
, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan,'') AS cve_gama_poliza
, nvl( CAT_TERRITO.PLNDSC,'')  as des_gama_poliza
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan,'') AS cve_plan_gama
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.plndsc,'')  as  des_plan_gama
, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan,'') AS cve_territorialidad
, nvl(CAT_TERRITO.clspln,'')   as  des_territorialidad
, '' AS cve_canal_venta
, ''  as  des_canal_venta
, '' AS cve_segmento
, ''   as   des_segmento
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dirplz,0) else  nvl(agente.dirplz,0) end AS cve_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS direccion_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.cdedoplz,0) else  nvl(agente.cdedoplz,0) end AS cve_edo_dir_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsedoplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsedoplz,'') end AS estado_plaza
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.GRZCVE,0) else  nvl(agente.GRZCVE,0) end AS cve_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(obtiene_agente_min.dsdirplz,'') else  nvl(agente.dsdirplz,'') end AS des_da
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz,'') else  nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ.cddirplz,'') end AS cve_red_territorial
, case  when agente.clnumfol is null  and gaz.pol_fec_emision_join <= obtiene_agente_min.am_proc then nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.red_terr,'') else  nvl(CAT_DIRPLZ.red_terr,'') end AS des_red_territorial
, '' AS ban_preexistencia
, CAST(CAST('1400-01-01' AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_registro_prod
, '' AS num_reg_producto
, gaz.pol_num_asg_dep AS num_aseg_dependientes
, gaz.pol_num_asg_pri AS num_aseg_titulares
, '' AS cve_reg_producto
, nvl(gaz.pol_tipo_admon,'') AS cve_tipo_poliza
, ''    as    des_tipo_poliza
, nvl(gaz.pol_num_tipo,'') AS cve_tipo_movimiento
, ''     as   des_tipo_movimiento
, ''   as   des_estado_plaza
, '' AS cve_negocio
, ''  as   des_negocio
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan,'') AS cve_prod_tecnico
, nvl(CAT_CIRCULO.plndsc,'')     as   des_prod_tecnico
, '' AS cve_prod_comercial
, ''  as   des_prod_comercial
, '' AS cve_motivo_movimiento
, ''   as  des_motivo_movimiento
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '')
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '')
, current_timestamp() AS ts_alta_hdfs
FROM
(
Select * from bddltrn.agrupado_gaz0_polizahis_duplicados
) gaz
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(
SELECT
cat.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat.dirplz,'') dirplz
, nvl(cat.cdedoplz,'')  cdedoplz
, nvl(cat.am_proc,'') am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') dsedoplz
, cat.redterin
,cat.GRZCVE
FROM bddlcru.cat_cagente2 cat
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz
ON cat.dirplz = plz.cddirplz
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz
ON cat.cdedoplz = edoplz.cdedoplz
) agente
ON gaz.pol_cve_agente = agente.clnumfol
AND gaz.pol_fec_emision_join = agente.am_proc
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_414_estatus_poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) STATUS
ON STATUS.cve_azul = gaz.pol_status_emis
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom,descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_415_forma_de_pago where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
) for_pago
on for_pago.cve_azul = gaz.pol_cve_pago
LEFT JOIN(
select trim(cve_hom) cve_hom, trim(descripcion) descripcion,trim(cve_azul) cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_148_Clave_Experiencia_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul <> ''
)CAT_EXPERI
ON gaz.pol_cve_experiencia=CAT_EXPERI.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN
(
select cve_hom, descripcion,cve_azul from bddlcru.cat_hom_594_Tipo_Administracion_Poliza where cve_azul is not null and cve_azul<>''
)CAT_ADMIN
ON CAT_ADMIN.cve_azul= gaz.pol_tipo_admon
LEFT JOIN
(
select trim(cve_pool) cve_pool, trim(pool) pool from bddlcru.cat_pool
)CAT_POOL
ON gaz.pol_pool =  CAT_POOL.cve_pool
LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ
on agente.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
(
select cdtiplan, clspln,PLNDSC from bddlcru.cat_cplanes
) CAT_TERRITO
ON CAT_TERRITO.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_sramo_plan
LEFT JOIN
(
select a.cdtiplan , b.cve_hom , a.cirind, a.plndsc from bddlcru.cat_cplanes a inner join
bddlcru.cat_hom_72_181_426_587_circ_med b on a.cirind=b.descripcion
)CAT_CIRCULO  ON  gaz.pol_num_tipo = cast(CAT_CIRCULO.cdtiplan as decimal(3,0))
LEFT JOIN
(
select psramcob,subsubco cve_cobertura_contable ,subdessu descripcion_cobertura_contable from bddlcru.cat_subramo
)CAT_CVE_CONTABLE
ON CAT_CVE_CONTABLE.psramcob=gaz.pol_sramo_cont
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT
cat2.clnumfol as clnumfol
, nvl(cat2.dirplz,'') as dirplz
, nvl(cat2.cdedoplz,'') as cdedoplz
, nvl(cat2.am_proc,'') as am_proc
, nvl(plz.dsdirplz,'') as dsdirplz
, nvl(edoplz.dsedoplz,'') as dsedoplz
, cat2.redterin as redterin
,cat2.GRZCVE
FROM
( select   clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, A.am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE    from (
select clnumfol, dirplz,cdedoplz, am_proc, redterin, GRZCVE,
RANK () over(partition by clnumfol
order by am_proc asc)  as Posicion from bddlcru.cat_cagente2
where clnumfol is not null
) A where Posicion=1)
cat2
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cddirplz plz
ON cat2.dirplz = plz.cddirplz
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlcru.cdedoplz edoplz
ON cat2.cdedoplz = edoplz.cdedoplz)  obtiene_agente_min
on gaz.pol_cve_agente = obtiene_agente_min.clnumfol
LEFT JOIN
(
select cddirplz, dsdirplz, red_terr  from  bddlcru.cat_cddirplz
)CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN
on obtiene_agente_min.dirplz= CAT_DIRPLZ_MIN.cddirplz
LEFT JOIN
bddlcru.cat_hom_460_subramo_admvo_pol cat_sramo
on gaz.pol_sramo_cont=cat_sramo.cve_azul
LEFT JOIN
(
select pla_plan as cdtiplan,  pla_nombre as plntpo from bddlcru.gaz0_tab_planes
) CAT_PLAN
ON CAT_PLAN.cdtiplan =  gaz.pol_num_tipo
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_oficina,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(pol_numero,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_ofi_renovac ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(gaz.pol_num_renovac,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)
WHERE gaz.ultimo_reg = 1

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_CBZA_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA_TMP as
SELECT
CAST(T.anio_mes_contable AS INT) AS anio_mes_contable
,T.fch_emision as fch_contable
,CAST(T.num_poliza AS VARCHAR(14)) AS num_poliza
,CAST(T.vigencia_poliza AS INT) AS vigencia_poliza
,CAST(T.num_version_poliza AS INT) AS num_version_poliza
,CAST(T.num_poliza_cobranza AS VARCHAR(8)) AS num_poliza_cobranza
,LPAD(CAST(T.num_endoso AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0') AS num_endoso
,CASE
WHEN (T.cve_forma_pago=0 ) THEN 'Unica'
WHEN (T.cve_forma_pago=1 ) THEN 'Anual'
WHEN (T.cve_forma_pago=2 ) THEN 'Semestral'
WHEN (T.cve_forma_pago=3 ) THEN 'Trimestral'
WHEN (T.cve_forma_pago=4 ) THEN 'Mensual'
END AS forma_pago
,CAST(T.cve_tipo_endoso AS VARCHAR(3)) AS cve_tipo_endoso
,CAST(T.mto_prima_tecnica AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_prima_tecnica
,CAST(T.mto_recargo_descuento AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_recargo_descuento
,CAST(T.mto_prima_neta AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_prima_neta
,CAST(T.mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,CAST(T.pct_pago_prima AS DECIMAL(11,6)) AS pct_pago_prima
,CAST(T.mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc
,CAST(T.mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago
,CAST(T.mto_derecho_poliza AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_derecho_poliza
,CAST(T.mto_cesion_comision AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_cesion_comision
,CAST(T.mto_iva_poliza AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_iva_poliza
,CAST(T.mto_prima_total AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_prima_total
,CAST(T.cve_cobertura_contable AS VARCHAR(3)) AS cve_cobertura_contable
,T.fch_emision
,NVL(segmento, '') as segmento
,NVL(desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento
,NVL(negocio, '') as negocio
,NVL(desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio
,NVL(bonos, '') as bonos
,NVL(desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos
,NVL(plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos
,NVL(pol_contr, '') as pol_contr
,NVL(desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr
,NVL(contrb, '') as contrb
,NVL(pol_prest, '') as pol_prest
,NVL(desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest
,NVL(mot_exc, '') as mot_exc
,NVL(desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
,'' as cve_canal_venta_alterno
,CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5
,CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO
,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS fechaaud
,CAST('CBZA' AS VARCHAR(10)) AS cve_sistema_int
FROM
(
SELECT DISTINCT * FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_POLIZA
UNION ALL
SELECT DISTINCT * FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_ENDOSO

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_CBZA_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA_TMP as
SELECT
CAST(T.anio_mes_contable AS INT) AS anio_mes_contable
,T.fch_emision as fch_contable
,CAST(T.num_poliza AS VARCHAR(14)) AS num_poliza
,CAST(T.vigencia_poliza AS INT) AS vigencia_poliza
,CAST(T.num_version_poliza AS INT) AS num_version_poliza
,CAST(T.num_poliza_cobranza AS VARCHAR(8)) AS num_poliza_cobranza
,LPAD(CAST(T.num_endoso AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0') AS num_endoso
,CASE
WHEN (T.cve_forma_pago=0 ) THEN 'Unica'
WHEN (T.cve_forma_pago=1 ) THEN 'Anual'
WHEN (T.cve_forma_pago=2 ) THEN 'Semestral'
WHEN (T.cve_forma_pago=3 ) THEN 'Trimestral'
WHEN (T.cve_forma_pago=4 ) THEN 'Mensual'
END AS forma_pago
,CAST(T.cve_tipo_endoso AS VARCHAR(3)) AS cve_tipo_endoso
,CAST(T.mto_prima_tecnica AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_prima_tecnica
,CAST(T.mto_recargo_descuento AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_recargo_descuento
,CAST(T.mto_prima_neta AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_prima_neta
,CAST(T.mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,CAST(T.pct_pago_prima AS DECIMAL(11,6)) AS pct_pago_prima
,CAST(T.mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc
,CAST(T.mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago
,CAST(T.mto_derecho_poliza AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_derecho_poliza
,CAST(T.mto_cesion_comision AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_cesion_comision
,CAST(T.mto_iva_poliza AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_iva_poliza
,CAST(T.mto_prima_total AS DECIMAL(20,6)) AS mto_prima_total
,CAST(T.cve_cobertura_contable AS VARCHAR(3)) AS cve_cobertura_contable
,T.fch_emision
,NVL(segmento, '') as segmento
,NVL(desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento
,NVL(negocio, '') as negocio
,NVL(desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio
,NVL(bonos, '') as bonos
,NVL(desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos
,NVL(plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos
,NVL(pol_contr, '') as pol_contr
,NVL(desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr
,NVL(contrb, '') as contrb
,NVL(pol_prest, '') as pol_prest
,NVL(desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest
,NVL(mot_exc, '') as mot_exc
,NVL(desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
,'' as cve_canal_venta_alterno
,CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5
,CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO
,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS fechaaud
,CAST('CBZA' AS VARCHAR(10)) AS cve_sistema_int
FROM
(
SELECT DISTINCT * FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_POLIZA
UNION ALL
SELECT DISTINCT * FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_ENDOSO
UNION ALL
SELECT DISTINCT * FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_HISTORIA
) T

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_alm_contratante_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    bddlalm.alm_contratante        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_HISTORIA as
SELECT
SUBSTRING(CAST(SDHISTEND.FECHEMIS_HISTEND AS STRING),1,6) AS anio_mes_contable
,CAST('1400-01-01 00:00:00' AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_contable
,CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) AS num_poliza
,-999 AS vigencia_poliza
,-999 AS num_version_poliza
,CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDHISTEND.OFNA_HISTEND ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDHISTEND.POLIZA_HISTEND,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
,CAST(SDHISTEND.NUMENDOSO_HISTEND AS VARCHAR(6)) AS num_endoso
,SDHISTEND.FORPAGEND_HISTEND AS cve_forma_pago
,TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) AS cve_tipo_endoso
,0 AS mto_prima_tecnica
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.DESCVOL_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.DESCVOL_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_recargo_descuento
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.PRINETA_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.PRINETA_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_prima_neta
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.RECARGO_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.RECARGO_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,0 AS pct_pago_prima
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.PRINETA_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.PRINETA_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc
,0 AS mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.GASTOS_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.GASTOS_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_derecho_poliza
,0 AS mto_cesion_comision
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.IMPORIMP_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.IMPORIMP_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_iva_poliza
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.PRIMATOT_HISTEND/100)*-1
ELSE (SDHISTEND.PRIMATOT_HISTEND/100)
END AS mto_prima_total
,COALESCE(CAT_SUBRAMO.SUBSUBCO,'') AS cve_cobertura_contable
,CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SDHISTEND.FECHEMIS_HISTEND AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDHISTEND.FECHEMIS_HISTEND AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDHISTEND.FECHEMIS_HISTEND AS STRING),7,2),' 00:00:00') AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_emision
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '') as segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '') as negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '') as bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '') as pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '') as contrb
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '') as pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
)SDPOLIZA
INNER JOIN
(SELECT OFNA_HISTEND,POLIZA_HISTEND,NUMENDOSO_HISTEND,FORPAGEND_HISTEND,TIPENDOSO_HISTEND,DESCVOL_HISTEND,PRINETA_HISTEND,RECARGO_HISTEND,GASTOS_HISTEND,IMPORIMP_HISTEND,PRIMATOT_HISTEND,FECHEMIS_HISTEND
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDHISTEND
GROUP BY OFNA_HISTEND,POLIZA_HISTEND,NUMENDOSO_HISTEND,FORPAGEND_HISTEND,TIPENDOSO_HISTEND,DESCVOL_HISTEND,PRINETA_HISTEND,RECARGO_HISTEND,GASTOS_HISTEND,IMPORIMP_HISTEND,PRIMATOT_HISTEND,FECHEMIS_HISTEND
)SDHISTEND
ON SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA = SDHISTEND.OFNA_HISTEND
AND SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA = SDHISTEND.POLIZA_HISTEND
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SUBRAMO CAT_SUBRAMO
ON SDPOLIZA.SUBRAMO_POLIZA = CAT_SUBRAMO.PSRAMCOB
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDHISTEND.OFNA_HISTEND ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDHISTEND.POLIZA_HISTEND,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

on  CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDHISTEND.OFNA_HISTEND ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDHISTEND.POLIZA_HISTEND,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_HISTORIA as
SELECT
SUBSTRING(CAST(SDHISTEND.FECHEMIS_HISTEND AS STRING),1,6) AS anio_mes_contable
,CAST('1400-01-01 00:00:00' AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_contable
,CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) AS num_poliza
,-999 AS vigencia_poliza
,-999 AS num_version_poliza
,CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDHISTEND.OFNA_HISTEND ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDHISTEND.POLIZA_HISTEND,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
,CAST(SDHISTEND.NUMENDOSO_HISTEND AS VARCHAR(6)) AS num_endoso
,SDHISTEND.FORPAGEND_HISTEND AS cve_forma_pago
,TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) AS cve_tipo_endoso
,0 AS mto_prima_tecnica
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.DESCVOL_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.DESCVOL_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_recargo_descuento
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.PRINETA_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.PRINETA_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_prima_neta
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.RECARGO_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.RECARGO_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,0 AS pct_pago_prima
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.PRINETA_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.PRINETA_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc
,0 AS mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.GASTOS_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.GASTOS_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_derecho_poliza
,0 AS mto_cesion_comision
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.IMPORIMP_HISTEND/100)*-1 ELSE (SDHISTEND.IMPORIMP_HISTEND/100) END AS mto_iva_poliza
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDHISTEND.TIPENDOSO_HISTEND) = 'D' THEN (SDHISTEND.PRIMATOT_HISTEND/100)*-1
ELSE (SDHISTEND.PRIMATOT_HISTEND/100)
END AS mto_prima_total
,COALESCE(CAT_SUBRAMO.SUBSUBCO,'') AS cve_cobertura_contable
,CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SDHISTEND.FECHEMIS_HISTEND AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDHISTEND.FECHEMIS_HISTEND AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDHISTEND.FECHEMIS_HISTEND AS STRING),7,2),' 00:00:00') AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_emision
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '') as segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '') as negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '') as bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '') as pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '') as contrb
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '') as pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
)SDPOLIZA
INNER JOIN
(SELECT OFNA_HISTEND,POLIZA_HISTEND,NUMENDOSO_HISTEND,FORPAGEND_HISTEND,TIPENDOSO_HISTEND,DESCVOL_HISTEND,PRINETA_HISTEND,RECARGO_HISTEND,GASTOS_HISTEND,IMPORIMP_HISTEND,PRIMATOT_HISTEND,FECHEMIS_HISTEND
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDHISTEND
GROUP BY OFNA_HISTEND,POLIZA_HISTEND,NUMENDOSO_HISTEND,FORPAGEND_HISTEND,TIPENDOSO_HISTEND,DESCVOL_HISTEND,PRINETA_HISTEND,RECARGO_HISTEND,GASTOS_HISTEND,IMPORIMP_HISTEND,PRIMATOT_HISTEND,FECHEMIS_HISTEND
)SDHISTEND
ON SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA = SDHISTEND.OFNA_HISTEND
AND SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA = SDHISTEND.POLIZA_HISTEND
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SUBRAMO CAT_SUBRAMO
ON SDPOLIZA.SUBRAMO_POLIZA = CAT_SUBRAMO.PSRAMCOB
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDHISTEND.OFNA_HISTEND ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDHISTEND.POLIZA_HISTEND,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_info
SELECT DISTINCT
num_poliza, vigencia_poliza, num_version_poliza, num_poliza_cobranza, num_endoso, cve_cliente_origen, cve_sistema, cve_sistema_int, rfc
, TRIM(nombre), TRIM(razon_social), correo_electronico, curp, cve_pais_nacimiento, nacionalidad, nacionalidad_residencia, cve_tipo
, cve_sexo, cve_estatus, telefono1, telefono2, fch_alta ,fch_baja, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechaaud, ori_contratante
, tsultmod_poliza, reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', concat(NUM_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,VIGENCIA_POLIZA)) IDMD5
, reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex'
,concat(
NUM_POLIZA, NUM_VERSION_POLIZA, VIGENCIA_POLIZA, CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN, CVE_SISTEMA, NVL(RFC,''), NVL(NOMBRE,'')
, NVL(RAZON_SOCIAL,''), NVL(CORREO_ELECTRONICO,''), NVL(CURP,''), NVL(CVE_PAIS_NACIMIENTO,''), NVL(NACIONALIDAD,'')
, NVL(NACIONALIDAD_RESIDENCIA,''), NVL(CVE_TIPO,''), NVL(CVE_SEXO,''), NVL(CVE_ESTATUS,''), NVL(TELEFONO1,'')
, NVL(TELEFONO2,''), NVL(CAST(FCH_ALTA AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(FCH_BAJA AS STRING),'')
)) IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_info

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_sdpoliza_cbza1
SELECT
num_poliza, vigencia_poliza, num_version_poliza, num_poliza_cobranza, num_endoso, cve_cliente_origen, cve_sistema, cve_sistema_int, TRIM(rfc)
, TRIM(nombre), TRIM(razon_social), correo_electronico, curp, cve_pais_nacimiento, nacionalidad
, nacionalidad_residencia, cve_tipo, cve_sexo, cve_estatus, telefono1, telefono2, fch_alta ,fch_baja
, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechaaud, ori_contratante, tsultmod_poliza
, reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex',
concat(NVL(NUM_POLIZA,''), NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''), NVL(NUM_ENDOSO,''))) IDMD5
, reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex'
,concat(
NUM_POLIZA, NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''), NVL(NUM_ENDOSO,''), NVL(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,''), CVE_SISTEMA, NVL(TRIM(RFC)   ,'')
, NVL(TRIM(NOMBRE),''), NVL(CORREO_ELECTRONICO, ''), NVL(CURP  ,''), NVL(CVE_PAIS_NACIMIENTO,'')
, NVL(NACIONALIDAD,''), NVL(NACIONALIDAD_RESIDENCIA  ,''), NVL(CVE_TIPO   ,'')
, NVL(CVE_SEXO,''), NVL(CVE_ESTATUS, ''), NVL(TELEFONO1  ,''), NVL(TELEFONO2,'')
, NVL(CAST(FCH_ALTA AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(FCH_BAJA AS STRING), '')
)) IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM (
SELECT * FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_sdpoliza_cbza1
UNION ALL
SELECT c2.*
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_sdendoso_cbza2 c2
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_sdhistend_cbza3 c3 ON
C2.num_poliza = c3.num_poliza
AND c2.num_poliza_cobranza = c3.num_poliza_cobranza
AND c2.num_endoso = c3.num_endoso
WHERE c3.num_poliza IS NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_sdhistend_cbza3
) Z

CREATE  TABLE IF NOT EXISTS bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_info AS
SELECT
CAST(pol.cdnumpol AS VARCHAR(14))                                 NUM_POLIZA
, CAST(pol.inancaco AS smallint)                                    VIGENCIA_POLIZA
, CAST(pol.ctvrspol AS INT)                                         NUM_VERSION_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL         AS VARCHAR( 8))                                 NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA
, CAST(NULL         AS VARCHAR( 6))                                 NUM_ENDOSO
, CAST(per.cdfiliac AS VARCHAR(10))                                 CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN
, CAST('INFO'       AS VARCHAR( 4))                                 CVE_SISTEMA
, CAST('INFO'       AS VARCHAR( 4))                                 CVE_SISTEMA_INT
, CAST(TRIM(per.cdrfc)    AS VARCHAR(16))                           RFC
, CONCAT(TRIM(dnnomrzm), ' ', TRIM(dnap1rzm), ' ', TRIM(dnap2rzm))  NOMBRE
, CONCAT(TRIM(dnnomrzm), ' ', TRIM(dnap1rzm), ' ', TRIM(dnap2rzm))  RAZON_SOCIAL
, CAST(NULL         AS VARCHAR(75))                                 CORREO_ELECTRONICO
, CAST(per.cdcurp   AS VARCHAR(20))                                 CURP
, CAST(per.tcnacper AS VARCHAR( 3))                                 CVE_PAIS_NACIMIENTO
, CAST(TRIM(cat_nac.dselemen) AS STRING)                            NACIONALIDAD
, CAST(TRIM(cat_res.dselemen) AS STRING)                            NACIONALIDAD_RESIDENCIA
, CAST(per.tcpefiju AS VARCHAR( 1))                                 CVE_TIPO
, CASE WHEN per.tcpefiju = 'F'
THEN CAST(NVL(TRIM(csex.cve_hom), '') AS VARCHAR(1))
ELSE CAST('' AS VARCHAR(1))
END                                                               CVE_SEXO
, CAST(per.tcestper AS VARCHAR( 1))                                 CVE_ESTATUS
, CAST(NULL         AS VARCHAR(75))                                 TELEFONO1
, CAST(NULL         AS VARCHAR(75))                                 TELEFONO2
, IF(per.fealpers = 0, 14000101, per.fealpers)                AS    FCH_ALTA
, IF(per.febapers = 0, 14000101, per.febapers)                AS    FCH_BAJA
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP)                                           FECHAAUD
, CAST('I1' AS VARCHAR(2))                                          ORI_CONTRATANTE
, pol.FECHAAUD                                                      TSULTMOD_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL AS VARCHAR(32))                                         IDMD5
, CAST(NULL AS VARCHAR(32))                                         IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM
(
SELECT  cdnumpol, inancaco, ctvrspol, clfiltom, pol.FECHAAUD FROM bddlcru.kcim06t pol
INNER JOIN (SELECT NVL(MAX(tsultmod_poliza), CAST('1900-01-01 00:00:00.00' AS TIMESTAMP)) AS tsultmod_poliza FROM bddlalm.alm_contratante
WHERE ORI_CONTRATANTE = 'I1') alm
WHERE CDCIAGRU = 'SA' AND pol.FECHAAUD > alm.tsultmod_poliza
UNION ALL
SELECT  cdnumpol, inancaco, ctvrspol, clfiltom, pol.FECHAAUD FROM bddlcru.kcim06t pol
INNER JOIN (SELECT num_poliza, num_version_poliza FROM bddlalm.alm_contratante WHERE ORI_CONTRATANTE = 'I1' AND idmd5completo IS NULL) con ON
pol.cdnumpol = con.num_poliza AND pol.ctvrspol = con.num_version_poliza
WHERE CDCIAGRU = 'SA'
) pol
LEFT OUTER JOIN  bddlcru.kpem08t per ON
pol.clfiltom = per.cdfiliac
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT CAST(TRIM(cve_info) AS VARCHAR(1)) cve_info, CAST(TRIM(cve_hom) AS VARCHAR(1)) cve_hom FROM bddlcru.cat_hom_509_gen_sex_aseg) csex ON
csex.cve_info = per.tcsexo
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT TRIM(cdelemen) cdelemen, TRIM(dselemen) dselemen FROM bddlcru.ktctget WHERE TRIM(cdtabla) = 'KTCTPAG') cat_nac  ON
cat_nac.cdelemen = per.TCNACPER
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT TRIM(cdelemen) cdelemen, TRIM(dselemen) dselemen FROM bddlcru.ktctget WHERE TRIM(cdtabla) = 'KTCTPAG') cat_res  ON
cat_res.cdelemen = per.TCNACRES

THEN CAST(NVL(TRIM(csex.cve_hom), '') AS VARCHAR(1))
ELSE CAST('' AS VARCHAR(1))
END                                                               CVE_SEXO
, CAST(per.tcestper AS VARCHAR( 1))                                 CVE_ESTATUS
, CAST(NULL         AS VARCHAR(75))                                 TELEFONO1
, CAST(NULL         AS VARCHAR(75))                                 TELEFONO2
, IF(per.fealpers = 0, 14000101, per.fealpers)                AS    FCH_ALTA
, IF(per.febapers = 0, 14000101, per.febapers)                AS    FCH_BAJA
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP)                                           FECHAAUD
, CAST('I1' AS VARCHAR(2))                                          ORI_CONTRATANTE
, pol.FECHAAUD                                                      TSULTMOD_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL AS VARCHAR(32))                                         IDMD5
, CAST(NULL AS VARCHAR(32))                                         IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM
(
SELECT  cdnumpol, inancaco, ctvrspol, clfiltom, pol.FECHAAUD FROM bddlcru.kcim06t pol
INNER JOIN (SELECT NVL(MAX(tsultmod_poliza), CAST('1900-01-01 00:00:00.00' AS TIMESTAMP)) AS tsultmod_poliza FROM bddlalm.alm_contratante
WHERE ORI_CONTRATANTE = 'I1') alm
WHERE CDCIAGRU = 'SA' AND pol.FECHAAUD > alm.tsultmod_poliza
UNION ALL
SELECT  cdnumpol, inancaco, ctvrspol, clfiltom, pol.FECHAAUD FROM bddlcru.kcim06t pol
INNER JOIN (SELECT num_poliza, num_version_poliza FROM bddlalm.alm_contratante WHERE ORI_CONTRATANTE = 'I1' AND idmd5completo IS NULL) con ON
pol.cdnumpol = con.num_poliza AND pol.ctvrspol = con.num_version_poliza
WHERE CDCIAGRU = 'SA'
) pol
LEFT OUTER JOIN  bddlcru.kpem08t per ON
pol.clfiltom = per.cdfiliac
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT CAST(TRIM(cve_info) AS VARCHAR(1)) cve_info, CAST(TRIM(cve_hom) AS VARCHAR(1)) cve_hom FROM bddlcru.cat_hom_509_gen_sex_aseg) csex ON
csex.cve_info = per.tcsexo
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT TRIM(cdelemen) cdelemen, TRIM(dselemen) dselemen FROM bddlcru.ktctget WHERE TRIM(cdtabla) = 'KTCTPAG') cat_nac  ON
cat_nac.cdelemen = per.TCNACPER
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT TRIM(cdelemen) cdelemen, TRIM(dselemen) dselemen FROM bddlcru.ktctget WHERE TRIM(cdtabla) = 'KTCTPAG') cat_res  ON
cat_res.cdelemen = per.TCNACRES

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_ENDOSO as
SELECT
SUBSTRING(CAST(SDENDOSO.FECHEMIS_ENDOSO AS STRING),1,6) AS anio_mes_contable
,CAST('1400-01-01 00:00:00' AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_contable
,CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) AS num_poliza
,-999 AS vigencia_poliza
,-999 AS num_version_poliza
,CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDENDOSO.OFNA_ENDOSO ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDENDOSO.POLIZA_ENDOSO,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
,CAST(SDENDOSO.NUMENDOSO_ENDOSO AS VARCHAR(6)) AS num_endoso
,SDENDOSO.FORPAGEND_ENDOSO AS cve_forma_pago
,TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) AS cve_tipo_endoso
,0 AS mto_prima_tecnica
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.DESCVOL_ENDOSO/100)*-1 ELSE (SDENDOSO.DESCVOL_ENDOSO/100) END AS mto_recargo_descuento
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.PRINETA_ENDOSO/100)*-1 ELSE (SDENDOSO.PRINETA_ENDOSO/100) END AS mto_prima_neta
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.RECARGO_ENDOSO/100)*-1 ELSE (SDENDOSO.RECARGO_ENDOSO/100) END AS mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,0 AS pct_pago_prima
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.PRINETA_ENDOSO/100)*-1 ELSE (SDENDOSO.PRINETA_ENDOSO/100) END AS mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc
,0 AS mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.GASTOS_ENDOSO/100)*-1 ELSE (SDENDOSO.GASTOS_ENDOSO/100) END AS mto_derecho_poliza
,0 AS mto_cesion_comision
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.IMPORIMP_ENDOSO/100)*-1 ELSE (SDENDOSO.IMPORIMP_ENDOSO/100) END AS mto_iva_poliza
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.PRIMATOT_ENDOSO/100)*-1
ELSE (SDENDOSO.PRIMATOT_ENDOSO/100)
END AS mto_prima_total
,COALESCE(CAT_SUBRAMO.SUBSUBCO,'') AS cve_cobertura_contable
,CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SDENDOSO.FECHEMIS_ENDOSO AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDENDOSO.FECHEMIS_ENDOSO AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDENDOSO.FECHEMIS_ENDOSO AS STRING),7,2) ,' 00:00:00') AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_emision
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '') as segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '') as negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '') as bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '') as pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '') as contrb
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '') as pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
)SDPOLIZA
INNER JOIN
(SELECT OFNA_ENDOSO,POLIZA_ENDOSO,NUMENDOSO_ENDOSO,FORPAGEND_ENDOSO,TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO,DESCVOL_ENDOSO,PRINETA_ENDOSO,RECARGO_ENDOSO,GASTOS_ENDOSO,IMPORIMP_ENDOSO,PRIMATOT_ENDOSO,FECHEMIS_ENDOSO
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDENDOSO
GROUP BY OFNA_ENDOSO,POLIZA_ENDOSO,NUMENDOSO_ENDOSO,FORPAGEND_ENDOSO,TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO,DESCVOL_ENDOSO,PRINETA_ENDOSO,RECARGO_ENDOSO,GASTOS_ENDOSO,IMPORIMP_ENDOSO,PRIMATOT_ENDOSO,FECHEMIS_ENDOSO
)SDENDOSO
ON SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA = SDENDOSO.OFNA_ENDOSO
AND SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA = SDENDOSO.POLIZA_ENDOSO
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SUBRAMO CAT_SUBRAMO
ON SDPOLIZA.SUBRAMO_POLIZA = CAT_SUBRAMO.PSRAMCOB
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDENDOSO.OFNA_ENDOSO ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDENDOSO.POLIZA_ENDOSO,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.RECARGO_ENDOSO/100)*-1 ELSE (SDENDOSO.RECARGO_ENDOSO/100) END AS mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,0 AS pct_pago_prima
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.PRINETA_ENDOSO/100)*-1 ELSE (SDENDOSO.PRINETA_ENDOSO/100) END AS mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc
,0 AS mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.GASTOS_ENDOSO/100)*-1 ELSE (SDENDOSO.GASTOS_ENDOSO/100) END AS mto_derecho_poliza
,0 AS mto_cesion_comision
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.IMPORIMP_ENDOSO/100)*-1 ELSE (SDENDOSO.IMPORIMP_ENDOSO/100) END AS mto_iva_poliza
,CASE WHEN TRIM(SDENDOSO.TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO) = 'D' THEN (SDENDOSO.PRIMATOT_ENDOSO/100)*-1
ELSE (SDENDOSO.PRIMATOT_ENDOSO/100)
END AS mto_prima_total
,COALESCE(CAT_SUBRAMO.SUBSUBCO,'') AS cve_cobertura_contable
,CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SDENDOSO.FECHEMIS_ENDOSO AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDENDOSO.FECHEMIS_ENDOSO AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDENDOSO.FECHEMIS_ENDOSO AS STRING),7,2) ,' 00:00:00') AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_emision
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '') as segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '') as negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '') as bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '') as pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '') as contrb
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '') as pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
)SDPOLIZA
INNER JOIN
(SELECT OFNA_ENDOSO,POLIZA_ENDOSO,NUMENDOSO_ENDOSO,FORPAGEND_ENDOSO,TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO,DESCVOL_ENDOSO,PRINETA_ENDOSO,RECARGO_ENDOSO,GASTOS_ENDOSO,IMPORIMP_ENDOSO,PRIMATOT_ENDOSO,FECHEMIS_ENDOSO
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDENDOSO
GROUP BY OFNA_ENDOSO,POLIZA_ENDOSO,NUMENDOSO_ENDOSO,FORPAGEND_ENDOSO,TIPOENDOSO_ENDOSO,DESCVOL_ENDOSO,PRINETA_ENDOSO,RECARGO_ENDOSO,GASTOS_ENDOSO,IMPORIMP_ENDOSO,PRIMATOT_ENDOSO,FECHEMIS_ENDOSO
)SDENDOSO
ON SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA = SDENDOSO.OFNA_ENDOSO
AND SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA = SDENDOSO.POLIZA_ENDOSO
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SUBRAMO CAT_SUBRAMO
ON SDPOLIZA.SUBRAMO_POLIZA = CAT_SUBRAMO.PSRAMCOB
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDENDOSO.OFNA_ENDOSO ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDENDOSO.POLIZA_ENDOSO,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

CREATE  TABLE IF NOT EXISTS bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_sdendoso_cbza2 AS
SELECT
CAST(pol.POLORI_POLIZA        AS VARCHAR(14))                 NUM_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL                     AS smallint)                    VIGENCIA_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL                     AS INT)                         NUM_VERSION_POLIZA
, CAST(CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(pol.OFNA_POLIZA   AS VARCHAR(2)),2,"0"),
LPAD(CAST(pol.POLIZA_POLIZA AS VARCHAR(6)),6,"0"))
AS VARCHAR( 8))                                         NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA
, CAST(LPAD(CAST(sdendoso.NUMENDOSO_ENDOSO AS VARCHAR(6)),6,"0")
AS VARCHAR(6))                                          NUM_ENDOSO
, CAST(pol.idnom_cont_poliza    AS VARCHAR(10))                 CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN
, CAST('CBZA'                   AS VARCHAR( 4))                 CVE_SISTEMA
, CAST('CBZA'                   AS VARCHAR( 4))                 CVE_SISTEMA_INT
, CAST(pol.rfc_poliza           AS VARCHAR(16))                 RFC
, pol.nombre_poliza                                             NOMBRE
, pol.nombre_poliza                                             RAZON_SOCIAL
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(75))                 CORREO_ELECTRONICO
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(20))                 CURP
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR( 3))                 CVE_PAIS_NACIMIENTO
, CAST(NULL                     AS STRING)                      NACIONALIDAD
, CAST(NULL                     AS STRING)                      NACIONALIDAD_RESIDENCIA
, CAST(
CASE
WHEN (lg_rfc > 3 AND regexp_extract(substr(pol.rfc_poliza,1,4), '^[A-Za-z]*$', 0) <> '')
THEN 'F'
WHEN (lg_rfc > 3 AND regexp_extract(substr(pol.rfc_poliza,1,4), '^[A-Za-z]*$', 0) = '')
THEN 'J'
ELSE NULL
END  AS VARCHAR( 1)
)                                                           CVE_TIPO
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR( 1))                 CVE_SEXO
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR( 1))                 CVE_ESTATUS
, CAST(pol.telefono_poliza      AS VARCHAR(75))                 TELEFONO1
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(75))                 TELEFONO2
, pol.fechemipoliza                                             FCH_ALTA
, CAST(NULL                     AS DECIMAL(8,0))                FCH_BAJA
, CAST(NULL                     AS TIMESTAMP)                   FECHAAUD
, CAST('C2'                     AS VARCHAR(2))                  ORI_CONTRATANTE
, sdendoso.fechaaud                                             TSULTMOD_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(32))                 IDMD5
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(32))                 IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,conendoso_poliza,idnom_cont_poliza,rfc_poliza,nombre_poliza,telefono_poliza,fechemipoliza, LENGTH(rfc_poliza) lg_rfc
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,conendoso_poliza,idnom_cont_poliza,rfc_poliza,nombre_poliza,telefono_poliza,fechemipoliza
) pol
INNER JOIN
(SELECT OFNA_ENDOSO,POLIZA_ENDOSO,NUMENDOSO_ENDOSO
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist, MAX(fechaaud) fechaaud
FROM BDDLCRU.SDENDOSO
GROUP BY OFNA_ENDOSO,POLIZA_ENDOSO,NUMENDOSO_ENDOSO
)SDENDOSO ON
pol.OFNA_POLIZA     = SDENDOSO.OFNA_ENDOSO
AND pol.POLIZA_POLIZA   = SDENDOSO.POLIZA_ENDOSO

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_ASEGURADO_DATOS_ADICIONALES STORED AS RCFile AS
SELECT
IF(NUM_POLIZA IS NULL,'',NUM_POLIZA)                                               AS NUM_POLIZA,
CAST(IF(VIGENCIA_POLIZA IS NULL,'',VIGENCIA_POLIZA) AS SMALLINT)                   AS VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
IF(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA IS NULL,'',NUM_VERSION_POLIZA)                               AS NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
IF(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA IS NULL,'',NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA)                             AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
IF(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN IS NULL,'',TRIM(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN))                         AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
CVE_SISTEMA_INT                                                                    AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
CVE_SISTEMA                                                                        AS CVE_SISTEMA,
IF(IND_CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL IS NULL,'',IND_CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL)                 AS IND_CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL,
IF(CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL IS NULL,'',CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL)                         AS CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL,
IF(CAST(IND_OBJETO AS INT) IS NULL,0,IND_OBJETO)                                   AS IND_OBJETO,
IF(CVE_ZONA_TARIFICACION IS NULL,'',CVE_ZONA_TARIFICACION)                         AS CVE_ZONA_TARIFICACION,
IF(ZONA_TARIFICACION IS NULL,'',ZONA_TARIFICACION)                                 AS ZONA_TARIFICACION,
IF(CODIGO_POSTAL_TARIFICACION IS NULL,'',CODIGO_POSTAL_TARIFICACION)               AS CODIGO_POSTAL_TARIFICACION,
IF(POBLACION IS NULL,'',POBLACION)                                                 AS POBLACION,
IF(ESTADO IS NULL,'',ESTADO)                                                       AS ESTADO,
IF(APELLIDO_PATERNO IS NULL,'',APELLIDO_PATERNO)                                   AS APELLIDO_PATERNO,
IF(APELLIDO_MATERNO IS NULL,'',APELLIDO_MATERNO)                                   AS APELLIDO_MATERNO,
IF(NOMBRE IS NULL,'',NOMBRE)                                                       AS NOMBRE,
IF(BAN_RIESGO_SELECTO IS NULL,'',BAN_RIESGO_SELECTO)                               AS BAN_RIESGO_SELECTO,
IF(CVE_PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO IS NULL,'',CVE_PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO)               AS CVE_PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO,
IF(PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO IS NULL,'',PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO)                       AS PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO,
IF( FCH_ALTA  IS NULL OR FCH_ALTA <14000101,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ALTA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))          AS FCH_ALTA,
IF( FCH_BAJA IS NULL OR FCH_BAJA   <14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_BAJA   as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))        AS FCH_BAJA,
IF( FCH_INI_MOVIMIENTO  IS NULL OR FCH_INI_MOVIMIENTO  <14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_INI_MOVIMIENTO  as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))   AS FCH_INI_MOVIMIENTO,
IF( FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO IS NULL OR FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO <14000101  ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))  AS FCH_FIN_MOVIMIENTO,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD<14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC<14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT <14000101,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC_OT_CIA IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC_OT_CIA <14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC_OT_CIA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_NAC_OT_CIA,
IF( FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT_OT_CIA IS NULL OR FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT_OT_CIA <14000101,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT_OT_CIA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_INT_OT_CIA,
IF( FCH_NACIMIENTO IS NULL OR FCH_NACIMIENTO <14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_NACIMIENTO as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp))   AS FCH_NACIMIENTO,
CAST(IF(CVE_SEXO IS NULL,'',CVE_SEXO) AS VARCHAR(1))                                                 AS CVE_SEXO,
IF(SEXO IS NULL,'',SEXO)                                                           AS SEXO,
CAST(IF(CVE_SEXO IS NULL,'',CVE_ESTATUS_ASEGURADO) AS VARCHAR(1))                                                 AS CVE_ESTATUS_ASEGURADO,
IF(SEXO IS NULL,'',ESTATUS_ASEGURADO)                                                           AS ESTATUS_ASEGURADO,
CAST(IF(IND_ULT_SITUACION IS NULL,'',IND_ULT_SITUACION) AS CHAR(1))                AS IND_ULT_SITUACION,
IF(IND_TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE IS NULL,'',IND_TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE)                     AS IND_TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE,
IF(TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE IS NULL,'',TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE)                             AS TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE,
IF(IND_RELACION IS NULL,'',IND_RELACION)                                           AS IND_RELACION,
IF(RELACION IS NULL,'',RELACION)                                                   AS RELACION,
IF(IND_GRATUIDAD IS NULL,'',IND_GRATUIDAD)                                         AS IND_GRATUIDAD,
IF(GRATUIDAD IS NULL,'',GRATUIDAD)                                                 AS GRATUIDAD,
IF(CAST(EDAD_EQUIVALENTE AS STRING) IS NULL,'',EDAD_EQUIVALENTE)                   AS EDAD_EQUIVALENTE,
IF(CVE_ESTADO_CIVIL IS NULL,'',CVE_ESTADO_CIVIL)                                   AS CVE_ESTADO_CIVIL,
IF(ESTADO_CIVIL IS NULL,'',ESTADO_CIVIL)                                           AS ESTADO_CIVIL,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE AS STRING )                                       AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_DEPORTE AS STRING )                                       AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_DEPORTE,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LAB_DEP AS STRING )                                       AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LAB_DEP,
IF(IMP_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE IS NULL,'',IMP_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE)               AS IMP_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_LABORAL AS STRING )                                       AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_LABORAL,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LABORAL AS STRING )                                       AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LABORAL,
CAST( IF(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_OBESIDAD IS NULL, '0',PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_OBESIDAD) AS STRING ) AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_OBESIDAD,
CAST( IF(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_EDAD IS NULL, '0',PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_EDAD) AS STRING ) AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_EDAD,
IF(CVE_TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA IS NULL,'',CVE_TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA)             AS CVE_TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA,
IF(TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA IS NULL,'',TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA)                     AS TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA,
IF(VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_EDAD IS NULL,'',VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_EDAD)                             AS VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_EDAD,
IF( FCH_INI_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA IS NULL OR FCH_INI_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA<14000101  ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_INI_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_INI_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA,
IF( FCH_FIN_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA IS NULL OR FCH_FIN_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA<14000101 ,
cast('1400-01-01 00:00:00' as timestamp),
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(FCH_FIN_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA as varchar(8)), 'yyyyMMdd')) as timestamp)) AS FCH_FIN_POLIZA_OTRA_CIA,
IF(NOMBRE_OTRA_CIA IS NULL, '', NOMBRE_OTRA_CIA)                                   AS NOMBRE_OTRA_CIA,
CAST( PESO AS STRING )                                                             AS PESO,
CAST( TALLA AS STRING )                                                            AS TALLA,
IF(BAN_IMC IS NULL,'',BAN_IMC)                                                     AS BAN_IMC,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT AS STRING )                                               AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT,
CAST( PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN AS STRING )                                               AS PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN,
IF(CVE_TIPO_DICTAMEN IS NULL,'',CVE_TIPO_DICTAMEN)                                 AS CVE_TIPO_DICTAMEN,
IF(TIPO_DICTAMEN IS NULL,'',TIPO_DICTAMEN)                                         AS TIPO_DICTAMEN,
IF(CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE IS NULL,'',CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE)                       AS CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE,
CAST( IF(PCT_DESCUENTO IS NULL, 0, PCT_DESCUENTO)  AS STRING )                     AS PCT_DESCUENTO,
IF(BAN_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL IS NULL,'',BAN_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL)                       AS BAN_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL,
CAST( IMP_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL AS STRING )                                           AS IMP_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL,
IF(RFC_ASEGURADO IS NULL,'',RFC_ASEGURADO)                                         AS RFC_ASEGURADO,
IF(BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP IS NULL,'',BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP)                         AS BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP,
IF(BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL IS NULL,'',BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL)                             AS BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,
IF(VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL IS NULL,'',VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL)                             AS VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,
IF(DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL IS NULL,'',DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL)                                     AS DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP())  AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
CASE WHEN CVE_SISTEMA = 'INFO' THEN CAST(reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',CONCAT(NVL(NUM_POLIZA,''), CAST(NVL(VIGENCIA_POLIZA,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,0) AS STRING), NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''), NVL(CAST(IND_OBJETO AS STRING),''))) AS VARCHAR(32)) ELSE CAST(reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',CONCAT(NVL(NUM_POLIZA,''), CAST(NVL(VIGENCIA_POLIZA,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,0) AS STRING), NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''), NVL(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,''))) AS VARCHAR(32)) END AS IDMD5,
CAST(reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',CONCAT(NVL(NUM_POLIZA,''),NVL(VIGENCIA_POLIZA,0),NVL(NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,0),NVL(NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''),NVL(CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,''),NVL(IND_CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL,''),NVL(CAMBIO_GPO_INDIVIDUAL,''),NVL(IND_OBJETO,''),NVL(CVE_ZONA_TARIFICACION,''),NVL(ZONA_TARIFICACION,''),NVL(CODIGO_POSTAL_TARIFICACION,''),NVL(POBLACION,''),NVL(ESTADO,''),NVL(APELLIDO_PATERNO,''),NVL(APELLIDO_MATERNO,''),NVL(NOMBRE,''),NVL(BAN_RIESGO_SELECTO,''),NVL(CVE_PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO,''),NVL(PERIODO_RIESGO_SELECTO,''),NVL(CVE_SEXO,''),NVL(SEXO,''),NVL(IND_ULT_SITUACION,''),NVL(IND_TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE,''),NVL(TITULAR_DEPENDIENTE,''),NVL(IND_RELACION,''),NVL(RELACION,''),NVL(IND_GRATUIDAD,''),NVL(GRATUIDAD,''),NVL(EDAD_EQUIVALENTE,0),NVL(CVE_ESTADO_CIVIL,''),NVL(ESTADO_CIVIL,''),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_DEPORTE,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LAB_DEP,0),NVL(IMP_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_DEPORTE,''),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_LABORAL,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN_LABORAL,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_OBESIDAD,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT_EDAD,0),NVL(CVE_TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA,''),NVL(TEMPORALIDAD_EXTRAPRIMA,''),NVL(VAL_EXTRAPRIMA_EDAD,''),NVL(NOMBRE_OTRA_CIA,''),NVL(PESO,0),NVL(TALLA,0),NVL(BAN_IMC,''),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_AUT,0),NVL(PCT_EXTRAPRIMA_MAN,0),NVL(CVE_TIPO_DICTAMEN,''),NVL(TIPO_DICTAMEN,''),NVL(CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE,''),NVL(PCT_DESCUENTO,0),NVL(BAN_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL,''),NVL(IMP_DERECHO_POL_MANUAL,0),NVL(RFC_ASEGURADO,''),NVL(BAN_PENALIZACION_HOSP,''),NVL(BAN_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,''),NVL(VAL_DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,''),NVL(DEDUCIBLE_ANUAL,''))
)AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_UNION_ASEG_AD

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_CBZA_POLIZA as
SELECT
SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),1,6) AS anio_mes_contable
,CAST('1400-01-01 00:00:00' AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_contable
,CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) AS num_poliza
,-999 AS vigencia_poliza
,-999 AS num_version_poliza
,CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) AS num_poliza_cobranza
,'000000' AS num_endoso
,SDPOLIZA.FORMAPAGO_POLIZA AS cve_forma_pago
,'' AS cve_tipo_endoso
,0 AS mto_prima_tecnica
,SDPOLIZA.DESCVOL_POLIZA/100 AS mto_recargo_descuento
,SDPOLIZA.PRINETA_POLIZA/100 AS mto_prima_neta
,SDPOLIZA.RECARGO_POLIZA/100 AS mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado
,0 AS pct_pago_prima
,SDPOLIZA.PRINETA_POLIZA/100 AS mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc
,0 AS mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago
,SDPOLIZA.GASTOS_POLIZA/100 AS mto_derecho_poliza
,0 AS mto_cesion_comision
,SDPOLIZA.IMPORIMP_POLIZA/100 AS mto_iva_poliza
,SDPOLIZA.PRINETA_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.RECARGO_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.IMPORIMP_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.DESCVOL_POLIZA/100 + SDPOLIZA.GASTOS_POLIZA/100 AS mto_prima_total
,COALESCE(CAT_SUBRAMO.SUBSUBCO,'') AS cve_cobertura_contable
,CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),1,4),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),5,2),'-',SUBSTRING(CAST(SDPOLIZA.FECHEMIPOLIZA AS STRING),7,2),' 00:00:00') AS TIMESTAMP) AS fch_emision
,nvl(EMAZ.segmento, '') as segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_segmento, '') as desc_segmento
,nvl(EMAZ.negocio, '') as negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_negocio, '') as desc_negocio
,nvl(EMAZ.bonos, '') as bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_bonos, '') as desc_bonos
,nvl(EMAZ.plan_incentivos, '') as plan_incentivos
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_contr, '') as pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr, '') as desc_pol_contr
,nvl(EMAZ.contrb, '') as contrb
,nvl(EMAZ.pol_prest, '') as pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest, '') as desc_pol_prest
,nvl(EMAZ.mot_exc, '') as mot_exc
,nvl(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc, '') as desc_mot_exc
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,FORMAPAGO_POLIZA,DESCVOL_POLIZA,PRINETA_POLIZA,RECARGO_POLIZA,GASTOS_POLIZA,IMPORIMP_POLIZA,FECHEMIPOLIZA,SUBRAMO_POLIZA
)SDPOLIZA
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SUBRAMO CAT_SUBRAMO
ON SDPOLIZA.SUBRAMO_POLIZA = CAT_SUBRAMO.PSRAMCOB
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on  CAST(SDPOLIZA.POLORI_POLIZA AS STRING) = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.OFNA_POLIZA ,0) AS VARCHAR(2)),2,'0'), LPAD(CAST(COALESCE(SDPOLIZA.POLIZA_POLIZA,0) AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0')) =  trim(EMAZ.cobranza)

CREATE  TABLE IF NOT EXISTS bddlint.stg_gmm_contratante_sdpoliza_cbza1 AS
SELECT
CAST(pol.POLORI_POLIZA        AS VARCHAR(14))                 NUM_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL                     AS smallint)                    VIGENCIA_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL                     AS INT)                         NUM_VERSION_POLIZA
, CAST(CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(pol.OFNA_POLIZA   AS VARCHAR(2)),2,"0"),
LPAD(CAST(pol.POLIZA_POLIZA AS VARCHAR(6)),6,"0"))
AS VARCHAR( 8))                                         NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA
, CAST('000000' AS VARCHAR(6))                                  NUM_ENDOSO
, CAST(pol.idnom_cont_poliza    AS VARCHAR(10))                 CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN
, CAST('CBZA'                   AS VARCHAR( 4))                 CVE_SISTEMA
, CAST('CBZA'                   AS VARCHAR( 4))                 CVE_SISTEMA_INT
, CAST(pol.rfc_poliza           AS VARCHAR(16))                 RFC
, pol.nombre_poliza                                             NOMBRE
, pol.nombre_poliza                                             RAZON_SOCIAL
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(75))                 CORREO_ELECTRONICO
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(20))                 CURP
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR( 3))                 CVE_PAIS_NACIMIENTO
, CAST(NULL                     AS STRING)                      NACIONALIDAD
, CAST(NULL                     AS STRING)                      NACIONALIDAD_RESIDENCIA
, CAST(
CASE
WHEN (lg_rfc > 3 AND regexp_extract(substr(pol.rfc_poliza,1,4), '^[A-Za-z]*$', 0) <> '')
THEN 'F'
WHEN (lg_rfc > 3 AND regexp_extract(substr(pol.rfc_poliza,1,4), '^[A-Za-z]*$', 0) = '')
THEN 'J'
ELSE NULL
END  AS VARCHAR( 1)
)                                                           CVE_TIPO
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR( 1))                 CVE_SEXO
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR( 1))                 CVE_ESTATUS
, CAST(pol.telefono_poliza      AS VARCHAR(75))                 TELEFONO1
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(75))                 TELEFONO2
, pol.fechemipoliza                                             FCH_ALTA
, CAST(NULL                     AS DECIMAL(8,0))                FCH_BAJA
, CAST(NULL                     AS TIMESTAMP)                   FECHAAUD
, CAST('C1'                     AS VARCHAR(2))                  ORI_CONTRATANTE
, pol.fechaaud                                                  TSULTMOD_POLIZA
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(32))                 IDMD5
, CAST(NULL                     AS VARCHAR(32))                 IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM
(SELECT POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,conendoso_poliza,idnom_cont_poliza,rfc_poliza,nombre_poliza,telefono_poliza,fechemipoliza, LENGTH(rfc_poliza) lg_rfc
,MAX(id_hist) AS id_hist, MAX(fechaaud) fechaaud
FROM BDDLCRU.SDPOLIZA
GROUP BY POLORI_POLIZA,OFNA_POLIZA,POLIZA_POLIZA,conendoso_poliza,idnom_cont_poliza,rfc_poliza,nombre_poliza,telefono_poliza,fechemipoliza
) pol

((stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta / stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta ) * stg_1.mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado),0) as mto_importe_comision_total,

reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(CAST(NVL(stg_1.ANIO_MES_CONTABLE ,0) AS  STRING),NVL( stg_1.NUM_POLIZA,'') ,CAST(NVL(stg_1.VIGENCIA_POLIZA,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(stg_1.num_version_poliza,0) AS STRING),NVL(stg_1.NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,''),NVL(stg_1.NUM_ENDOSO,''),CAST(NVL(stg_1.CONTADOR_SECUENCIA_OBJETO,0) AS STRING),NVL(stg_1.CVE_COBERTURA_CONTRATADA,''),NVL(stg_1.DES_COBERTURA_CONTRATADA,''),NVL(stg_1.CVE_ASEGURADO,''),NVL(stg_1.IDENTIFICADOR_NVO_RENOVADO,''),NVL(stg_1.CVE_COBERTURA_CONTABLE,''),NVL(stg_1.FORMA_PAGO,''),CAST(NVL(stg_1.MTO_COMISION_PRIMA_NETA ,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(((stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta / stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta ) * stg_1.mto_comision_derecho_poliza) ,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(((stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta / stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta ) * stg_1.mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado) ,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(MTO_ISR_COMISIONES ,0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL((stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta +((stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta / stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta ) * stg_1.mto_comision_derecho_poliza)+((stg_1.mto_comision_prima_neta / stg_2.sum_comi_prima_neta ) * stg_1.mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado)) ,0) AS STRING),NVL(CVE_CANAL_VENTA_ALTERNO,''),CAST(NVL(PORCENTAJE_COMISION ,0) AS STRING),NVL(CVE_SISTEMA,''))) AS IDMD5COMPLETO ,
from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) as 	FECHAAUD ,
stg_1.recibo
from BDDLTRN.STG_COMISIONES_PAGADA_POLIZA_ASEGURADO stg_1
inner join
( select num_poliza,num_poliza_cobranza,num_endoso,recibo,sum(mto_comision_prima_neta) sum_comi_prima_neta

INSERT INTO BDDLTRN.STG_COMISIONES_PAGADA_POLIZA_ASEGURADO
select
CAST (amo_mes_conta AS INT)             					as anio_mes_contable,
case when fecha_contable = 0 or length (fecha_contable) <8 THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(fecha_contable as string) ,'yyyyMMdd'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) END fecha_contable ,
LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0')        		as num_poliza,
-999                                    					as vigencia_poliza,
-999                                    					as num_version_poliza,
LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0')         	as num_poliza_cobranza,
cast (ENDOSO AS varchar(6))             					as num_endoso,
0                                       					as contador_secuencia_objeto,
COBERTURA                               					as cve_cobertura_contratada,
NVL(CAT.DESCRIPCION,'')                         			as descr_cobertura_contratada,
CAST (CERTIFICADO AS varchar(10))       					as cve_asegurado,
CAST (IDEN_NEW_RENOV AS varchar(10))    					as identificador_nvo_renovado,
CASE WHEN poliza.cve_cobertura_contable IS NULL THEN   cnm_poliza.cve_cobertura_contable else  poliza.cve_cobertura_contable end as cve_cobertura_contable,
FORMA_PAGO                              					as forma_pago,
NVL(PRIMA*(porciento_com/100),0)               				as mto_comision_prima_neta,
NVL(comis_gastos,0)                            				as mto_comision_derecho_poliza,
NVL(comis_recargo,0)                           				as mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
0                                       					as mto_isr_comisiones,
NVL((comis_neta+comis_recargo+comis_gastos),0) 				as mto_importe_comision_total,
''                                      					as cve_identificador_intermediario,
''                                      					as des_identificador_intermediario,
case when fecha_pag = 0 or length (fecha_pag) <8 THEN cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE('1400-01-01'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) ELSE
cast(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(TO_DATE(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(cast(fecha_contable as string) ,'yyyyMMdd'), 'yyyy-MM-dd')), 'yyyy-MM-dd')) as TIMESTAMP) END as fecha_movimiento_comision,
''                                      					as cve_canal_venta_alterno,
NVL(porciento_com,0)                        				as porcentaje_comision,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.segmento), '') as segmento,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_segmento), '') as desc_segmento,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.negocio), '') as negocio,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_negocio), '') as desc_negocio,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.bonos), '') as bonos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_bonos), '') as desc_bonos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.plan_incentivos), '') as plan_incentivos,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.pol_contr), '') as pol_contr,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_pol_contr), '') as desc_pol_contr,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.contrb), '') as contrb,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.pol_prest), '') as pol_prest,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_pol_prest), '') as desc_pol_prest,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.mot_exc), '') as mot_exc,
nvl(trim(EMAZ.desc_mot_exc), '') as desc_mot_exc,
RECIBO														as Recibo,
CAST ("AZUL" AS varchar(20))            					as cve_sistema,
CAST ("AZUL" AS varchar(20))            					as cve_sistema_int,
amo_mes_conta                           					as periodo_proceso,
'pagada'                                					as tipo_comision
from (SELECT * FROM BDDLCRU.GAZ0_PAGOS_POLIZAS_FINAL PRIMA2
where amo_mes_conta = 201911
) PRIMA
LEFT JOIN
(select CVE_AZUL,DESCRIPCION from bddlcru.cat_hom_515_286_287_clave_cob_contratada_afectada where CVE_AZUL <> "") CAT
ON  TRIM(PRIMA.COBERTURA) = TRIM(CAT.CVE_AZUL)
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza,num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from  BDDLAPR.CNM_POLIZA_AZUL) poliza
ON  LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') =  poliza.num_poliza
and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = poliza.num_poliza_cobranza
LEFT JOIN
(select num_poliza_cobranza,cve_cobertura_contable from bddlapr.cnm_poliza where cve_sistema = 'CBZA') cnm_poliza
ON cnm_poliza.num_poliza_cobranza = LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0')
LEFT JOIN
(
select POLIZA, cobranza, '' as  SEGMENTO, NVL(SEGMENTO, '') AS desc_segmento, '' as NEGOCIO, NVL(NEGOCIO, '') AS desc_negocio, '' AS BONOS, NVL(BONOS, '') as desc_bonos, NVL(PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '') AS PLAN_INCENTIVOS, '' as POL_CONTR, NVL(POL_CONTR, '') AS desc_POL_CONTR, NVL(CONTRB, '') AS CONTRB, '' as POL_PREST, NVL(POL_PREST, '') AS desc_pol_prest, '' as mot_exc, '' as desc_mot_exc from BDDLCRU.EMAZETIQ
) EMAZ
on   LPAD(CAST (POLIZA_ORI AS varchar(14)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.POLIZA) and LPAD(CAST (PRIMA.POLIZA_COB AS varchar(8)),8,'0') = trim(EMAZ.cobranza)
