END
)
END
ELSE ''
END AS RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCT),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCR),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.CDRFC,'')) AS RFC_HOSPITAL,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNNOMRZS,'')) AS NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP1RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP2RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FERESDIC = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FERESDIC) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FERESDIC,10000101) END AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(KACM50T.INRESDIC,'') AS CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
KACM54T.VADEDNAP AS MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
'MXP' AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
KACM50T.POCOASHM AS PCT_COASEGURO,
KACM50T.POCOASGH AS PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP,
KACM50T.PORECARG AS PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
KACM50T.POCOAADI AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
KACM50T.POCOAGFH AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
KACM51T.CTNUICD  as CTNUICD,
KACA53T.CDSECUEN AS CDSECUEN
FROM
(
SELECT KSI.*, KCI.inancaco
FROM (
SELECT CDSINIES,INAPSLCF,FECOMUNI,FEOCUSIN,TCSITSIN,TCMOTTER,CDNUMPOL,CTVRSPOL,CDINTERM,CTSECOBJ
FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM10T
WHERE TCTIPSIN = 'SA'
AND fechaaud > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) KSI
JOIN (SELECT cdnumpol,CTVRSPOL,inancaco FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T WHERE cdciagru = 'SA') KCI
ON  KCI.cdnumpol = KSI.cdnumpol
AND KCI.CTVRSPOL = KSI.CTVRSPOL
) KSIM10T
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM50T KACM50T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KSIA12T KSIA12T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN (SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,TCCDICD,INPRINCI,CTNUICD
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM51T WHERE INPRINCI = 'S' ) KACM51T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES =  KACM51T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN =  KACM51T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM54T KACM54T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM54T.CDSINIES
AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM54T.CTNUPOIN   AND  KACM50T.CDMCT = KACM54T.CDMCT    AND  KACM50T.CDMCR = KACM54T.CDMCR
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM56T KACM56T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM56T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM56T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CASE WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(INSIANTE),'') = 'S' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) >= 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM57T  GROUP BY CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN ) KACM57T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM57T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM57T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_MEDT
ON KACM50T.CDFILDOC = KPEM08T_MEDT.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CDSINIES,TCPEROBJ,CDFILIAC FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM20T where TCPEROBJ = 'ASG') KSIM20T_ASG
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KSIM20T_ASG.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_ASG
ON KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC = KPEM08T_ASG.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_PROV
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = KPEM08T_PROV.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN
(select DNNOMRZS,DNAP1RZS,DNAP2RZS,CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CDSECUEN from BDDLCRU.KACA53T  where INMEDTRA = 'S' ) KACA53T
ON KACA53T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES	AND KACA53T.CTNUPOIN = KACM50T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTRPV0 NPMTRPV0
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = NPMTRPV0.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTHOS0 NPMTHOS0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTHOS0.HOS_RFC) AND NPMTRPV0.RPV_SCR_CVE = NPMTHOS0.HOS_SCR_CVE
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTSAU0 NPMTSAU0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTSAU0.SAU_RFC_PEE)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_INFO
SELECT DISTINCT
KSIM10T.CDSINIES			AS ID_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDNUMPOL),'') AS NUM_POLIZA,
COALESCE(KSIM10T.CTVRSPOL,-999) AS NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
KSIM10T.inancaco AS VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
'' AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
-999 AS NUM_RENOVACION_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
COALESCE(KSIM10T.CTSECOBJ, -999) AS CONTADOR_SECUENCIA_OBJETO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC),'') AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
KACM50T.CDRECICD 			AS NUM_RECLAMACION,
-999 						AS CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,
NVL(KACM50T.TCMODALI, '')	AS CVE_MODALIDAD,
KSIA12T.CDSINIZU			AS FOLIO_SOLICITUD,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNNOMRZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNNOMRZS,'')) END AS NOMBRE_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNAP1RZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNAP1RZS,'')) END AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNAP2RZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNAP2RZS,'')) END AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN COALESCE(TRIM(KPEM08T_MEDT.CDRFC),'')
ELSE '' END AS RFC_MEDICO_TRATANTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.TCCDICD),'') AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.INAPSLCF),'') AS IND_TRAMITE_FONDO_CASHFLOW,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS),'') AS CVE_HOSPITAL_ORIGEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCCDCMED),'') AS CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INACCIDE),'')='S' THEN 'AC' ELSE 'EN' END AS CVE_TIPO_EVENTO,
COALESCE(CAST(KACM50T.VAHOSPI AS STRING),'') AS CVE_NIVEL_HOSPITALARIO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEINGRES = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEINGRES) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEINGRES < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEINGRES,10000101) END AS FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEEGRES = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEEGRES) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEEGRES,10000101) END AS FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN KSIM10T.FECOMUNI = 0 OR LENGTH(KSIM10T.FECOMUNI) < 8 OR KSIM10T.FECOMUNI < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KSIM10T.FECOMUNI,10000101) END AS FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN = 0 OR LENGTH(KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN,10000101) END AS FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.INPRINCI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.INPRINCI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '3' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAE,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '2' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '1' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAB,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_URGENCIA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCADMIS),'') AS CVE_TIPO_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_READMISION,
COALESCE(KACM50T.NUDIAINT,-999) AS NUM_DIAS_TERAPIA_INTENSIVA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDCAUACC),'') AS CVE_CAUSA_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDLUGACC),'') AS CVE_UBICACION_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDACTDEP),'') AS CVE_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(KACM57T.BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,-1) AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTMAD = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTMAD ) < 8 OR KACM56T.FEANTMAD < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTMAD,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTTIT = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTTIT ) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTTIT,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_MAMA_BIEN,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_BEBE_BIEN,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGIN,-999) AS CALIFICACION_INICIAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGFI,-999) AS CALIFICACION_FINAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INESTVAL),'') AS CVE_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEESTVAL = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEESTVAL) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEESTVAL,10000101) END AS FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPRIVIS = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS,10000101) END AS FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS,240101) IN (0,240101) THEN '00:00:00' ELSE
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),1,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),3,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),5,2))
END AS HR_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPROME = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPROME) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEPROME < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPROME,10000101) END AS FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.NUMHABIT),'') AS NUM_HABITACION_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INRESDIC),'') AS CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCSITSIN),'') AS CVE_SITUACION_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCMOTTER),'') AS CVE_MOTIVO_TERMINACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDINTERM),'') AS CVE_AGENTE,
'' AS CVE_DA_AGENTE,
-999 AS NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) = 0 THEN ''
WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) > 1 THEN
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA,''))
ELSE (CASE WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE = 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTHOS0.HOS_NOM,''))
WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE > 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTSAU0.SAU_NOM_PEE,''))
ELSE ''
END
)
END
ELSE ''
END AS RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCT),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCR),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.CDRFC,'')) AS RFC_HOSPITAL,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNNOMRZS,'')) AS NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP1RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP2RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FERESDIC = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FERESDIC) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FERESDIC,10000101) END AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(KACM50T.INRESDIC,'') AS CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
KACM54T.VADEDNAP AS MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
'MXP' AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
KACM50T.POCOASHM AS PCT_COASEGURO,
KACM50T.POCOASGH AS PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP,
KACM50T.PORECARG AS PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
KACM50T.POCOAADI AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
KACM50T.POCOAGFH AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
KACM51T.CTNUICD  as CTNUICD,
KACA53T.CDSECUEN AS CDSECUEN
FROM
(
SELECT KSI.*, KCI.inancaco
FROM (
SELECT CDSINIES,INAPSLCF,FECOMUNI,FEOCUSIN,TCSITSIN,TCMOTTER,CDNUMPOL,CTVRSPOL,CDINTERM,CTSECOBJ
FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM10T
WHERE TCTIPSIN = 'SA'
AND fechaaud > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) KSI
JOIN (SELECT cdnumpol,CTVRSPOL,inancaco FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T WHERE cdciagru = 'SA') KCI
ON  KCI.cdnumpol = KSI.cdnumpol
AND KCI.CTVRSPOL = KSI.CTVRSPOL
) KSIM10T
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM50T KACM50T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KSIA12T KSIA12T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN (SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,TCCDICD,INPRINCI,CTNUICD
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM51T WHERE INPRINCI = 'S' ) KACM51T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES =  KACM51T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN =  KACM51T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM54T KACM54T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM54T.CDSINIES
AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM54T.CTNUPOIN   AND  KACM50T.CDMCT = KACM54T.CDMCT    AND  KACM50T.CDMCR = KACM54T.CDMCR
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM56T KACM56T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM56T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM56T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CASE WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(INSIANTE),'') = 'S' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) >= 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM57T  GROUP BY CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN ) KACM57T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM57T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM57T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_MEDT
ON KACM50T.CDFILDOC = KPEM08T_MEDT.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CDSINIES,TCPEROBJ,CDFILIAC FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM20T where TCPEROBJ = 'ASG') KSIM20T_ASG
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KSIM20T_ASG.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_ASG
ON KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC = KPEM08T_ASG.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_PROV
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = KPEM08T_PROV.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN
(select DNNOMRZS,DNAP1RZS,DNAP2RZS,CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CDSECUEN from BDDLCRU.KACA53T  where INMEDTRA = 'S' ) KACA53T
ON KACA53T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES	AND KACA53T.CTNUPOIN = KACM50T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTRPV0 NPMTRPV0
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = NPMTRPV0.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTHOS0 NPMTHOS0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTHOS0.HOS_RFC) AND NPMTRPV0.RPV_SCR_CVE = NPMTHOS0.HOS_SCR_CVE
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTSAU0 NPMTSAU0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTSAU0.SAU_RFC_PEE)

ELSE -1 END AS BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA,

WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '1' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAB,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='S' THEN 1

ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE,

WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_URGENCIA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCADMIS),'') AS CVE_TIPO_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_READMISION,
COALESCE(KACM50T.NUDIAINT,-999) AS NUM_DIAS_TERAPIA_INTENSIVA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDCAUACC),'') AS CVE_CAUSA_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDLUGACC),'') AS CVE_UBICACION_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDACTDEP),'') AS CVE_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(KACM57T.BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,-1) AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTMAD = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTMAD ) < 8 OR KACM56T.FEANTMAD < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTMAD,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTTIT = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTTIT ) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTTIT,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_MAMA_BIEN,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_BEBE_BIEN,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGIN,-999) AS CALIFICACION_INICIAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGFI,-999) AS CALIFICACION_FINAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INESTVAL),'') AS CVE_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEESTVAL = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEESTVAL) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEESTVAL,10000101) END AS FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPRIVIS = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS,10000101) END AS FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS,240101) IN (0,240101) THEN '00:00:00' ELSE
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),1,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),3,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),5,2))
END AS HR_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPROME = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPROME) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEPROME < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPROME,10000101) END AS FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.NUMHABIT),'') AS NUM_HABITACION_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INRESDIC),'') AS CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCSITSIN),'') AS CVE_SITUACION_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCMOTTER),'') AS CVE_MOTIVO_TERMINACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDINTERM),'') AS CVE_AGENTE,
'' AS CVE_DA_AGENTE,
-999 AS NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) = 0 THEN ''
WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) > 1 THEN
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA,''))
ELSE (CASE WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE = 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTHOS0.HOS_NOM,''))
WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE > 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTSAU0.SAU_NOM_PEE,''))
ELSE ''
END
)
END
ELSE ''
END AS RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCT),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCR),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.CDRFC,'')) AS RFC_HOSPITAL,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNNOMRZS,'')) AS NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP1RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP2RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FERESDIC = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FERESDIC) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FERESDIC,10000101) END AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(KACM50T.INRESDIC,'') AS CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
KACM54T.VADEDNAP AS MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
'MXP' AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
KACM50T.POCOASHM AS PCT_COASEGURO,
KACM50T.POCOASGH AS PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP,
KACM50T.PORECARG AS PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
KACM50T.POCOAADI AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
KACM50T.POCOAGFH AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
KACM51T.CTNUICD  as CTNUICD,
KACA53T.CDSECUEN AS CDSECUEN
FROM
(
SELECT KSI.*, KCI.inancaco
FROM (
SELECT CDSINIES,INAPSLCF,FECOMUNI,FEOCUSIN,TCSITSIN,TCMOTTER,CDNUMPOL,CTVRSPOL,CDINTERM,CTSECOBJ
FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM10T
WHERE TCTIPSIN = 'SA'
AND fechaaud > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) KSI
JOIN (SELECT cdnumpol,CTVRSPOL,inancaco FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T WHERE cdciagru = 'SA') KCI
ON  KCI.cdnumpol = KSI.cdnumpol
AND KCI.CTVRSPOL = KSI.CTVRSPOL
) KSIM10T
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM50T KACM50T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KSIA12T KSIA12T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN (SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,TCCDICD,INPRINCI,CTNUICD
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM51T WHERE INPRINCI = 'S' ) KACM51T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES =  KACM51T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN =  KACM51T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM54T KACM54T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM54T.CDSINIES
AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM54T.CTNUPOIN   AND  KACM50T.CDMCT = KACM54T.CDMCT    AND  KACM50T.CDMCR = KACM54T.CDMCR
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM56T KACM56T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM56T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM56T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CASE WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(INSIANTE),'') = 'S' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) >= 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM57T  GROUP BY CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN ) KACM57T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM57T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM57T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_MEDT
ON KACM50T.CDFILDOC = KPEM08T_MEDT.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CDSINIES,TCPEROBJ,CDFILIAC FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM20T where TCPEROBJ = 'ASG') KSIM20T_ASG
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KSIM20T_ASG.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_ASG
ON KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC = KPEM08T_ASG.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_PROV
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = KPEM08T_PROV.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN
(select DNNOMRZS,DNAP1RZS,DNAP2RZS,CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CDSECUEN from BDDLCRU.KACA53T  where INMEDTRA = 'S' ) KACA53T
ON KACA53T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES	AND KACA53T.CTNUPOIN = KACM50T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTRPV0 NPMTRPV0
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = NPMTRPV0.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTHOS0 NPMTHOS0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTHOS0.HOS_RFC) AND NPMTRPV0.RPV_SCR_CVE = NPMTHOS0.HOS_SCR_CVE
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTSAU0 NPMTSAU0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTSAU0.SAU_RFC_PEE)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_INFO
SELECT DISTINCT
KSIM10T.CDSINIES			AS ID_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDNUMPOL),'') AS NUM_POLIZA,
COALESCE(KSIM10T.CTVRSPOL,-999) AS NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
KSIM10T.inancaco AS VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
'' AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
-999 AS NUM_RENOVACION_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
COALESCE(KSIM10T.CTSECOBJ, -999) AS CONTADOR_SECUENCIA_OBJETO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC),'') AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,

'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNNOMRZS,''))

CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNAP1RZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNAP1RZS,'')) END AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNAP2RZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNAP2RZS,'')) END AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN COALESCE(TRIM(KPEM08T_MEDT.CDRFC),'')
ELSE '' END AS RFC_MEDICO_TRATANTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.TCCDICD),'') AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.INAPSLCF),'') AS IND_TRAMITE_FONDO_CASHFLOW,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS),'') AS CVE_HOSPITAL_ORIGEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCCDCMED),'') AS CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INACCIDE),'')='S' THEN 'AC' ELSE 'EN' END AS CVE_TIPO_EVENTO,
COALESCE(CAST(KACM50T.VAHOSPI AS STRING),'') AS CVE_NIVEL_HOSPITALARIO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEINGRES = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEINGRES) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEINGRES < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEINGRES,10000101) END AS FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEEGRES = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEEGRES) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEEGRES,10000101) END AS FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN KSIM10T.FECOMUNI = 0 OR LENGTH(KSIM10T.FECOMUNI) < 8 OR KSIM10T.FECOMUNI < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KSIM10T.FECOMUNI,10000101) END AS FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN = 0 OR LENGTH(KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN,10000101) END AS FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.INPRINCI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.INPRINCI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '3' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAE,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '2' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '1' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAB,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_URGENCIA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCADMIS),'') AS CVE_TIPO_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_READMISION,
COALESCE(KACM50T.NUDIAINT,-999) AS NUM_DIAS_TERAPIA_INTENSIVA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDCAUACC),'') AS CVE_CAUSA_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDLUGACC),'') AS CVE_UBICACION_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDACTDEP),'') AS CVE_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(KACM57T.BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,-1) AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTMAD = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTMAD ) < 8 OR KACM56T.FEANTMAD < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTMAD,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTTIT = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTTIT ) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTTIT,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_MAMA_BIEN,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_BEBE_BIEN,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGIN,-999) AS CALIFICACION_INICIAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGFI,-999) AS CALIFICACION_FINAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INESTVAL),'') AS CVE_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEESTVAL = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEESTVAL) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEESTVAL,10000101) END AS FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPRIVIS = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS,10000101) END AS FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS,240101) IN (0,240101) THEN '00:00:00' ELSE
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),1,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),3,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),5,2))
END AS HR_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPROME = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPROME) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEPROME < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPROME,10000101) END AS FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.NUMHABIT),'') AS NUM_HABITACION_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INRESDIC),'') AS CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCSITSIN),'') AS CVE_SITUACION_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCMOTTER),'') AS CVE_MOTIVO_TERMINACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDINTERM),'') AS CVE_AGENTE,
'' AS CVE_DA_AGENTE,
-999 AS NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) = 0 THEN ''
WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) > 1 THEN
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA,''))
ELSE (CASE WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE = 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTHOS0.HOS_NOM,''))

END
)
END
ELSE ''
END AS RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCT),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCR),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.CDRFC,'')) AS RFC_HOSPITAL,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNNOMRZS,'')) AS NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP1RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP2RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FERESDIC = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FERESDIC) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FERESDIC,10000101) END AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(KACM50T.INRESDIC,'') AS CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
KACM54T.VADEDNAP AS MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
'MXP' AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
KACM50T.POCOASHM AS PCT_COASEGURO,
KACM50T.POCOASGH AS PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP,
KACM50T.PORECARG AS PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
KACM50T.POCOAADI AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
KACM50T.POCOAGFH AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
KACM51T.CTNUICD  as CTNUICD,
KACA53T.CDSECUEN AS CDSECUEN
FROM
(
SELECT KSI.*, KCI.inancaco
FROM (
SELECT CDSINIES,INAPSLCF,FECOMUNI,FEOCUSIN,TCSITSIN,TCMOTTER,CDNUMPOL,CTVRSPOL,CDINTERM,CTSECOBJ
FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM10T
WHERE TCTIPSIN = 'SA'
AND fechaaud > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) KSI
JOIN (SELECT cdnumpol,CTVRSPOL,inancaco FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T WHERE cdciagru = 'SA') KCI
ON  KCI.cdnumpol = KSI.cdnumpol
AND KCI.CTVRSPOL = KSI.CTVRSPOL
) KSIM10T
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM50T KACM50T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KSIA12T KSIA12T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN (SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,TCCDICD,INPRINCI,CTNUICD
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM51T WHERE INPRINCI = 'S' ) KACM51T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES =  KACM51T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN =  KACM51T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM54T KACM54T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM54T.CDSINIES
AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM54T.CTNUPOIN   AND  KACM50T.CDMCT = KACM54T.CDMCT    AND  KACM50T.CDMCR = KACM54T.CDMCR
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM56T KACM56T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM56T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM56T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CASE WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(INSIANTE),'') = 'S' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) >= 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM57T  GROUP BY CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN ) KACM57T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM57T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM57T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_MEDT
ON KACM50T.CDFILDOC = KPEM08T_MEDT.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CDSINIES,TCPEROBJ,CDFILIAC FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM20T where TCPEROBJ = 'ASG') KSIM20T_ASG
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KSIM20T_ASG.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_ASG
ON KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC = KPEM08T_ASG.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_PROV
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = KPEM08T_PROV.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN
(select DNNOMRZS,DNAP1RZS,DNAP2RZS,CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CDSECUEN from BDDLCRU.KACA53T  where INMEDTRA = 'S' ) KACA53T
ON KACA53T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES	AND KACA53T.CTNUPOIN = KACM50T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTRPV0 NPMTRPV0
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = NPMTRPV0.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTHOS0 NPMTHOS0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTHOS0.HOS_RFC) AND NPMTRPV0.RPV_SCR_CVE = NPMTHOS0.HOS_SCR_CVE
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTSAU0 NPMTSAU0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTSAU0.SAU_RFC_PEE)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_INFO
SELECT DISTINCT
KSIM10T.CDSINIES			AS ID_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDNUMPOL),'') AS NUM_POLIZA,
COALESCE(KSIM10T.CTVRSPOL,-999) AS NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
KSIM10T.inancaco AS VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
'' AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
-999 AS NUM_RENOVACION_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
COALESCE(KSIM10T.CTSECOBJ, -999) AS CONTADOR_SECUENCIA_OBJETO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC),'') AS CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
KACM50T.CDRECICD 			AS NUM_RECLAMACION,
-999 						AS CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,
NVL(KACM50T.TCMODALI, '')	AS CVE_MODALIDAD,
KSIA12T.CDSINIZU			AS FOLIO_SOLICITUD,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
'INFO' AS CVE_SISTEMA,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNNOMRZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNNOMRZS,'')) END AS NOMBRE_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNAP1RZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNAP1RZS,'')) END AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_MEDT.DNAP2RZS,''))
ELSE TRIM(COALESCE(KACA53T.DNAP2RZS,'')) END AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILDOC)) > 1 THEN COALESCE(TRIM(KPEM08T_MEDT.CDRFC),'')
ELSE '' END AS RFC_MEDICO_TRATANTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.TCCDICD),'') AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.INAPSLCF),'') AS IND_TRAMITE_FONDO_CASHFLOW,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS),'') AS CVE_HOSPITAL_ORIGEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCCDCMED),'') AS CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INACCIDE),'')='S' THEN 'AC' ELSE 'EN' END AS CVE_TIPO_EVENTO,
COALESCE(CAST(KACM50T.VAHOSPI AS STRING),'') AS CVE_NIVEL_HOSPITALARIO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEINGRES = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEINGRES) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEINGRES < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEINGRES,10000101) END AS FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEEGRES = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEEGRES) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEEGRES,10000101) END AS FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN KSIM10T.FECOMUNI = 0 OR LENGTH(KSIM10T.FECOMUNI) < 8 OR KSIM10T.FECOMUNI < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KSIM10T.FECOMUNI,10000101) END AS FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN = 0 OR LENGTH(KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KSIM10T.FEOCUSIN,10000101) END AS FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.INPRINCI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM51T.INPRINCI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '3' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAE,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '2' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '0' THEN 0
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '1' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAB,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_URGENCIA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCADMIS),'') AS CVE_TIPO_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_READMISION,
COALESCE(KACM50T.NUDIAINT,-999) AS NUM_DIAS_TERAPIA_INTENSIVA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDCAUACC),'') AS CVE_CAUSA_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDLUGACC),'') AS CVE_UBICACION_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDACTDEP),'') AS CVE_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(KACM57T.BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,-1) AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTMAD = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTMAD ) < 8 OR KACM56T.FEANTMAD < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTMAD,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTTIT = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTTIT ) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTTIT,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_MAMA_BIEN,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_BEBE_BIEN,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGIN,-999) AS CALIFICACION_INICIAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGFI,-999) AS CALIFICACION_FINAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INESTVAL),'') AS CVE_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEESTVAL = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEESTVAL) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEESTVAL,10000101) END AS FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPRIVIS = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS,10000101) END AS FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS,240101) IN (0,240101) THEN '00:00:00' ELSE
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),1,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),3,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),5,2))
END AS HR_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPROME = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPROME) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEPROME < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPROME,10000101) END AS FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.NUMHABIT),'') AS NUM_HABITACION_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INRESDIC),'') AS CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCSITSIN),'') AS CVE_SITUACION_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCMOTTER),'') AS CVE_MOTIVO_TERMINACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDINTERM),'') AS CVE_AGENTE,
'' AS CVE_DA_AGENTE,
-999 AS NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) = 0 THEN ''
WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) > 1 THEN
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA,''))
ELSE (CASE WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE = 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTHOS0.HOS_NOM,''))
WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE > 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTSAU0.SAU_NOM_PEE,''))
ELSE ''
END
)
END
ELSE ''
END AS RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCT),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCR),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.CDRFC,'')) AS RFC_HOSPITAL,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNNOMRZS,'')) AS NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP1RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP2RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FERESDIC = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FERESDIC) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FERESDIC,10000101) END AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(KACM50T.INRESDIC,'') AS CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
KACM54T.VADEDNAP AS MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
'MXP' AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
KACM50T.POCOASHM AS PCT_COASEGURO,
KACM50T.POCOASGH AS PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP,
KACM50T.PORECARG AS PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
KACM50T.POCOAADI AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
KACM50T.POCOAGFH AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
KACM51T.CTNUICD  as CTNUICD,
KACA53T.CDSECUEN AS CDSECUEN
FROM
(
SELECT KSI.*, KCI.inancaco
FROM (
SELECT CDSINIES,INAPSLCF,FECOMUNI,FEOCUSIN,TCSITSIN,TCMOTTER,CDNUMPOL,CTVRSPOL,CDINTERM,CTSECOBJ
FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM10T
WHERE TCTIPSIN = 'SA'
AND fechaaud > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) KSI
JOIN (SELECT cdnumpol,CTVRSPOL,inancaco FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T WHERE cdciagru = 'SA') KCI
ON  KCI.cdnumpol = KSI.cdnumpol
AND KCI.CTVRSPOL = KSI.CTVRSPOL
) KSIM10T
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM50T KACM50T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KSIA12T KSIA12T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN (SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,TCCDICD,INPRINCI,CTNUICD
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM51T WHERE INPRINCI = 'S' ) KACM51T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES =  KACM51T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN =  KACM51T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM54T KACM54T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM54T.CDSINIES
AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM54T.CTNUPOIN   AND  KACM50T.CDMCT = KACM54T.CDMCT    AND  KACM50T.CDMCR = KACM54T.CDMCR
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM56T KACM56T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM56T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM56T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CASE WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(INSIANTE),'') = 'S' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) >= 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM57T  GROUP BY CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN ) KACM57T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM57T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM57T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_MEDT
ON KACM50T.CDFILDOC = KPEM08T_MEDT.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CDSINIES,TCPEROBJ,CDFILIAC FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM20T where TCPEROBJ = 'ASG') KSIM20T_ASG
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KSIM20T_ASG.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_ASG
ON KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC = KPEM08T_ASG.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_PROV
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = KPEM08T_PROV.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN
(select DNNOMRZS,DNAP1RZS,DNAP2RZS,CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CDSECUEN from BDDLCRU.KACA53T  where INMEDTRA = 'S' ) KACA53T
ON KACA53T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES	AND KACA53T.CTNUPOIN = KACM50T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTRPV0 NPMTRPV0
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = NPMTRPV0.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTHOS0 NPMTHOS0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTHOS0.HOS_RFC) AND NPMTRPV0.RPV_SCR_CVE = NPMTHOS0.HOS_SCR_CVE
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTSAU0 NPMTSAU0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTSAU0.SAU_RFC_PEE)

ELSE -1 END AS BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA,

WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INCBAGEO),'') = '1' THEN 1
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_CAB,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INANTDEC),'')='S' THEN 1

ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE,

WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INCONGEN),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INASINTO),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INEMERG),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_URGENCIA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREQHOS),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.TCADMIS),'') AS CVE_TIPO_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREADMI),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_READMISION,
COALESCE(KACM50T.NUDIAINT,-999) AS NUM_DIAS_TERAPIA_INTENSIVA,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INPADREL),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDCAUACC),'') AS CVE_CAUSA_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDLUGACC),'') AS CVE_UBICACION_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.CDACTDEP),'') AS CVE_ACCIDENTE,
COALESCE(KACM57T.BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,-1) AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTMAD = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTMAD ) < 8 OR KACM56T.FEANTMAD < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTMAD,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA,
CASE WHEN KACM56T.FEANTTIT = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM56T.FEANTTIT ) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM56T.FEANTTIT,10000101) END AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTMAM),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_MAMA_BIEN,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM56T.INESTBEB),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_BEBE_BIEN,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGIN,-999) AS CALIFICACION_INICIAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(KACM56T.CALAPGFI,-999) AS CALIFICACION_FINAL_BEBE,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INESTVAL),'') AS CVE_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEESTVAL = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEESTVAL) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEESTVAL,10000101) END AS FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPRIVIS = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPRIVIS,10000101) END AS FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS,240101) IN (0,240101) THEN '00:00:00' ELSE
CONCAT(SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),1,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),3,2),':',SUBSTRING(LPAD(CAST(KACM50T.HOPRIVIS AS STRING),6,'0'),5,2))
END AS HR_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FEPROME = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FEPROME) < 8 OR KACM50T.FEPROME < 14000101 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FEPROME,10000101) END AS FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.NUMHABIT),'') AS NUM_HABITACION_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='S' THEN 1
WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INREPOSH),'')='N' THEN 0
ELSE -1 END AS BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.INRESDIC),'') AS CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCSITSIN),'') AS CVE_SITUACION_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.TCMOTTER),'') AS CVE_MOTIVO_TERMINACION,
COALESCE(TRIM(KSIM10T.CDINTERM),'') AS CVE_AGENTE,
'' AS CVE_DA_AGENTE,
-999 AS NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) = 0 THEN ''
WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KACM50T.CDFILHOS)) > 1 THEN
CASE WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA)) > 1 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.NOEMPTRA,''))
ELSE (CASE WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE = 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTHOS0.HOS_NOM,''))
WHEN NPMTRPV0.TPV_CVE > 2 THEN TRIM(COALESCE(NPMTSAU0.SAU_NOM_PEE,''))
ELSE ''
END
)
END
ELSE ''
END AS RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCT),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
COALESCE(TRIM(KACM50T.CDMCR),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_PROV.CDRFC,'')) AS RFC_HOSPITAL,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNNOMRZS,'')) AS NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP1RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(COALESCE(KPEM08T_ASG.DNAP2RZS,'')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CASE WHEN KACM50T.FERESDIC = 0 OR LENGTH(KACM50T.FERESDIC) < 8 THEN 10000101
ELSE COALESCE(KACM50T.FERESDIC,10000101) END AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
COALESCE(KACM50T.INRESDIC,'') AS CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
KACM54T.VADEDNAP AS MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
'MXP' AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
KACM50T.POCOASHM AS PCT_COASEGURO,
KACM50T.POCOASGH AS PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP,
KACM50T.PORECARG AS PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
KACM50T.POCOAADI AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
KACM50T.POCOAGFH AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
KACM51T.CTNUICD  as CTNUICD,
KACA53T.CDSECUEN AS CDSECUEN
FROM
(
SELECT KSI.*, KCI.inancaco
FROM (
SELECT CDSINIES,INAPSLCF,FECOMUNI,FEOCUSIN,TCSITSIN,TCMOTTER,CDNUMPOL,CTVRSPOL,CDINTERM,CTSECOBJ
FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM10T
WHERE TCTIPSIN = 'SA'
AND fechaaud > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) KSI
JOIN (SELECT cdnumpol,CTVRSPOL,inancaco FROM bddlcru.KCIM06T WHERE cdciagru = 'SA') KCI
ON  KCI.cdnumpol = KSI.cdnumpol
AND KCI.CTVRSPOL = KSI.CTVRSPOL
) KSIM10T
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM50T KACM50T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KSIA12T KSIA12T
ON KSIM10T.CDSINIES = KSIA12T.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN (SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,TCCDICD,INPRINCI,CTNUICD
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM51T WHERE INPRINCI = 'S' ) KACM51T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES =  KACM51T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN =  KACM51T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM54T KACM54T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM54T.CDSINIES
AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM54T.CTNUPOIN   AND  KACM50T.CDMCT = KACM54T.CDMCT    AND  KACM50T.CDMCR = KACM54T.CDMCR
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KACM56T KACM56T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM56T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM56T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CASE WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(INSIANTE),'') = 'S' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) >= 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO
FROM BDDLCRU.KACM57T  GROUP BY CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN ) KACM57T
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KACM57T.CDSINIES AND KACM50T.CTNUPOIN = KACM57T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_MEDT
ON KACM50T.CDFILDOC = KPEM08T_MEDT.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT CDSINIES,TCPEROBJ,CDFILIAC FROM BDDLCRU.KSIM20T where TCPEROBJ = 'ASG') KSIM20T_ASG
ON KACM50T.CDSINIES = KSIM20T_ASG.CDSINIES
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_ASG
ON KSIM20T_ASG.CDFILIAC = KPEM08T_ASG.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.KPEM08T KPEM08T_PROV
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = KPEM08T_PROV.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN
(select DNNOMRZS,DNAP1RZS,DNAP2RZS,CDSINIES,CTNUPOIN,CDSECUEN from BDDLCRU.KACA53T  where INMEDTRA = 'S' ) KACA53T
ON KACA53T.CDSINIES = KACM50T.CDSINIES	AND KACA53T.CTNUPOIN = KACM50T.CTNUPOIN
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTRPV0 NPMTRPV0
ON KACM50T.CDFILHOS = NPMTRPV0.CDFILIAC
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTHOS0 NPMTHOS0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTHOS0.HOS_RFC) AND NPMTRPV0.RPV_SCR_CVE = NPMTHOS0.HOS_SCR_CVE
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.NPMTSAU0 NPMTSAU0
ON TRIM(NPMTRPV0.RFC_PEE) = TRIM(NPMTSAU0.SAU_RFC_PEE)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_PADECIMIENTO_delta
SELECT Z.*
FROM
(
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_PADECIMIENTO           actual
INNER JOIN BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_PADECIMIENTO_DELTA    stg ON
actual.idmd5         =   stg.idmd5

UNION ALL

FROM    BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_PADECIMIENTO_DELTA        stg
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLALM.ALM_PADECIMIENTO actual ON
stg.idmd5 = actual.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5 IS NULL
) Z

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddltrn.stg_gmm_solicitud_circulo_med_rcla
SELECT DISTINCT
circulo_med.ceo_cve
, circulo_med.mda_cve
, circulo_med.slr_num_fol
, circulo_med.rfc_medico_tratante
, npmtgcm0.tmd_cve
, circulo_med.fch_registro_tramite
FROM  bddltrn.stg_gmm_solicitud_circulo_med_rcla circulo_med
INNER JOIN (SELECT med_rfc, tmd_cve, gcm_fec_ini, gcm_fec_fin FROM bddlorg.npmtgcm0 UNION ALL
SELECT med_rfc, tmd_cve, gcm_fec_ini, gcm_fec_fin FROM bddlcru.npmhgcm0) npmtgcm0
ON TRIM(circulo_med.rfc_medico_tratante) = TRIM(npmtgcm0.med_rfc)
WHERE    npmtgcm0.gcm_fec_ini <= circulo_med.fch_registro_tramite
AND (npmtgcm0.gcm_fec_fin >= circulo_med.fch_registro_tramite OR npmtgcm0.gcm_fec_fin is null)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_ALM_PADECIMIENTO_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    BDDLALM.ALM_PADECIMIENTO        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_PADECIMIENTO_DELTA ) stg ON

WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddltrn.stg_gmm_solicitud_circulo_med_rcla
SELECT
nrltslr0.ceo_cve
, nrltslr0.mda_cve
, nrltslr0.slr_num_fol
, nrltaan0.aan_med_cve AS rfc_medico_tratante
, CAST(NULL AS INT) cve_circulo_medico
, CASE  WHEN nrltaan0.aan_med_tip = 'MI' OR nrltaan0.aan_med_tip = 'MR'
THEN CASE
WHEN nrltslr0.mda_cve = 'RH'
THEN NVL(nrltslr0.slr_fec_ing, nrltslr0.slr_fec_reo)
WHEN nrltslr0.mda_cve = 'RE'
THEN COALESCE(MIN(nrltdog0.dog_fec_exd), nrltslr0.slr_fec_ini_stm, nrltslr0.slr_fec_reo)
ELSE NVL(nrltaan0.aan_fec_pme_gas, nrltslr0.slr_fec_reo)
END
ELSE NULL
END   fch_registro_tramite
FROM (SELECT cve_centro_regional, cve_modalidad, CAST(folio_solicitud AS DECIMAL(7,0)) folio_solicitud FROM bddltrn.stg_gmm_con_alm_solicitud_delta_rcla) enrsol
INNER JOIN bddlint.lmp_nrltslr0 nrltslr0 ON
enrsol.cve_centro_regional      = nrltslr0.ceo_cve
AND enrsol.cve_modalidad            = nrltslr0.mda_cve
AND enrsol.folio_solicitud          = nrltslr0.slr_num_fol
INNER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTAAN0 nrltaan0 ON
nrltaan0.aan_med_tip IN ('MI', 'MR')
AND nrltaan0.ceo_cve = nrltslr0.ceo_cve
AND nrltaan0.mda_cve = nrltslr0.mda_cve
AND nrltaan0.slr_num_fol = nrltslr0.slr_num_fol
LEFT JOIN bddlcru.nrltdog0 ON
nrltslr0.ltd_num = nrltdog0.ltd_num
AND nrltslr0.ltd_anu = nrltdog0.ltd_anu
GROUP BY nrltslr0.ceo_cve , nrltslr0.mda_cve, nrltslr0.slr_num_fol, nrltaan0.aan_fec_pme_gas, nrltslr0.slr_fec_reo
, nrltslr0.slr_fec_ing, nrltslr0.slr_fec_ini_stm, nrltslr0.ltd_num, nrltslr0.ltd_anu, nrltaan0.aan_med_tip, aan_med_cve

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_PADECIMIENTO_DELTA
SELECT DISTINCT
ID_SOLICITUD,
NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,
NUM_CONSECUTIVO_PADECIMIENTO,
CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
DES_SISTEMA_INT,
CVE_SISTEMA,
DES_SISTEMA,
CVE_PAD_ICD9_RECLAMACION,
DES_PAD_ICD9_RECLAMACION,
CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
DES_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
CVE_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION,
DES_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION,
BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,
FROM_UNIXTIME(UNIX_TIMESTAMP()) AS TS_ALTA_HDFS,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', concat(ID_SOLICITUD, NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION, NUM_CONSECUTIVO_PADECIMIENTO)) AS IDMD5,
REFLECT('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils', 'md5Hex', concat(ID_SOLICITUD, NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION, NUM_CONSECUTIVO_PADECIMIENTO, CVE_SISTEMA_INT, DES_SISTEMA_INT, CVE_SISTEMA, DES_SISTEMA, CVE_PAD_ICD9_RECLAMACION, DES_PAD_ICD9_RECLAMACION, CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD, DES_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD, CVE_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION, DES_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION, BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_PADECIMIENTO_DELTA_CATALOGOS

INSERT INTO BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_ALM_SOLICITUD_DELTA_RCLA
SELECT DISTINCT
ENRSOL.ID_SOLICITUD,
NVL(CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(NRLTAAN0.AAN_OFN_ORG AS STRING),2,'0'),LPAD(CAST(NRLTAAN0.AAN_POL_NO AS STRING),6,'0')),'') AS NUM_POLIZA,
-999 AS NUM_VERSION_POLIZA,
-999 AS VIGENCIA_POLIZA,
NVL(CONCAT(LPAD(CAST(NRLTAAN0.AAN_OFN_CBR_VGT AS STRING),2,'0'),LPAD(CAST(NRLTAAN0.AAN_NUM_CBR_VGT AS STRING),6,'0')),'') AS NUM_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
-999 AS NUM_RENOVACION_POLIZA_COBRANZA,
-999 AS CONTADOR_SECUENCIA_OBJETO,
CASE WHEN NRLTAAN0.AAN_NUM_CFD IS NULL OR TRIM(NRLTAAN0.AAN_NUM_CFD) = '' THEN LPAD('0', 8, '0') ELSE LPAD(TRIM(regexp_replace(NRLTAAN0.AAN_NUM_CFD, '', '')), 8, '0') END AS
CVE_CLIENTE_ORIGEN,
ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,
ENRSOL.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,
ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD,
ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD,
'AZUL' AS CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
'RCLA' AS CVE_SISTEMA,
TRIM(NVL(NRLTSLR0.SLR_NOM_MDC,'')) AS NOMBRE_MED_TRATANTE,
TRIM(NVL(NRLTSLR0.SLR_APE_PAT_MDC,'')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
TRIM(NVL(regexp_replace(NRLTSLR0.SLR_APE_MAT_MDC,'[\\n\\r]+', ' ' ),'')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_MED_TRATANTE,
NRLTAAN0.aan_med_cve AS RFC_MEDICO_TRATANTE,
NVL(TRIM(NRLTSLR0.ICD_CVE),'') AS CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
'' AS IND_TRAMITE_FONDO_CASHFLOW,
'' AS CVE_HOSPITAL_ORIGEN,
'' AS CVE_CIRCULO_MEDICO,
NVL(TRIM(NRLTSLR0.EVN_TIP),'') AS CVE_TIPO_EVENTO,
'' AS CVE_NIVEL_HOSPITALARIO,
CASE WHEN NVL(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_ING AS STRING),'1000-01-01') IN ('0','1000-01-01') THEN 10000101 ELSE
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_ING AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_ING AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_ING AS STRING),9,2))
AS INT)
END AS FCH_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN NVL(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_SAI_HOS AS STRING),'1000-01-01') IN ('0','1000-01-01') THEN 10000101 ELSE
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_SAI_HOS AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_SAI_HOS AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_SAI_HOS AS STRING),9,2))
AS INT)
END AS FCH_EGRESO_HOSPITAL,
CASE WHEN NVL(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),'1000-01-01') IN ('0','1000-01-01') THEN 10000101 ELSE
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),9,2))
AS INT)
END AS FCH_REPORTE_SINIESTRO,
CASE ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD WHEN 'RE' THEN
CASE WHEN NVL(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),'1000-01-01') IN ('0','1000-01-01') THEN 10000101
ELSE CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),9,2))
AS INT)
END
ELSE
CASE WHEN NVL(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),'1000-01-01') IN ('0','1000-01-01') THEN 10000101
ELSE CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),9,2))
AS INT)
END
END AS FCH_OCURRENCIA_SINIESTRO,
-1 AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL,
-1 AS BAN_CAE,
-1 AS BAN_AFECTA_FRANJA,
-1 AS BAN_CAB,
-1 AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PREEXISTE,
-1 AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_CONGENITO,
-1 AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_ASINTOMATICO,
-1 AS BAN_URGENCIA,
-1 AS BAN_SINIESTRO_HOSPITALIZACION,
'' AS CVE_TIPO_INGRESO_HOSPITAL,
-1 AS BAN_READMISION,
-999 AS NUM_DIAS_TERAPIA_INTENSIVA,
-1 AS BAN_PADECIMIENTO_RELACIONADO,
NVL(TRIM(NRLTSLR0.CAX_CVE),'') AS CVE_CAUSA_ACCIDENTE,
NVL(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_ACC_UBI AS STRING),'') AS CVE_UBICACION_ACCIDENTE,
'' AS CVE_ACCIDENTE,
-1 AS BAN_ANTECEDENTE_DECLARADO,
10000101 AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_MAMA,
10000101 AS FCH_ANTIGUEDAD_TITULAR,
-1 AS BAN_MAMA_BIEN,
-1 AS BAN_BEBE_BIEN,
-999 AS CALIFICACION_INICIAL_BEBE,
-999 AS CALIFICACION_FINAL_BEBE,
'' AS CVE_ESTADO_VALORACION,
10000101 AS FCH_ESTADO_VALORACION,
CASE WHEN NVL(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_HOR_VST AS STRING),'1000-01-01') IN ('0','1000-01-01') THEN 10000101 ELSE
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_HOR_VST AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_HOR_VST AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_HOR_VST AS STRING),9,2))
AS INT)
END AS FCH_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
CASE WHEN NVL(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_HOR_VST AS STRING),'00:00:00') IN ('0','00:00:00') THEN '00:00:00' ELSE
SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_HOR_VST AS STRING),12,8)
END AS HR_PRIMER_VISITA_GNP,
10000101 AS FCH_PROMESA_RESPUESTA,
NVL(NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_CKO,'') AS NUM_HABITACION_HOSPITAL,
-1 AS BAN_REPORTE_POSTHOSPITALARIO,
NVL(CAST(NRLTSLR0.RES_CVE AS STRING),'') AS CVE_RESULTADO_DICTAMEN,
'' AS CVE_SITUACION_SINIESTRO,
'' AS CVE_MOTIVO_TERMINACION,
NVL(TRIM(NRLTSLR0.AGT_CVE),'') AS CVE_AGENTE,
'' AS CVE_DA_AGENTE,
ENRSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,
'' AS RAZON_SOCIAL_PROVEEDOR,
'' AS CVE_COBERTURA_SINIESTRO,
NVL(TRIM(NRLTDDC0.COB_CVE),'') AS CVE_COBERTURA_AFECTADA,
TRIM(NVL(NRLTAAN0.AAN_HOS_CVE,'')) AS RFC_HOSPITAL,
TRIM(NVL(NRLTSLR0.SLR_NOM_ASE,'')) AS NOMBRE_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(NVL(NRLTSLR0.SLR_APE_PAT_ASE,'')) AS APELLIDO_PATERNO_ASEGURADO,
TRIM(NVL(NRLTSLR0.SLR_APE_MAT_ASE,'')) AS APELLIDO_MATERNO_ASEGURADO,
CASE WHEN NVL(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_DIC AS STRING),'1000-01-01') IN ('0','1000-01-01') THEN 10000101 ELSE
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_DIC AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_DIC AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_DIC AS STRING),9,2))
AS INT)
END AS FCH_DICTAMEN,
NVL(NRLTSLR0.EDL_CVE_ACT,'') AS CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_DED_VAL AS MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
TRIM(NVL(NRLTDDC0.DDC_DED_UNI,'')) AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_COA_HON_CAL / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_COA_GAS_CAL / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO_GASTOS_HOSP,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_COA_TOG_VAL / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_COA_ADI_VAL / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_GAS_FUE_HOS / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
0 AS CTNUICD,
0  AS  CDSECUEN
FROM (
SELECT ENRSOL.ID_SOLICITUD,ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,ENRSOL.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD,ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD,ENRSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,ENRSOL.NUM_ENTE_INTERVINIENTE,ENRSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT,ENRSOL.ts_alta_hdfs
FROM BDDLENR.ENR_SOLICITUD AS ENRSOL
WHERE ENRSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT='AZUL'
AND ENRSOL.ts_alta_hdfs > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) ENRSOL
INNER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTSLR0 NRLTSLR0
ON ENRSOL.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL = NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE AND ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD = NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE AND ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD = CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING) AND NVL(ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,'') = NVL(NRLTSLR0.RCL_NUM,'')
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDDC0 NRLTDDC0
ON NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE = NRLTDDC0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE = NRLTDDC0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = NRLTDDC0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTAAN0 NRLTAAN0
ON NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE = NRLTAAN0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE = NRLTAAN0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = NRLTAAN0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL, MIN(DOG0.DOG_FEC_EXD) AS DOG_FEC_EXD
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDOG0 DOG0
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDGG0 DGG0
ON DOG0.LTD_ANU = DGG0.LTD_ANU
AND DOG0.LTD_NUM = DGG0.LTD_NUM
AND DOG0.DOG_FOL = DGG0.DOG_FOL
AND DGG0.DGG_CVE = 1
GROUP BY DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL
) DOGG0
ON NVL(ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,'') = NVL(DOGG0.RCL_NUM,'') AND ENRSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE = DOGG0.SLR_NUM_TMT AND ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD      = CAST(DOGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING)

ELSE CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),9,2))

AS INT)

NRLTDDC0.DDC_GAS_FUE_HOS / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,

FROM (
SELECT ENRSOL.ID_SOLICITUD,ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,ENRSOL.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD,ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD,ENRSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,ENRSOL.NUM_ENTE_INTERVINIENTE,ENRSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT,ENRSOL.ts_alta_hdfs
FROM BDDLENR.ENR_SOLICITUD AS ENRSOL
WHERE ENRSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT='AZUL'
AND ENRSOL.ts_alta_hdfs > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) ENRSOL
INNER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTSLR0 NRLTSLR0
ON ENRSOL.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL = NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE AND ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD = NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE AND ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD = CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING) AND NVL(ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,'') = NVL(NRLTSLR0.RCL_NUM,'')
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDDC0 NRLTDDC0
ON NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE = NRLTDDC0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE = NRLTDDC0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = NRLTDDC0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTAAN0 NRLTAAN0
ON NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE = NRLTAAN0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE = NRLTAAN0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = NRLTAAN0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL, MIN(DOG0.DOG_FEC_EXD) AS DOG_FEC_EXD
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDOG0 DOG0
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDGG0 DGG0
ON DOG0.LTD_ANU = DGG0.LTD_ANU
AND DOG0.LTD_NUM = DGG0.LTD_NUM
AND DOG0.DOG_FOL = DGG0.DOG_FOL
AND DGG0.DGG_CVE = 1
GROUP BY DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL
) DOGG0
ON NVL(ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,'') = NVL(DOGG0.RCL_NUM,'') AND ENRSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE = DOGG0.SLR_NUM_TMT AND ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD      = CAST(DOGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING)

GROUP BY DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL

FROM (
SELECT ENRSOL.ID_SOLICITUD,ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,ENRSOL.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD,ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD,ENRSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,ENRSOL.NUM_ENTE_INTERVINIENTE,ENRSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT,ENRSOL.ts_alta_hdfs
FROM BDDLENR.ENR_SOLICITUD AS ENRSOL
WHERE ENRSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT='AZUL'
AND ENRSOL.ts_alta_hdfs > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) ENRSOL
INNER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTSLR0 NRLTSLR0
ON ENRSOL.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL = NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE AND ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD = NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE AND ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD = CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING) AND NVL(ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,'') = NVL(NRLTSLR0.RCL_NUM,'')
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDDC0 NRLTDDC0
ON NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE = NRLTDDC0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE = NRLTDDC0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = NRLTDDC0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTAAN0 NRLTAAN0
ON NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE = NRLTAAN0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE = NRLTAAN0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = NRLTAAN0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL, MIN(DOG0.DOG_FEC_EXD) AS DOG_FEC_EXD
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDOG0 DOG0
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDGG0 DGG0
ON DOG0.LTD_ANU = DGG0.LTD_ANU
AND DOG0.LTD_NUM = DGG0.LTD_NUM
AND DOG0.DOG_FOL = DGG0.DOG_FOL
AND DGG0.DGG_CVE = 1
GROUP BY DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL
) DOGG0
ON NVL(ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,'') = NVL(DOGG0.RCL_NUM,'') AND ENRSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE = DOGG0.SLR_NUM_TMT AND ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD      = CAST(DOGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING)

GROUP BY DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL

CASE ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD WHEN 'RE' THEN
CASE WHEN NVL(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),'1000-01-01') IN ('0','1000-01-01') THEN 10000101
ELSE CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),9,2))

END

CASE WHEN NVL(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),'1000-01-01') IN ('0','1000-01-01') THEN 10000101
ELSE CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),9,2))

AS INT)

NVL(NRLTSLR0.EDL_CVE_ACT,'') AS CVE_ESTATUS_DICTAMEN,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_DED_VAL AS MTO_DEDUCIBLE,
TRIM(NVL(NRLTDDC0.DDC_DED_UNI,'')) AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_COA_HON_CAL / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO,

NRLTDDC0.DDC_COA_ADI_VAL / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_GAS_FUE_HOS / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,
0 AS CTNUICD,
0  AS  CDSECUEN
FROM (
SELECT ENRSOL.ID_SOLICITUD,ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,ENRSOL.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL,ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD,ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD,ENRSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE,ENRSOL.NUM_ENTE_INTERVINIENTE,ENRSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT,ENRSOL.ts_alta_hdfs
FROM BDDLENR.ENR_SOLICITUD AS ENRSOL
WHERE ENRSOL.CVE_SISTEMA_INT='AZUL'
AND ENRSOL.ts_alta_hdfs > date_sub(current_timestamp(),15)
) ENRSOL
INNER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTSLR0 NRLTSLR0
ON ENRSOL.CVE_CENTRO_REGIONAL = NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE AND ENRSOL.CVE_MODALIDAD = NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE AND ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD = CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING) AND NVL(ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,'') = NVL(NRLTSLR0.RCL_NUM,'')
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDDC0 NRLTDDC0
ON NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE = NRLTDDC0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE = NRLTDDC0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = NRLTDDC0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTAAN0 NRLTAAN0
ON NRLTSLR0.CEO_CVE = NRLTAAN0.CEO_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.MDA_CVE = NRLTAAN0.MDA_CVE AND NRLTSLR0.SLR_NUM_FOL = NRLTAAN0.SLR_NUM_FOL
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL, MIN(DOG0.DOG_FEC_EXD) AS DOG_FEC_EXD
FROM BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDOG0 DOG0
LEFT OUTER JOIN BDDLINT.LMP_NRLTDGG0 DGG0
ON DOG0.LTD_ANU = DGG0.LTD_ANU
AND DOG0.LTD_NUM = DGG0.LTD_NUM
AND DOG0.DOG_FOL = DGG0.DOG_FOL
AND DGG0.DGG_CVE = 1
GROUP BY DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL
) DOGG0
ON NVL(ENRSOL.NUM_RECLAMACION,'') = NVL(DOGG0.RCL_NUM,'') AND ENRSOL.NUM_SOLICITUD_TRAMITE = DOGG0.SLR_NUM_TMT AND ENRSOL.FOLIO_SOLICITUD      = CAST(DOGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL AS STRING)

CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),9,2))

ELSE CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(DOGG0.DOG_FEC_EXD AS STRING),9,2))

ELSE CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),1,4),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),6,2),SUBSTRING(CAST(NRLTSLR0.SLR_FEC_REO AS STRING),9,2))

TRIM(NVL(NRLTDDC0.DDC_DED_UNI,'')) AS CVE_UNIDAD_DEDUCIBLE,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_COA_HON_CAL / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO,

NRLTDDC0.DDC_COA_TOG_VAL / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO_NIVEL_HOSP,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_COA_ADI_VAL / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO_ADICIONAL,
NRLTDDC0.DDC_GAS_FUE_HOS / 100.0 AS PCT_COASEGURO_FUERA_HOSP,

) ENRSOL

GROUP BY DOG0.RCL_NUM,DOG0.SLR_NUM_TMT,DGG0.SLR_NUM_FOL
) DOGG0

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_PADECIMIENTO_DELTA_CATALOGOS
SELECT
ID_SOLICITUD,
NUM_CONSECUTIVO_COMPLICACION,
NUM_CONSECUTIVO_PADECIMIENTO,
PADECIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA_INT,
NVL(SISTEMA_INT.SISTEMA, ''),
PADECIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA,
NVL(SIST.SISTEMA, ''),
CVE_PAD_ICD9_RECLAMACION,
NVL(TRIM(GCCTICDC.PADECIMIENTO_ICD9_ESP), ''),
CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD,
NVL(TRIM(GCCTICDC1.PADECIMIENTO_ICD9_ESP), ''),
CVE_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION,
NVL(TRIM(GCCTICDC2.PADECIMIENTO_ICD9_ESP), ''),
BAN_PADECIMIENTO_PRINCIPAL
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_PADECIMIENTO_DELTA_FORMATEO PADECIMIENTO
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN SISTEMA_INT
ON TRIM(PADECIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA_INT) = TRIM(SISTEMA_INT.CVE_SISTEMA)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_SISTEMA_ORIGEN SIST
ON TRIM(PADECIMIENTO.CVE_SISTEMA) = TRIM(SIST.CVE_SISTEMA)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_PADECIMIENTO_ICD9 GCCTICDC
ON TRIM(PADECIMIENTO.CVE_PAD_ICD9_RECLAMACION) = TRIM(GCCTICDC.CVE_ICD9)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_PADECIMIENTO_ICD9 GCCTICDC1
ON TRIM(PADECIMIENTO.CVE_PAD_ICD9_SOLICITUD) = TRIM(GCCTICDC1.CVE_ICD9)
LEFT JOIN BDDLCRU.CAT_PADECIMIENTO_ICD9 GCCTICDC2
ON TRIM(PADECIMIENTO.CVE_PAD_ICD9_COMPLICACION) = TRIM(GCCTICDC2.CVE_ICD9)

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_CON_PADECIMIENTO_DELTA_CATALOGOS
SELECT
